title: Delightful!
text: This is a gem! I bought this for my 3 yr old, learning basic math skills. What a treat. The pieces are so sturdy, well constructed and so bright and colorful! Muffins are adorable and a great size for little hands. These pieces are not tiny! And they are solid, not hollow. The dice are large, soft and colorful. The versatility of ways to play, match, sort, count is wonderful. The little cards and dice direct the child to group the muffins into the cups in various ways, or make patterns. She even stacked the muffins (into a pyramid sort of pile) which was a delight to watch. Oh, and the squeezy tweezers! Even I want to use those  things!! I was so pleased over all and she is having a blast. I HIGHLY recommend this gem of a product. For learning to count, color sort or just play. I would buy again and again! Now I have to go help her create an oven...because as an added bonus, she's "making me muffins" for breakfast.

title: He's beautiful and very realistic.
text:
This doll is not a real reborn, however is a factory doll with realistic features. He is a great option for someone who can't afford a true reborn baby. He has a lot of lifelike features such as blushing, mottling, veining, and even glossing around his little nose.

His head and limbs are soft vinyl and his body is cloth and is slightly weighted. His limbs are a bit difficult to pose, but you can if you work with them. He comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate.

For the price, this little guy is worth it. He is very realistic and is perfect for both kids and adult collectors.

title: A beautiful baby doll and so realistic.
text:
This baby doll is beautiful and so realistic. Truly great for the price as real reborn dolls can cost hundreds to thousands of dollars. This is a great alternative, even if he is a factory doll.

He has lifelike features: mottling, veining, and blushing all over. His hair is painted on very nicely and his body is cloth. His limbs are a soft vinyl and they are posable (but you just have to work with them).

He comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate.

He is really so sweet and perfect for both doll collectors and children!

title: Wow! She is so beautiful!
text:
This baby doll is not a real reborn, but is a more affordable option. She is a factory doll with very realistic details and is truly so beautiful! Her features are so lifelike!

She looks just like a real baby and her body is slightly weighted so she even feels like a real baby. Her body is cloth and her limbs are a soft vinyl. Her limbs are posable, but you have to work with them.

She comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. She is wearing a regular white onesie, but that is the fun part - dressing her up! Also, this baby could be a boy or a girl, you decide! Her face does look more like a girl, but she could also pass as a boy. My wife is a doll collector and loves this little girl!

title: It's not silicone, it's full vinyl from head to toe.
text:
This doll is advertised as silicone. It is not silicone. It is full vinyl from head to toe. Also, the appearance of the doll makes it look more like a boy, but in fact it is anatomically correct and is a girl.

This doll is great for a full body vinyl doll with realistic features. She does look very real, but again, looks more like a boy doll than a girl. She even came with a blue baby bottle. She also comes with a birth certificate and a magnetic pacifier.

Good quality factory doll for the price though.

title: Beautiful doll, but has different limbs.
text:
This doll looks like a brand new baby girl. She is incredibly realistic with mottling, veining, and blushing all over.

She is a Frankenbaby though.

The photos show that the doll is August. The doll I received is the August head and Lou Lou's limbs. The limbs are different from the picture as 2 kits were used to create this doll. The seller may want to update the product pictures to match the doll you receive.

Her cloth body is slightly weighted and her legs are 3/4 and posable. Her arms are full vinyl, and you do have to work with them to pose them. She comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. Her hair is painted on very nicely. She even has glossing on her face under her little nose which adds more realism! She is a fantastic doll for the price. She is not a real reborn, but is so cute and is great for both kids and adults!

text: Love these magnetic protective cases. My kids put their rare Pokemon cards in there and they work perfectly. Great for displaying!

title: Nice cards for the price.
text: These are authentic Pokemon cards and you get so many at a low price. The cards are nice quality and you get 4 holo and 1 rare just like the package says. My kids love them.

title: Adorable Valentine's set!
text: This Valentines snap bracelet set is adorable. It comes with 28 snap bracelets and cards. These are a great option for a child to give to classmates instead of the traditional candy and a card.

title: Fun set for Valentines!
text: This Valentines set is fun! It includes 28 foam airplanes (unassembled), clear gift bags, temporary tattoos, and Valentines cards. Perfect for a child to give to classmates on Valentine's Day, instead of candy. It's a great value overall.

title: Cute valentines!
text: These dinosaur valentines are really cute! You get 24 cards, dinosaurs, and ties. You just use the tie to secure them to the card. Really cute idea and it's different.

title: Colorful, but not rubber. They are plastic.
text: The description of these toy lizards says that they are rubber. They aren't. Instead they are made of plastic. They are really cute and colorful though.

title: She is very beautiful, but not a reborn.
text:
This doll is very beautiful, but she is not a reborn. She is a full vinyl doll with some lifelike features. She would be a great doll for a child.

Her hair is a wig, but it is very soft and so pretty. Her face is gorgeous. She comes with 2 outfits, a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate.

Her outfits are very pretty and so are her shoes. The clothing quality is fantastic.

The doll is a good size too.

title: So much fun! A great set.
text: These pop it keychains are so much fun! You can attach them to a backpack and other things. The pop its come separate from the keychains, so you need to put them together yourself. There are so many different colors!

title: Good quality Christmas stickers.
text: These Christmas Stickers are good quality, fun, and colorful! They are easy to peel and stick and there are so many different designs included!

title: He's sooo cute!
text:
This little boy doll is sooo cute! He is not a reborn and is not the most realistic looking, but is still adorable and well worth the price.

His body is cloth and very soft. He is not weighted and has a vinyl head and limbs. His outfit is adorable and he comes wearing a diaper as well.

He also comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. His hair is a wig, but is very soft.

This doll would be perfect for a young child to enjoy!

title: Adorable doll for the price.
text:
This doll is not a reborn, but she is so adorable. She is not the most realistic looking, but is still a good quality doll. Her face expression is very cute and her hair is so soft. Her outfit is so pretty too!

She comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate that you can fill out.

Her body is cloth and is very soft, but she is not weighted. Her limbs and head are vinyl. She has blushing all over too. I would say for the price she is definitely worth it.

title: Adorable baby doll for the price.
text: This baby doll is adorable and very much worth the price. She is a bargain for the quality. She is 22” long and the size of a newborn baby. Her body is soft cloth and her head and limbs and vinyl. She has the sweetest little face and her hair is a wig, but her hair is soft. Her outfit is so cute too. She comes with a birth certificate, blanket, bottle, and a magnetic pacifier. Her limbs do pose, so that you can move her into a sitting position. I would say she would be better for children than adult doll collectors though, but she is still really nice quality.

title: Adorable full body silicone baby boy!
text:
This full body silicone baby boy is heavy, and feels just like holding a real baby! His silicone is pretty firm compared to some others. He is good quality and you can easily sit him up.

The company was so nice to send some extras with him. They sent a Santa hat and reindeer antlers that actually fit my wife's head perfectly, Christmas window clings, magic milk and juice bottles, a pacifier, a birth certificate, and an outfit.

The outfit was unfortunately too small for him. Only the shirt fit. The overalls and the hat did not fit him as he is too big. That is fine as he fits perfect in newborn clothing and my wife was able to find an outfit that fits him. He also doesn't come with a diaper, so you will need your own.

His eyes and facial features look so real. His eyelashes are very long, even better than my wife's when she wears mascara! Ha!

FYI: You can see the silicone injection spot on the top of his head, and the seams on the sides. If this is an issue for you, then this doll is not for you. It is completely normal for silicone dolls to have this.

Overall, he is a very realistic looking full body silicone baby boy and anyone would love him! He feels so real, just like holding a real baby in your arms!

title: Super cute and soft!
text: My kids love the movie Sea Beast and I don't remember this little guy, but they do! He is super cute and they love him. He is very soft and cuddly.

title: Looks just like the Sea Beast in the movie!
text: This Sea Beast pillow is very soft and cuddly. It also looks just like the Sea Beast in the movie! Great quality all around.

title: Very nice hard shell case!
text: This hard shell zip case is very nice. It is perfect for store your Pokemon cards in! It zips and unzips easily and feels very durable so that it will protect your cards.

title: He's adorable and such a great price too!
text:
This little boy doll is so adorable. He has a lot of realistic features and blushing all over. I couldn't believe the price, as these dolls usually cost more for this type of awesome quality.

His hair is very soft and is a wig. His eyes are beautiful and blue. He comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. His little outfit is so sweet and he has a matching hat as well.

His head and limbs are vinyl and his body is cloth. His legs are posable so that you can move him to a sitting position easily. His cloth body is slightly weighted too.

He is a great doll for both children and adult collectors. He is so lifelike and cute!

title: Cute stickers!
text: These Hello Kitty stickers are so cute! Even better that they are waterproof and good quality. Each one is different and they are very easy to peel and stick.

title: Beautiful baby girl!
text:
This baby girl by Milidool is so beautiful! She has a lot of realistic features and has the prettiest face ever. My wife is a doll collector and loves this little girl's expression.

Her body is cloth and is nicely weighted. Her hair is a wig, but is soft. Her head and limbs are a soft vinyl. She comes with a plush bunny, bottle, magnetic pacifier, blanket, and a birth certificate.

She is a great quality, beautiful doll at a bargain price. Perfect for both adult collectors and children!

title: He's really cute!
text: This little miniature silicone doll is really cute! It is a full body silicone baby and is very tiny, and can fit in your hand. He has a skeleton inside and you can feel it. His hair is rooted nicely and he is wearing an adorable outfit. He is also anatomically correct.

title: He's adorable, but his hair is very thin.
text:
This baby boy doll is a full vinyl doll that is anatomically correct. He is super cute, however his hair is rooted and is very thin. If he had a better rooting job, he would be almost perfect. Another thing is his back is kind of strange. It looks like a concave back. Outside of those 2 things, he is perfect.

His outfit is very cute and his limbs and head are posable. He comes with a plush friend, birth certificate, bottle, and a magnetic pacifier. He has veining and blushing details all over to give a realistic look.

title: Beautiful and very realistic.
text:
This baby girl is very beautiful and very realistic looking. She is the size of a real newborn baby. Her hair is painted on very nicely and she has nice details all over her vinyl skin.

Her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. Her limbs and head are soft vinyl and are soft. Her limbs are posable.

She comes with a headband, birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. She is a great alternative if you can't afford a real reborn baby as they could be very expensive. She has a lot of nice details and is well worth the price.

title: Awesome toy car!
text: This RC Lamborghini remote control car is so cool! Perfect for teenagers or older children. It comes with a remote and a rechargeable lithium battery, which is nice as you don't have to worry about supplying extra batteries for the car. The color is nice, and it looks sharp.

title: Adorable little nightlight!
text: This little Snug Bug nightlight is so cute! He comes with his own little snuggle pod and works great as a nightlight. He already comes with batteries and has 2 glowing modes: bright or a duller mode. My daughter has these books and just loves these little glowing bugs!

title: Wow! It's soooo nice!
text: This Pokemon binder is so nice! It is nicely made and it has Mewtwo on the front (my daughter's favorite)! It has lots of slots so you can add all of your favorite cards to it.

title: Adorable silicone piglet!
text:
This silicone piglet is absolutely adorable! It is so tiny, and the easiest pet to care for. No messes to clean up, nothing. Just play with it!

My daughter loves it! The silicone is squishy and it comes with a bottle, leash, stairs, and a fuzzy sleeping bag.

It looks so much like a real piglet, except it's not. It's silicone! Just a reminder that silicone is delicate, so this little piglet does need to be handled with care.

title: Squishy and so adorable!
text: This review is for 4 miniature silicone babies: Emma, Madison, Isabella, and Aiden. All 4 are so different and unique, but all are great quality. They are soft and squishy and fit right in the palm of your hand. The girls all have matching outfits and Aiden is dressed like a little gentleman. They don't come with any accessories other than their outfits, but that is fine as the babies are perfect! Highly recommend for adult collectors and older, mature children as these silicone dolls do need to be handled with care.

title: Beautiful baby dolls!
text:
This review is for 2 baby dolls: Sleeping Lion and Sleeping Deer.

Sleeping Deer baby girl:

This little girl by Aori is so cute! Her adorable deer outfit matches her plush deer friend that comes with her. She also comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a mat.

Her cloth body is weighted very nicely and her head and limbs are a soft vinyl - perfect for cuddling!

She has a lot of realistic details and her mohair is very soft. For the price of this doll, the quality is outstanding.

Sleeping Lion Baby Boy:

This little boy is the little girl's twin and is wearing a lion outfit instead of a deer outfit. He comes with a plush lion friend, a blanket, magnetic pacifier, bottle, birth certificate, and a mat.

He looks very realistic and his mohair is very soft. He is a big baby at about 22” and has a good weight. His vinyl is very soft.

For the price, both of these dolls are amazing quality and I highly recommend them.

title: So cute and so squishy!
text:
This review is for 2 mini silicone baby dolls: Isabella and Emma.

Isabella:

This miniature silicone baby is so cute! She is so tiny that she can fit in your hand and the silicone is so squishy. Since she is silicone, she is very delicate - I would only recommend her for older, mature children or adult collectors.

She doesn't come with any accessories, but her outfit is so cute. She is also anatomically correct.

Emma:

Adorable baby doll. She doesn't feel quite as squishy and soft as Isabella, but is still very soft. She is very delicate and is to be handled with care. She looks very realistic and can fit in the palm of your hand.

Both dolls are very realistic and are very soft and squishy. Adorable!

title: Amazing baby boy doll. He looks so real!
text:
This baby boy doll is amazing for the price! He looks so real! His hair is mohair and is very soft. His outfit is so adorable too.

He is a good size and his cloth body is weighted. His limbs and head are soft vinyl, so he is perfect to snuggle.

He comes with a lion lovey, a magnetic pacifier, bottle, mat, and a birth certificate. He is also wearing a hat that matches his adorable outfit.

He has blushing all over which truly makes him look so real. He is perfect. Great for both doll collectors and children.

title: Beautiful smaller sized baby girl.
text: This baby girl by Milidool is very beautiful! She has a sweet expression on her face and looks realistic. She is a smaller sized baby at 18”, but is so adorable. Her body is cloth and is weighted, and her head and limbs are a soft vinyl. She arrives in an adorable bunny bassinet with a bunny plush. She also comes with a diaper, mat, bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. Her hair is a wig, but is very soft. For the price, the quality of this doll is amazing. Perfect for both doll collectors and children!

title: A perfect little sleeping beauty!
text:
This little sleeping beauty by Aori takes your breathe away when you open the box. The presentation is out of this world!!

She arrives wrapped in a beautiful purple plush blanket. The blanket is excellent quality. Her little sleeping face is the cutest little thing too!

She comes with a bunch of accessories, a plush boy, bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate.

Her hair is very soft and beautiful. She has blushing all over and looks very real! Her body is cloth and has a good weight. She is a nice sized baby.

For the price, the details on this doll are amazing. She would make an excellent gift for someone special. Perfect for both doll collectors and children.

title: Beautiful little girl with so many accessories!
text:
This little panda girl by Aori is very beautiful! She is a smaller size at 18”, but still has a good weight to her. She arrives in her cute panda bassinet and comes with a bunch of accessories: plush panda toy, diaper mat, bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. The presentation of this doll is outstanding. She would make an excellent gift.

Her body is cloth and is weighted. Her limbs and head are a soft vinyl and she has blushing all over to give a nice, realistic look. Both doll collectors and children would love this little lady! She's so cute! Also, not to mention, the price is incredible for the quality of this doll.

title: Beautiful boy doll at an amazing price!
text:
This little boy doll by Milidool is so beautiful! My wife collects realistic dolls and reborns and has never been disappointed by this brand before. Their dolls are great quality and the prices are incredible too.

This little guy is actually a good sized doll at 22”. His body is cloth and has a good weight. His head and limbs are a soft vinyl. The vinyl has blushing all over to give a nice, realistic look.

He comes with a bunch of accessories too, a plush owl toy, a mat, a bottle, a magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate that you can fill out.

My wife just loves his owl themed outfit. It is so cute! The clothes are great quality. For the price, this little guy is amazing!

title: Gorgeous doll at a bargain price.
text:
This baby girl by Aori is a gorgeous doll at a bargain price. The quality of the doll is outstanding and you get so many accessories with her! She comes in a plush pink bassinet that you can carry her in. She also comes with a plush pink teddy bear, a bottle, magnetic pacifier, birth certificate, a bib, and a mat. Her outfit is so pretty and she comes with a matching headband. She is a smaller sized Aori doll, but still has a good weight to her. Her body is cloth and her limbs are 3/4 vinyl and the vinyl is very soft. Her head is also a soft vinyl. Her hair is a wig, but her hair is very soft. She has the cutest little face!

The presentation of this doll is outstanding. My wife loves Aori dolls and this one is amazing. This little girl would be perfect for both doll collectors and children and she would make an excellent Christmas gift.

title: Such a cutie pie!
text: This little mini full body silicone baby by Vollence is such a cutie pie! She is the Liam sculpt and arrives in a little box and is wearing a super cute outfit! Her little face is so cute and the silicone is very squishy. Since silicone is delicate, this doll does need to be handled with care or else she will tear. This doll would be best for adult collectors or older, mature children. She is also a good price for a full body silicone baby! She is so tiny and can fit perfectly in your hand.

title: Wow! He is such a beautiful full silicone doll!
text:
This little guy is such a beautiful full body silicone doll and the price is amazing for his size. My wife collects reborns, realistic dolls, and silicone babies and this little guy is one of her favorites.

He is very heavy, to be exact he weighs 6.6 lbs (weighed him on a baby scale), and it feels just like holding a real baby. He has nice painting and blushing all over to give a nice realistic look.

Since he is a full body silicone baby, he needs to be handled with extra care, or the silicone may tear. I would recommend this boy only for adult collectors or older, mature children that can care for a newborn baby. He needs to be handled just like a real newborn and you do have to support his neck when holding him.

He doesn't come with any accessories, but that is fine. His outfit and matching hat are so cute! He is dressed just like a little gentleman.

The silicone is very squishy and he even has a opened mouth and can take a bottle or a regular pacifier. Please be aware that you can see the silicone injection spots on this doll, and that is normal for these types of dolls. You can also see the seams. This is also normal for these types of dolls. He is also anatomically correct. He wasn't wearing a diaper, but that is fine as you can put one on him. It is also a good habit to frequently bathe and powder these dolls after bathing, so the silicone doesn't get sticky.

He is super adorable and well worth the price. The quality of this doll is amazing!

title: So tiny and so cute!
text: This little miniature silicone baby by Vollence is so tiny and so cute! He is a silicone Liam sculpt and has the cutest little face. He arrives wearing a cute outfit too. He is so tiny that he can fit perfectly in your hand. The silicone is good quality and very squishy. Since silicone is delicate, I would only recommend this doll for older children and adult collectors. He is a good price for a full silicone baby too!

title: Amazing quality dolls and worth the price.
text:
This review is for 2 dolls: Flamingo baby girl and Crab baby boy.

Flamingo baby girl:

This baby girl by Aori is such a beautiful doll and she is well worth the price. She has the sweetest little face and is a good size baby. She is 22” long and can wear 0-3 months sized clothing.

Her body is cloth and has a good weight for a manufactured doll. Her hair is very soft and her eyes are so pretty. Her head and limbs are a soft vinyl. She comes with a plush flamingo friend, a bottle, magnetic pacifier, changing pad, and a birth certificate. Her outfit is so pretty and it comes with a matching headband. She has blushing all over to give a realistic look. This doll is perfect for both collectors and children.

Crab baby boy:

This little baby boy doll is absolutely adorable! He is wearing the cutest crab outfit and has such a sweet chunky little face. He is nicely weighted and his vinyl is very soft. He has a lot of realistic details. For the price, the quality is amazing.

He comes with a plush friend, a blanket, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate.

Both of these dolls are amazing and definitely worth the price. The quality is outstanding!

title: Adorable lifelike dog!
text:
This little dog is so cute! It is so lifelike and barks and walks. It requires 3 x AA batteries (not included). He also comes with a plastic milk bottle so your child can pretend to feed him.

There are 2 modes with this toy dog, “on” or “try me”. He only walks in the “try me” mode. When in the “on” mode he will just bark and lick. When in the “try me” mode, there is a switch on the side of his waist that will change the mode from walking to barking and licking. He is so soft and so cute. My daughter just loves him so much!

title: It's too cute!!
text: [[VIDEOID:e5f9cb6f2c0b405177f597c4478fdcad]] This little plush interactive dog is too cute! He looks so much like a real puppy and even acts like one. He requires 3 x AA batteries and comes with a bottle so you can simulate feeding him milk. He has an “on” mode and a “try me” mode. He only walks in the “try me” mode, but there is a switch on the side where you can change the mode while in the “try me” so either he will walk or bark and lick. If in the “on” mode, he only barks and licks. My daughter just loves this little guy!

title: Purrfectly CUTE!
text: [[VIDEOID:62fb334bf3feffcb8c979b04647e66fc]] This little robotic cat is so cute! My daughter loves it so much! It requires 3 x AA batteries (not included) and has an “on” mode and a “try me” mode. It will only walk when in the “try me” mode. When it's in the “on” mode, it will just meow and lick. It is cute, but it seems it does more in the try me mode. There is a button on the side of the cat's waist which will change the mode when in the “try me” mode. It comes with a bottle so you can even pretend to feed it milk. It is adorable and would make a purrfect Christmas gift.

title: So cute!
text: This little robotic cat is so realistic and cute! It requires 3 x AA batteries (not included) and it has a switch to turn on or “try me” mode. It only walks in the “try me” mode though. If you set as “on” it will just keep meowing and licking. My daughter loves it so much. After awhile it can be a bit annoying, so thank goodness for the off switch. Lol!

title: Adorable plush axolotl!
text: This axolotl plush is absolutely adorable! It is very soft and huggable. It comes in a vacuum sealed bag and is a bit wrinkled at first, but eventually it fluffs out.

title: He's soooooo cute!
text:
This little guy by Jizhi is sooooo cute! He has a lot of realistic details and comes with a birth certificate, diaper, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. His hair is rooted perfectly, and is soft and curly. His little sleeping face is so precious.

His body is cloth and slightly weighted. He has a soft vinyl head and limbs. His limbs are posable, so you can switch him from the laying position to a sitting position. His body is so soft and snuggly.

He is really so realistic looking and an incredible baby for the price. Perfect for both doll collectors and children.

title: Awesome puppets!
text: [[VIDEOID:be1e5e215acd87040a9b730fd406f309]] These Christmas puppets are awesome! My kids love them. Perfect for puppet shows and playing with. They are nicely made and very soft. They work on both adult and children's hands. Super cute!

title: So soft and soooo cute!
text: This plush axolotl is so soft and sooo cute! For the low price he is so worth it! My daughter loves axolotls and this little guy. His colors are beautiful and he has the sweetest face!

title: Cute, but looks different from the photo.
text:
This doll is not a reborn. He is a manufactured doll with realistic features. He is cute, but doesn't look anything like the stock photo. The stock photo is a prototype baby, not the baby you will receive. Prototypes from artists can cost you hundreds, even thousands of dollars. This little guy has a lot of realistic details and is good for the price.

His body is cloth and is slightly weighted. His limbs are a soft vinyl and he is posable. He comes with a pink bottle and pink magnetic pacifier… Which is odd for a boy doll. He also comes with a birth certificate that you can fill out.

His hair is rooted very nicely and he has blushing to add that realistic look. He doesn't have any mottling or veining, but still has a lot of great realistic details.

I would say this doll would be perfect for children. Collectors may love him too, but there are more realistic looking dolls out there.

title: So cute! Perfect accessory for Halloween!
text: This little plush black cat is so cute! It is the perfect accessory for Halloween! He is very soft and looks just like the photos!

title: Cute, tiny, but the 1 baby has alien fingers!
text:
These twins are not real reborns, they are replicas and manufactured. They are a good option if you can't afford to buy a true reborn.

Both babies come packaged in one box wrapped in a pink swaddle wrap. Both babies are wearing white onesies, which are too big for them. They would fit best in preemie sized clothing as they are so tiny. They swim in the onesies that they arrived in. Each baby is also wearing a flower headband.

You get 2 bottles and 2 magnetic pacifiers with the babies. The babies have cloth bodies and vinyl limbs and are slightly weighted. They both have painted hair which is done very nicely and have a lot of realistic details.

The one baby has alien fingers. They are extremely long and don't look like regular baby fingers. I guess this makes her unique? Lol.

For the price, they are nice. You get 2 babies for the price that you would normally get just 1 for.

Great for both collectors and children.

title: He's so cute and so soft!
text: This Pinocchio plush is soooo cute! He is so soft and arrives in a vacuum sealed bag. He is a bit wrinkled at first, but eventually fluffs out. Perfect for Pinocchio fans as he looks just like the real Pinocchio from the movie.

title: So cute!
text: This grinch plush is so cute! He looks just like his picture and is very soft. He comes in a vacuum sealed bag, so he is a little wrinkled at first, but then eventually poofs out. Perfect for Christmas!

title: Sooo stinking cute!!!
text:
My wife loves this doll! She is so stinking cute! She especially loves the little hearts on her face. It is like she has her face all painted and is ready for carnival fun!

She has a lot of realistic details and is wearing the cutest little dress. She has blushing all over and her eyes are beautiful. Her body is slightly weighted and her limbs are posable.

She comes with a little plush bear, bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. My wife owns a lot of reborns and also realistic manufactured dolls, and this is the first one that she has seen with it's face painted. It makes it special and unique. She loves it!

title: Soft and squishy, the weight is just like a real baby.
text:
This full body silicone baby is cute! He is super heavy and feels just like holding a real baby. The silicone is very soft and squishy. Since he is a full body silicone, he needs to be handled with care or else he will tear or rip. I would not recommend this doll for younger children. Only older mature children and doll collecting adults.

His eyes are big, bright, and blue. His mouth is open so he can take a pacifier. He is wearing an adorable outfit that even has his name on it - Nathaniel! So cute!

He comes with a baby carrier. It is pink… A little odd for a boy doll, but that is fine, as the doll itself is perfect. He also comes with a magic milk bottle, magic juice bottle, and a pacifier.

This doll is anatomically correct and has a lot of realistic details. It's just like holding a real baby, except this one doesn't cry! Too good to be true. :) My wife is a doll collector and loves this little guy. Highly recommend!

title: Too cute!
text: This little axolotl is too cute! It is tiny, but it is worth the price of $10. So soft, just like a Squishmallow.

title: Gorgeous doll with realistic details!
text:
This baby girl is a manufactured Saskia replica. She is not a real reborn, but is still gorgeous and has a lot of realistic details. Her eyes are stunning, just so beautiful and even more beautiful in person. Her hair is very soft, full, and beautifully rooted. Her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. Her limbs are soft vinyl and are posable.

Her outfit is so cute too! She is wearing beautiful gold bangle bracelets. She comes with 2 rattles, a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. She is definitely worth the price.

title: Not worth it. There is no doll, just clothes.
text:
The description for this product makes it sound like you get 6 BJD dolls + 6 sets of extra clothes for them, however that is not the case. We only received 6 little outfits. The outfits are cute, however they are not worth $90. For paying such a high price tag, you would expect to receive the dolls too. Very disappointed.

The product description needs to be updated as it is very misleading as there are no dolls with this set. Just clothes for tiny dolls.

title: The cutest clown doll ever!
text: This little clown doll is the cutest little clown doll ever! She reminds me of a Funko Pop. She is plastic and her clothes are nice quality. Her hair is blonde, curly, and very full. It's beautiful. She even comes with a little balloon that you can attach to her arm. Oh! And she even comes with a doll stand! It's an amazing doll for the price!

title: Cute little peanut!
text:
This doll looks so realistic! It can be a boy or a girl based on the outfit, so you choose! I think it is supposed to be a boy since the bottle is blue, but honestly it can be either.

The baby has veining, mottling, and blushing all over to give that realistic look. He is a tiny little peanut and fits in preemie sized clothing.

The outfit is adorable, and he comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, and birth certificate. The arms are wrapped in tissue paper and tape. This was a bit difficult to remove. I wish the packaging was a bit less stressful to remove, but once he is out, he is perfect.

He is slightly weighted and has a cloth body. His limbs are a soft vinyl as well as his head. The hair is painted on very nicely.

He looks so real and I think both children and doll collectors would love him!

title: A gorgeous baby! Amazing for the price!
text:
This baby by Aori is gorgeous! She is amazing for the price! I love her outfit and she is packaged so nicely. She comes with the cutest little teddy bear lovey, birth certificate, bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a mat.

She is nicely weighted and her body is floppy, just like a real baby. Her vinyl is very soft. She has blushing all over to make her look realistic. Her hair is beautiful and soft too.

This baby is just amazing. Definitely recommend for both children and collectors.

title: Beautiful full vinyl girl baby dolls with realistic details.
text:
This review is for 2 dolls:

Doll #1: Painted hair
This sweet little girl by Babeside is very beautiful. She is a full vinyl baby and is anatomically correct. She does have realistic details and her eyelashes are so pretty. She has blushing all over too.

She arrives in a bag that is packaged with aromatherapy packets that make her smell good. Her little floral outfit is so cute. Her limbs are fully posable and she comes with a bag of accessories, a diaper, a bottle, and a magnetic pacifier.

I think both children and collectors would love this little lady. She's so cute!

Doll #2: Rooted hair
This sweet little lady from Babeside is absolutely adorable. She is wearing a blue outfit and has the same sweet sleeping face as the doll with the painted hair. The dolls are identical, other than 1 having painted hair and the other having rooted hair. My wife personally loves the doll with the rooted hair as it is very soft.

She has a lot of realistic details and blushing all over. Her body is full vinyl as well and she is also anatomically correct. She comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, birth certificate, hospital bracelet, rattles, and a diaper. She is packaged with aromatherapy and smells so good!

Her limbs are also fully posable just like the other doll.

Both dolls are just perfect. It is just up to your preference if you like rooted hair or painted on hair.

title: Great for your Halloween display!
text: These little plastic spiders work great on outdoor spiderwebs as part of your Halloween display. They attach easily to the spider web and my daughter loved decorating with these. The price is right too.

title: Adorable set!
text: This Elf and Book set is so adorable! My kids love the Elf on the Shelf and this reminds me of it. This Elf is not plush though, he is plastic but is posable. My daughter loves him! The story book is adorable too. The letters are nice and big and perfect for a child to read.

title: Cute, soft, and huggable! The kids love it!
text: This plush Among Us Imposter is cute and looks exactly as pictured! My kids love it as they love anything Among Us. He is soft and huggable!

title: Beautiful doll!
text: This American Girl Truly Me doll is absolutely beautiful! She is wearing a cute camouflage print outfit and comes with a colorful book that your child can fill out. She is 18” tall and has gorgeous long hair. Her face is so cute too. I think any little girl would love this doll!

title: Cool idea, look real, but they didn't stick.
text:
These Vampire fangs are cool. My daughter wanted to be a Vampire for Halloween so I ordered these for her as it is labeled for “kids”.

The Vampire fangs do look just like real teeth and come with moldable plastic pellets which are supposed to help the teeth adhere, however these did not work for my daughter. She is only 6, and it may be because her teeth are too small (baby teeth), but they would not stick with the melted plastic and we followed the instructions exactly to the point. I may have to test these out on my teeth and if they do work, I will be sure to update the review.

title: Your dolls can look like Disney Princesses!
text: These Disney Princess costumes are so cute! Now your dolls can too be Disney princesses. It is perfect for the Halloween season. The dresses are nicely made and fit American Girl dolls perfectly. The only thing that could make these better is if they came with extra accessories and shoes, but still it is a great deal for 6 different costumes.

title: Adorable Halloween outfits!
text: These doll Halloween outfits are so cute! They fit American Girl dolls perfectly and look exactly as pictured. Very nicely made and perfect for the Halloween season!

title: Beautiful Encanto doll clothes!
text: My daughter loves Encanto and these 18” doll clothes look exactly like Mirabel and Isabela's dresses in the movie. They are nicely made and come with cool accessories. My daughter is happy now that she can dress her dolls just like one of her favorite Disney movies!

title: Adorable doll and love her cool hair!
text: This American Girl - So Truly Me doll is an adorable doll! She has the prettiest and coolest hair - It's pink and purple and she is wearing a tie dye dress that matches her hair perfectly. Her hair is very soft and she has sleepy eyes that open and close as you lay her down or stand her up. She comes with a cute little book that you child can fill out to record all of their memories with the doll too.

title: Gorgeous American Girl doll!
text: This American Girl So Truly Me doll is gorgeous. My daughter loves these dolls and we have never been disappointed with one yet. She stands tall at 18” and is wearing a cute black dress. Her hair is blonde and very soft. Her eyes are beautiful and they are sleepy eyes, so if you lay her down her eyes will close. If you stand her up, her eyes will open. She comes with an adorable book that your child can fill out too! This makes this doll so much more fun as your child can record all of their dolly adventures in this sweet book and keep to cherish the memories.

title: Beautiful doll with the coolest hair!
text: This American Girl, So Truly Me doll is probably the coolest one of these that I have seen yet. Her hair is so cool! She has brown hair, but it has streaks of different colors. She is wearing the cutest little camouflage outfit and comes with a book that your child can fill out. She has sleepy eyes too, so if your child lays her down, her eyes will close. When you stand her up, her eyes will open. She is so pretty and I think any child would adore this doll!

title: Such a beautiful American Girl doll!
text: This American Girl - So Truly Me is absolutely beautiful! She stands 18” tall and is packaged so nicely. She even comes with a book that your child can fill out! Her dress is beautiful, her eyes open and close depending on if you lay her down or stand her up, and her hair is a wig, but is so soft and beautiful. She is just a perfect doll all around and so pretty!

title: Beautiful set!
text: My wife loves this witch hat and choker set! It's so pretty and perfect if you are going to be a witch for Halloween! The witch hat is beautiful as it has a flower with beads and lace. The choker is also beautiful and it fits my wife's neck loosely, which is good so it won't get uncomfortable. Awesome set for the price.

title: Makes reading so much fun!
text: I ordered this book “Stink or Swim” for my 6 year old daughter as I thought this would be a great book to learn how to read, and it is! The book is so cute and fun and full of adventures! The little Bookworm toy that comes with it is adorable! When you squeeze him, he lights up (batteries already included too)! This is such a wonderful idea to make reading fun!

title: The kids love them!
text: [[VIDEOID:8c9dc9065484249f60ba16b1c0e90ad5]] These foam glow sticks are awesome! Each is individually wrapped and they all come with batteries. There are 3 different modes to choose from as well. My kids love them and these would be great for Halloween themed parties. They are very bright and fun!

title: Absolutely adorable doll at a great price.
text:
This baby girl doll by Aori is realistic looking and absolutely adorable. We have never been disappointed with an Aori doll as their quality and prices are always great.

She has blushing and little wrinkles on her vinyl to add that realistic look. She has the sweetest little sleeping face and her outfit is so adorable.

She comes with a plush friend, a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. Her body is weighted and is cloth. Her limbs are a soft vinyl. Her hair is very soft. She looks exactly like her photos - What you see is what you get, and she is perfect. Both doll collectors and children would love this sweet girl.

title: Gorgeous dolls at a great price.
text: These little princess dolls are so cute! They have the prettiest faces and have posable limbs. Each doll comes in a beautiful princess dress and they come with additional outfits and accessories. Gorgeous dolls at a great price.

title: The kids love them!
text: These Halloween squishies are a hit with my kids! They love them as they are so squishy, and they don't get sticky at all. Each one is different and they come packaged in a nice box.

title: Great for the kiddos on Halloween!
text: This set of Halloween party favors is great. They are perfect if you are having a Halloween themed party to give to the kiddos. Some of the toys are cheap, but you get 118 pieces, so I would say for the low price it is worth it for the amount you get in this set.

title: Beautiful doll at an incredible price!
text: This doll by Werflot is so realistic looking and beautiful! For the price, the quality of this doll is amazing. He has nicely rooted mohair which is very soft and blushing all over to give that realistic look. His little face is so precious and his outfit is adorable too. He came with a pacifier clip, however the actual pacifier was missing. It's not a big deal though, with or without the pacifier he is perfect. The body is cloth and is weighted very nicely. His limbs are vinyl and the vinyl is soft. His legs are posable and his arms are slightly posable, but you need to work with them. I think both collectors and children would adore this sweet little boy!

title: Good doll for the price.
text:
This baby girl is a good doll for the price. She does have realistic details such as mottling, veining, and blushing. She also has the cutest little smile.

Her body is all vinyl and her limbs are posable. Her body is hollow inside (not weighted), and she has a concave back. For all of the realistic dolls I have seen around this same price point all have the same concave back, so it's not a specific defect of this particular doll. Just keep that in mind when you order this doll, as this is what you will get.

She comes with a bag of basic plastic accessories, bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. Her outfit is adorable, however her hat doesn't stay on too well. I think it is a bit big for her head.

I think this is a good doll for the low price she is being sold at. The painting details on her are great.

title: Awesome foam glow sticks!
text: [[VIDEOID:c189f360f86e306803cd367c060010c8]] These light up LED foam glow sticks are awesome! They are even cooler than I expected them to be. You get 200 in the set. These are perfect for the kiddos on Halloween as they are bright and have 3 different modes to choose from. My kids love them!

title: Adorable baby with a cute round head.
text:
This full body silicone baby boy is adorable. He has the most round head that you have ever seen and just looks so peaceful sleeping. He is nicely painted, however just wish it was more detailed for the price. I have seen other full body silicone dolls that are bigger than this at a similar price that have more detail.

He is heavy! Feels just like holding a real baby. His outfit is so so cute! The packaging idea is wonderful too. He arrives in a box wrapped in a see through heart plastic bag and inside he is wrapped in a swaddle blanket with a hat that matches his outfit.

I would not recommend this doll for children under the age of 14 as silicone needs to be handled with care or it will rip. This doll needs to be handled just as if you were caring for a real baby. I think doll collectors would love this little guy, I just wish the price was a bit less.

One last thing, is that you can see the seams of the silicone mold. If this is something that will bother you, then this doll is not for you.

title: Cute doll at a great price.
text:
This realistic looking doll Lily is so cute! Her details are realistic and she has blushing all over. Her body is full vinyl and her limbs are posable. Her limbs and body is also hollow.

Her hair is rooted, but it is thin in some areas. Her outfit is very beautiful. She comes with a bottle, birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bunch of other accessories.

For the price, I would say this doll is worth it. She is very cute and has a lot of realistic details. I think both kids and adult collectors would love her.

title: Gorgeous doll at an amazing price.
text:
This baby doll is gorgeous and realistic looking. For the price, the quality is amazing. The doll is quite big and the vinyl limbs are posable. The body is cloth and is slightly weighted. The baby has rooted mohair (very soft) and the rooting is done very well. The baby has blushing all over to give that realistic look. The outfit is so so adorable too!

Overall, this is an amazing doll for an amazing price! Perfect for both collectors and children.

title: Beautiful doll for the price!
text:
This sweet baby could be a boy or a girl as it comes in a plain white onesie. I think it is supposed to be a girl as it does come with a pink bottle and a pink magnetic pacifier. She also comes with a birth certificate. She doesn't come in the soft cover shown in the picture though - Just a plain white onesie.

The painting details on her are amazing. She has a lot of blushing, mottling, and veining as if she were done by a real artist. Her hair is even painted on perfectly. For the price, the quality of this doll is amazing.

Her arms are full limbs and her legs are 3/4. She is posable. Her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. She even has some glossing on her face to add that realistic look. This doll is perfect for a child and even a doll collector. She's just gorgeous.

The only recommendation is that we wish she came with a better outfit, but that is fine as it can be changed.

title: A bit pricey for what you get, but the kids like them.
text: These Halloween themed bouncy balls are great to give to the kiddos for a Halloween themed party or even for the trick or treaters. They bounce well and glow in the dark. They come with a cute drawstring bag to keep them in too. If these cost about $5 less, I would say they would be perfect.

title: Perfect for a Halloween themed party.
text: This Halloween gift set is such a neat idea! This is perfect if you are having a Halloween themed party to give to the kiddos! You get 168 pieces total and it comes with 24 of each, so it will work perfect for a group of 24 kids. The quality of the toys inside are nice too.

title: Awesome!
text: [[VIDEOID:2ff702aacc1b7a4b23f1451f81057761]] My kids love this inflatable dinosaur on wheels! This is the coolest toy ever! It takes a few hours to charge and the remote requires 3 x AAA batteries and then all you do is turn on the remote and the dinosaur and watch him go! The remote is very easy to use and it even makes realistic dinosaur sounds. It's definitely awesome!

title: Beautiful doll.
text: This little baby doll by La Newborn and Berenguer is absolutely beautiful. It comes in a nice box complete with all accessories as a new baby would coming home from the hospital. So lifelike and sweet. Great for both collectors and children.

title: So cute, cuddly, and weighted.
text: My 6 year old is fascinated with axolotls, so I had to order her this plush. It has slept by her side since day one and is perfect for cuddling. It is nicely weighted and very soft. It's her new favorite plush!

title: Soft and cuddly! Kids love it!
text: My kids love Rainbow Friends so I had to order them this plush. He is so cute and looks just like the real character. He did have a little  extra thread hanging on his right eye, but that was easily fixed. So soft and cuddly!

title: Looks just like the real character!
text: My kids love Rainbow Friends so I had to get them this plush. He looks just like the real character and is very soft and cuddly.

title: So beautiful and realistic.
text: This sweet little baby girl by Wooroy is so beautiful and realistic. She has veining and mottling all over her skin to give that realistic look. Her legs are 3/4 and posable. Her arms are full limbs. Her head and limbs are soft vinyl and her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. She comes with adorable teal socks that match her outfit, a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. Her hair is painted on perfectly. Perfect for both doll collectors and children, she is such a beauty!

title: Cute set!
text: This talking cash register set is really cute. It comes with batteries installed, so it is all ready to use. It comes with play food and play money. The only downfall is that the fake dollars are too big to fit inside the cash register drawer. Other than that, it is so much fun for my daughter.

title: Moves just like a real snake. Works great on hard floors.
text:
[[VIDEOID:297d00d02a917ec075ff3da71bc194fa]] This Zuru Robo Alive snake is cool and my kids love it. It works great on hard floors, not on carpet. It moves just like a real snake and the eyes and tongue move as well.

This toy requires 3 AAA batteries (not included) and finding the battery compartment was the biggest challenge as it isn't listed in the instructions anywhere. I took a picture of where the battery compartment is located so hopefully this will help you out if you order it and you don't run into my dilemma on searching for the battery compartment. It would be nice if this was in the instructions!

title: Nice alternative to candy
text: These Halloween Party Favors are a nice alternative to candy for trick or treaters or to give to the kiddos if you have a Halloween party. You get a lot in the set. The toys are cheap plastic, but you get a bunch. I would say it is a good value for the amount that you get in the set as candy would cost a lot more.

title: Neat idea, lots of toys, but they are kind of cheap.
text: This is a neat idea. A big bucket filled with a bunch of Halloween toys. Perfect for trick or treaters. The toys are a bit cheap though. If this cost $5 less, I would say it would be worth it.

title: So cute and love her hair!
text: This Cry Babies Dressy Fantasy Bruny doll is so cute! She has rooted hair that you can play with and style too. There is an opening on the back of her head when you can fill with water which will make real tears. Just be careful as this can be a messy task. She will cry and make sounds just like a real baby. Her outfit is so pretty too. This doll has a big head and is top heavy, so she doesn't sit up too well on her own. You will need to lean her up against something. Overall, I think she is a great doll for the price. My daughter loves her!

title: Awww! It's Blue!
text: We love the movie Sea Beast! Little Blue is my daughter's favorite character and this little guy has been by her side since he arrived. He is nicely made and looks just like his photos. You also get a cool little dinosaur keychain with it. Great price too!

title: These little dolls are so cute!
text: These little dolls are so cute and are perfect for a doll collector! My wife loves them. They are dressed in adorable costumes and have the cutest faces. They are packaged in a nice box and each doll is individually wrapped. They are jointed and you can pose them. My wife's favorite is the Ronald McDonald doll. Cuteness overload!

title: Cool mask, but has some flaws.
text: This Venom mask is cool and my daughter loves how it lights up. It is made of plastic, so it can get a bit uncomfortable after wearing for a long period. When it lights up, there is an annoying humming/beeping sound that constantly goes off and that can be a bit annoying. I wish there was a way to get that sound to stop.

title: My kids love this creepy Sonic!
text: This is like the horror version of Sonic and my kids love it! He is creepy looking, but still so soft and cuddly. He comes in a vacuum sealed bag so does take some time to fluff out. He's pretty neat though!

title: Awesome little action figures!
text: These miniature action figures are awesome! Great set for the price. My kids love these things and they work perfect for cakes and play as well. They each come with a little stand. Each comes individually wrapped as well.

title: Beautiful dolls at a great price!
text:
This review is for 2 dolls:

Baby girl with baby blanket:

This baby girl doll by Aori is so beautiful! Her features are so realistic and she has the cutest little sleepy face. She is even wearing a hospital bracelet. She has blushing all over too.

She is wrapped in an adorable colorful unicorn blanket. She comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a plush unicorn toy that matches her blanket.

Her limbs are vinyl, but are soft and her body is cloth and is weighted. Holding her is just like holding a real baby. She is so adorable and both children and doll collectors would love this sweet baby girl.

Sleeping baby girl with plush bunny:

This doll is absolutely gorgeous! She looks very close to the other doll reviewed, they could even be twins. The only difference is their outfits and accessories. This little girl is wearing a pink onesie and she comes with a matching headband, a baby blanket, plush bunny, bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate.

She is nicely weighted and has a cloth body with a vinyl head and limbs. Her vinyl is very soft. Her hair is very soft mohair. She looks so real! Perfect for both collectors and children.

Both dolls are so beautiful and worth the price!

title: Precious posable sleepy baby.
text:
This sleeping baby is so precious! She has very realistic features and her sleepy face is just soooo cute! What is nice about this doll is that she is fully posable.

She has nice blushing all over to give that realistic look and her brown curly hair is rooted very nicely. Her outfit is so pretty and comes with a matching headband.

Her limbs are soft vinyl and her body is cloth (not weighted). She comes with a bag of accessories, a birth certificate, a bottle, and a magnetic pacifier.

She is a super cute doll. The only thing that could make her better is if she were weighted. Other than that, she is perfect.

title: Love the Alice in Wonderland theme!
text: This Baby born surprise mini baby set is so cute! You can actually keep the box and use it as a play set and the little babies are so cute. You get 10 total in the set. Love love love the Alice in Wonderland theme! Soooo cute!

title: Big, soft, and cuddly!
text: My daughter loves this plush shark! He is even bigger than expected and he is so soft and cuddly! Great quality and it looks exactly as pictured.

title: The kids love them! So much fun!
text:
These Halloween pull back cars are so much fun! My kids love them! For the amount that you get (24), I would say they are well worth the price. They work just as expected.

These would be great to use as party favors for the kids at a Halloween party!

title: So cute and so much fun!
text:
This Baby Alive Princess Ellie grows up doll is so cute! She requires 4 x AA batteries (not included) and she says so many different phrases. Her mouth does not move - that is the only bummer about this doll. It would be cooler if her mouth moved when she talks.

The more you interact with this doll, the more she will grow. She comes with a bunch of accessories and will tell you exactly what she wants (hugs, snuggles, food, drink). If you follow what she wants, you will soon see her grow right before you eyes. She also comes with an attachable hair piece and a big girl skirt for when she is fully grown. She even comes with a growth chart.

The neat thing about this doll is that when you turn her off and back on again, she will shrink back down to baby size and you can have fun growing all over again! So so cute!

title: Adorable growing doll!
text:
This Baby Alive Ellie grows up doll is absolutely adorable. She talks, however her mouth or eyes do not move. It would be cool if her mouth moved when she talked. She is so cute as a baby and she grows up into a beautiful princess. She comes with a bunch of accessories that help her grow. She requires 4 x AA batteries (not included).

She says a bunch of different phrases and will tell you exactly what she wants (snuggles, food, drink, etc). If you follow what she wants, you will soon see her grow right before her eyes. The cool thing is, once she is fully grown up, if you turn her off and turn her back on, she shrinks back down to baby size to have fun growing all over again.

title: Soooo cute! But wish her mouth would move when she talks.
text:
This Baby Alive Princess Ellie grows up doll is so cute! My daughter loves Baby Alive dolls and my wife grew up with Baby Alive dolls. This one takes 4 x AA batteries and she talks. The only bummer is that her mouth doesn't move. It would be cooler if they made her mouth move when she talks.

She comes with a bunch of accessories that you can use with her to help her grow. She will tell you if she needs snuggles, or if she is thirsty or hungry. Then watch the magic right before you eyes, she grows! Once you turn her off and turn her back on, she will shrink back down to baby size.

She comes with a tiara/long hair that attaches right to her head to make it appear that she has grown up. She also comes with a “big girl” skirt that you can put on her for when she is grown up. So so cute!

title: Big, soft, and cuddly.
text: My kids love this giant plush snake. It looks exactly as pictured and is very soft. It is giant just like it says in the description and the colors are very bright. Great giant plush for the price.

title: Great for a young child.
text:
This doll is cute, but she is not a reborn. She is a manufactured doll that has somewhat realistic features. My wife is a reborn collector and to be honest, this one looks more just like a regular a baby doll. This doll would be best for young kids, not for collectors.

Her outfit is very cute and her body is full vinyl from head to toe. Her limbs are posable. She comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate. Her hair is pretty nice and is soft. Her vinyl limbs and body are hollow inside.

title: Cute, but pricey for not being authentic.
text: This plush cobra pillow is very squishy, but is not a real squishmallow. The cost of him not being authentic is a bit steep. If he cost a few dollars less, it would be 5 stars as even though he isn't authentic, my daughter loves him so much and he is very soft and squishy.

title: Great for Halloween!
text:
These LED light up rings are great for Halloween. Perfect for the kiddos if you have a Halloween themed party or trick or treaters. There are so many different designs in this set. They light up very bright too.

The only thing is that the packaging could be better. The box was partially dented and already opened. The rings were all out of order up upon opening the box. No damage to the rings themselves though.

title: Awesome giant snake!
text: This giant plush snake is awesome and my 6 year old loves it! It is just as big as expected and it's very soft. There is some tape on his eyes that you need to peel off, I assume it was placed on there to protect his eyes from being scratched.

title: They look so real!
text: These rubber snakes are my daughter's new favorite toy. She has so much fun with them as they look so real! They are nicely detailed and well made.

title: Gorgeous doll!
text: My wife loves Madame Alexander dolls as her Mom and Grandma collected them, and now she collects them as well. This Madame Alexander “It's all me” doll is so cute! She is great for both children and collectors. She comes in a nice box and has accessories for her favorite things: Swimming and dancing! She has jointed arms and legs, so she is posable. Her hair is very beautiful with blonde and purple. She is a gorgeous little doll.

title: Cute, colorful, and so much fun!
text: These Halloween popping keychains are so much fun! They are Halloween shapes and you can hook right on to your keys or backpack with the keychain. They are not too small, and not too big. Just right. Cute and colorful. Perfect for Halloween too!

title: Great set of party favors!
text: These Halloween party favors are great! You get a bunch of them and they light up just as expected. Perfect if you have a Halloween themed party for the kiddos.

title: Amazing little pig for the price!
text:
If you have always dreamed of having a pet pig, especially a baby pig and don't all of the responsibilities of being a pet owner, then this little guy is your answer!

He is silicone and looks just like a real baby pig, but is maintenance free! His silicone is soft and squishy. He has black spots and his hair is rooted. Just be careful with the hair as it is rooted and could fall out if you aren't gentle with him.

I wouldn't recommend this guy for little kids as the silicone may tear. He would be best for older kids and adults.

My wife loves this little guy and named him Ham.

For the price, this little guy is HAM-AZING!

title: Super cute!
text:
This baby doll is super cute! She looks like a Berenguer doll, but is not a real Berenguer doll, and costs about the same price… If her price was a bit less expensive I would give her 5 stars. She is a bit costly for not being a real Berenguer doll.

She has an adorable impish smile and is wearing an adorable pink outfit. Her body is vinyl from head to toe and she is anatomically correct. She comes with a bottle and a magnetic pacifier. She is tiny, but so cute.

title: Adorable, looks like a real newborn baby.
text:
This sweet baby girl looks like a real newborn baby. She is so realistic and her painting details are amazing. Her body is cloth, but not weighted and her limbs and head are a soft vinyl.

She is wearing the cutest pink bunny outfit and comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. Her legs are posable, but her arms not so much. The arms do move, but you have to really work with them.

She is tiny and fits in preemie sized clothing. I think both doll collectors and children would love this sweet little doll. She is beautiful.

title: Very nicely detailed and looks awesome.
text: This Michael Myers mask is very nicely detailed and looks awesome! The fit is great for a teenager or an adult and you can still breathe in it. Nice quality mask for sure!

title: Awesome for the price.
text: These monster trucks are awesome for the price. They are friction powered and my kids love playing with them. It's nice as they are all different colors too, and they are very bright and easy to find.

title: What a perfect beauty! She looks so REAL!
text:
This Sandie doll by Zero Pam is a perfect beauty! She looks so REAL! She has mottling, veining, and blushing all over. Her painting is perfect! For the price, she is so worth it!

Her eyes are blue, but have brown inside… Just gorgeous. Her eyelashes were a bit messed up upon arrival, but my wife cut them and they look better now. Still, with or without eyelashes, she is a beauty. She also doesn't have bottom lashes like shown in the picture, but that is not a big deal.

Her hair is so soft and rooted perfectly. She has the cutest little curls and her hair is a light brown color that is gorgeous and goes perfectly with her blue eyes.

She can stand up when leaning against something. We weighed her on a baby scale and she weighs 3 lbs. Her legs are posable, so you can adjust to sit or stand.

Her body is cloth and her limbs are a very soft vinyl - So she is nice and huggable. Her outfit is so sweet and she comes with a matching headband, shoes, a magnetic pacifier, plastic bottle, diaper, and a birth certificate.

She fits perfectly in 6-9 months size clothing.

If you are looking for a very realistic doll on a budget, then this is it. You won't be disappointed. She is perfect!

My wife is a doll collector and this little lady is one of her favorites!

title: Cute and worth the price.
text:
This Saskia replica doll is very cute and is a great option if you can't afford a true reborn. She is affordable and is painted nicely to give her that realistic look.

Please note: The baby in the first few photos is a prototype and is not the doll you will receive. Please see the manufacturers video or my pictures for a more accurate look at the doll.

Her hair is rooted and looks pretty good for a manufactured doll. Her outfit is kind of plain, but that can always be changed. She comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate.

Her legs are 3/4 vinyl so that you can easily pose her to a sitting position. Her body is cloth and is not weighted. Her limbs are hollow inside. I would still say she is very cute and worth the price.

title: So cute and sounds just like the show!
text: This Tinky Winky talking plush is so cute! He is tiny, but he talks and sounds just like he does on the show. My son grew up watching the Teletubbies, so this is a great memory keepsake for him to have.

title: The cutest!
text: This axolotl plush is the cutest! The axolotl is my daughter's favorite animal, so I had to order this for her. She loves it! It's so soft and huggable and she takes it everywhere with her. It's cheaper than the name brand too.

title: So cute and interactive!
text:
[[VIDEOID:bf96180e532c19a37b698dfb5604d349]] My daughter has loved the Cry Babies since she was little, and Dreamy has to be the best one yet! She has a bunch of them, but none are as interactive as Dreamy is. She is definitely one of her favorites!

She comes with batteries already, so that is a plus! She also comes with an ice cream rattle, a baby bottle, and attached pacifier, and a comb for her hair. Her hair is so soft and very colorful. She has a bald spot on the top of her head where you can open up to fill her with water to make real tears when she cries. When she is upset, her cheeks get red and light up. Her eyes open and shut, her mouth moves, and even there is movement by her eyebrows in her forehead, which i wasn't even expecting to see - So that was a pleasant surprise!

Her outfit is very pretty, and she will interact with the accessories you use on her. If she cries, give her a bottle and she will make a drinking sound.

The only thing is that her head is very heavy - the heaviest part of her! So be careful or she will fall headfirst (even when in a sitting position). I have seen that will all of the Cry Babies dolls though, so that is nothing new. I just wish they were better proportioned, but she is still an amazing doll for all of the things she does. I am happy as long as she makes my kid happy.

title: She's so precious!
text:
This baby girl by Jizhi is precious! She is a smaller version of the Liam kit and she looks very realistic. If she was a bit bigger in size, she would be perfect. She is only about 18”, so she is not really the size of a toddler, even though she looks like a toddler. Still a cutie though!

Her hair was a bit messed up upon arrival, but my wife was able to fix it. Her outfit is too cute and she comes with a magnetic pacifier, birth certificate, accessories, diaper, and a bottle. Her accessories don't match her clothing too well. That is one recommendation is that it would be nice if the accessories were color coordinated with the doll's outfits.

Her body is cloth, and is slightly weighted. Her limbs are a soft vinyl. She would be great for both children and adult collectors to love!

title: Doesn't look like her photos, but still cute.
text:
This sleeping baby girl doesn't really look much like her photos. The first photo is a full body silicone baby done by an artist, so that is a bit misleading. The doll you get is not silicone, she is vinyl and is a manufactured doll. She is still cute, but doesn't look like the stock photos at all.

She is nicely painted though and does have some realistic features. Her hair is rooted and soft, but not as full as I would have liked it to be. Her legs are 3/4, so you can pose her to a sitting position. Her body is cloth, but not weighted and her limbs are soft vinyl.

This doll is more of a play doll than a collector's doll. She would be great for children to love though.

title: Wow! She is SO gorgeous!
text:
Wow! This doll is absolutely gorgeous! She looks so realistic and just like her photos. My wife is a doll collector and loves this sweet little girl!

She is perfectly painted from head to toe and has great details. Her hair is rooted so nicely! Rooted MUCH nicer than some other manufactured dolls. It is so full, and there are no bald spots. Her hair is also very soft.

She comes with a bag of accessories, a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate.

Her body is cloth, but not weighted. Her limbs are a soft vinyl.

She is a perfect doll at a perfect price. Highly recommend this sweet girl for both doll collectors and children!

title: Great for a first pet experience!
text:
This light up ant habitat is so neat! My 6 year old has been begging for a pet, so I decided to get this for her so she can start an ant farm.

It was very easy to set up, and looks really nice when lit up. We found some ants and put them inside. The big ants work best in this as we tried with smaller ants and they just died as I guess they were not strong enough to dig through the gel. The big ant was just having a blast in here! We haven't found a huge colony of big ants yet, but will keep on looking to put them in here so that they can explore.

The only thing that could make this better is if it were battery powered, which would make it portable. You have to plug this into a USB power source to keep it lit up.

title: Fun and easy!
text: These Pixobitz are so much fun! Both of my kids love them. The kit is huge and includes so many different colors and accessories. They are very easy to make as well. It makes a great art project at home!

title: Great Halloween prop!
text: These fake bloody hands are a great Halloween prop! They are rubber and look exactly as pictured. There is a lot of detail in these hands that makes them look realistic.

title: So many neat things in this set! Educational and fun!
text: [[VIDEOID:8370ddc28312cbd2657ea97d95be876]] This science kit is awesome! My kids love science, so this is the perfect summer activity. There are so many fun things to do in here. It comes with Earth and Mars, and you can dig in them to find surprises. Also, you get a volcano that you can paint, then erupt. There are so many neat things in this set. Both educational and fun!

title: Small containers and nice texture.
text: My kids like this Scentos scented dough. The texture is just like Play-Doh, but these have a scent. The scent is ok and it is not overpowering at all. Just wish there was more in the containers as they are so tiny.

title: She's gorgeous!
text: This 2022 Holiday Barbie is absolutely gorgeous! Her face is so pretty and her curls are beautiful. She is wearing an elegant red gown and the box she comes in is so nice. She would be perfect for a doll collector. My wife plans to keep her in the box as the box itself is too nice to open.

title: He looks SO REAL!
text:
This baby boy doll truly looks so real! He has so much detail put into him - blushing, mottling, veining and his hair is nicely rooted and looks like real baby's hair.

He is slightly weighted and has a cloth body. His limbs are vinyl and posable. He comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier and a bottle. The only weird thing is that the bottle and magnetic pacifier are pink. To me, this baby looks more of a boy rather than a girl, so they should have sent a blue bottle and a pacifier. Besides that small thing, this doll is perfect. He is so beautiful!

title: The cutest little silicone babies!
text:
[[VIDEOID:32a37aee1a8e64d57638dfe9d526c3c5]] This review is for 2 mini silicone babies: Joseph and Ethan. Both are extremely cute and a great value for the price!

My wife wanted these little silicone babies as she is a doll collector, but I kept little Joseph as my little buddy - He is too cool! His silicone is very soft and squishy and he has the cutest face!

Since their silicone is very delicate, I wouldn't recommend these dolls for little kids, only for adults or older children that show good responsibility of caring for their toys. If silicone isn't treated properly, then he may rip or tear.

Joseph is tiny, but fits perfectly into your hand and is so cute. He comes with a birth certificate, pacifier, pacifier clip, blanket, bottle, diaper, and a newborn hat. He is already wearing an adorable outfit too. The only downfall is that the outfit on him is not very easy to remove. It would be better if it was Velcro.

Ethan is super cute too! Love the crying expression on this little doll's face. His silicone is very soft and squishy just like Joseph's. The only odd thing about Ethan, is that he is anatomically correct and is for sure a boy, but arrived dressed like a baby girl wearing a purple romper and a pompom headband. The outfit is still cute though, even though it is for a girl. He is wrapped in a hospital blanket and comes with a birth certificate, pacifier, and a bottle.

You can see the silicone injection area on the top of their heads which is common for these dolls. They also have seams from the mold. That is not a big deal as this is common for silicone dolls. For the price, the quality of these dolls is amazing. Highly recommend!

title: OMG! He is soooo cute!
text:
OMG, this little guy by Jizhi is soooo adorable! He looks exactly like his pictures and is very realistic looking.

His hair is rooted and is very thick and full. He is wearing the sweetest little outfit and has blushing all over. His body is full vinyl from head to toe and he is anatomically correct.

He comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. His adorable outfit even comes with a matching hat. For being an all vinyl baby, his back is much better than some others that I have seen on dolls. He is about the size of a newborn and I think both kids and adults would love this guy.

title: This baby STINKS like CHEMICALS!
text:
My wife is a reborn collector and she thought this little girl looked so cute, so we ordered her. As soon as we opened up the bag that she came in we smelled a strong chemical odor that smelled almost like paint remover. The smell was so strong that it immediately gave my wife a headache. We immediately put this doll back in the box as she couldn't take the smell!

Her features are very realistic and her hair is rooted nicely. Her body is all vinyl and she is anatomically correct, but her back looks like it is concaved. Also, she is not weighted (the vinyl is hollow inside).

She comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate. Her outfit is really cute.

She does have a few good things about her, but we just can't get past the stink of her! For that reason, we can't recommend this doll.

title: Stunning doll!
text:
This 2022 Holiday Barbie is a stunning doll! She is so elegant and beautiful. Her gown is so pretty too!

She arrived packaged very nicely. Her primary box was packaged inside of a Mattel cardboard box, but her primary box was wrapped in tissue paper for extra protection.

My wife plans to keep this doll in her box as a collector's item. The box she comes in is too nice to open!

title: Wow, she is gorgeous!
text: This 2022 Brunette Holiday Barbie is gorgeous! She looks exactly like her photos and the box she comes in is so nice. She would make a perfect gift for a collector. Her hair is styled nicely and her dress is so pretty.

title: She is gorgeous! Great for a collector!
text: This 2022 Holiday Barbie is gorgeous! She is the classic Barbie with blonde hair and blue eyes and is wearing a beautiful holiday gown. She is packaged very nicely as well. She is in a cardboard box, but her box inside is wrapped in tissue paper for extra protection. This doll is great to have as a collector's item and I think any doll collector would love her!

title: Cute!! But the fabric is not the softest.
text:
These nightgowns are so cute!! They fit my 6 year old daughter perfectly. They also look exactly as pictured.

The only issue is that the fabric is not the softest, hopefully it will get softer after a few washes.

title: Fearless Bunny is so cute and so soft!
text: My kids love this Fearless Bunny! He is seriously so cute and grumpy looking with his eyebrows. He is extremely soft and perfect for cuddling. He even has pockets that you can put his hands into.

title: Great drone for the price!
text: This drone is great for the price! It is easy to use and comes with a extra replacement parts. It also comes in a very nice case. It is easy to use and my teenager loves it. It's easy to control with the included remote.
