You can download the app on your phone and once it is connected you can record live videos, however you must be quite skilled for using the app as it is a bit more difficult than the remote. Also, when it records video, there is no audio. It gives the option to use pre-loaded music from the app. Also, it doesn't do great in the wind, so I would use on a day when it is not that windy. It has quite a few cool features, but I will learn it all in time. It's definitely worth the price!

title: Noah is such an amazingly beautiful baby boy!
text:
Noah - The Down Syndrome Awareness Baby by Paradise Galleries is an amazingly beautiful doll! He has the most sweetest smile that will melt your heart and would be perfect for a doll collector to add to their collection. My wife just loves this little guy so much!

He smells just like a real baby and you notice the scent of baby powder as soon as you open the box. He smells so sweet and it just makes you want to snuggle him! His vinyl is scented and it is the soft touch vinyl, which is softer than the standard vinyl. His body is cloth and he is slightly weighted to give that feeling of a real baby.

His details are amazing and he is perfectly painted. His hair is so soft and is rooted. He has nice blushing too.

He also does stick out his tongue when you squeeze his cheeks - So neat! This is the first Paradise Galleries baby that I have seen with this feature.

One great thing to point out is that Paradise Galleries sent the overalls and hat in a separate bag with care instructions to wash before putting on Noah as the clothes may stain his vinyl. I love that they did this as a safety precaution! That is exactly what we did and now he has freshly laundered clothes and no stains.

Highly recommend this little guy as he is absolutely perfect!

title: She is very beautiful and big!
text:
This toddler doll is very beautiful and realistic looking. She doesn't look like the photos listed as that is a prototype doll. See the manufacturer's video for an accurate picture of this particular doll. For the price of this doll, I would say she is well worth it. Real reborns cost much more than this!

Her hair is nicely rooted and is a light brown color. She has beautiful blue eyes and a sweet facial expression. She is quite large and very chunky, however she is not weighted. Her limbs are hollow and her legs and arms do not pose, however I was able to place her into a sitting position.

She comes with her ears pierced, a cute hair barrette, plush bear, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate that you can fill out.

The vinyl on this doll is soft and is painted very nicely. She even has veining and mottling! The quality of this doll overall is amazing. Perfect for both collectors and children!

title: A beautiful doll at a bargain price!
text:
This baby girl Viola by Aori is so sweet! She is such a beautiful doll at a bargain price. She isn't as blushed as some other dolls, but she is still so adorable!

Her body is cloth and weighted and her soft vinyl limbs are 3/4 for easy posing. She comes with a plush teddy bear, blanket, magnetic pacifier, and a sippy cup. She also has a magenta colored headband that matches her outfit. Her outfit is soooo pretty and is nice quality!

Her hair is soft, but is a wig. Her eyes are a beautiful light shade of blue and she has the most adorable face. Perfect for both kids and adults!

title: She is beautiful! The pictures don't do her justice!
text:
This baby girl doll by Jizhi is even cuter than her photos! The pictures do not do her justice! She looks very realistic and her eyes are so beautiful! This is the first thing I noticed about this doll is that her eyes are amazing.

Her curly hair is a reddish brown color and is beautifully rooted and long. She comes with a bag of accessories, however I wouldn't recommend using that hair brush as it is plastic. It is better to use a soft bristled baby hair brush on her hair so that it doesn't get damaged. She also comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, birth certificate and instructions.

Her outfit is a pretty shade of mint green. It looks so pretty with her complexion. She is perfectly painted from head to toe and has blushing all over. Her limbs are posable (both arms and legs).

Her body is cloth and is slightly weighted to give that feeling of holding a real baby. This doll is just too sweet for words and anyone would adore her!

title: She is a gorgeous baby and looks very realistic!
text:
This baby Saskia by KSBD is gorgeous and looks very realistic. She is nicely painted with blushing, mottling, and veining all over to give that realistic look. She has the most adorable facial expression too!

She is wearing an adorable strawberry outfit and comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate. She also comes with a pretty white headband.

Her legs are 3/4 and are posable so that you can easily move her to a sitting position. Her arms are not posable.

Her head and limbs are soft vinyl, and her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. Her hair is rooted, but is a bit thin in some areas. It is not terrible, just not the best hair I have seen on these dolls. Her hair is a pretty shade of brown.

This doll is perfect for both children and adult doll collectors. She is very beautiful.

title: She is so pretty and looks just like her photos!
text:
This toddler girl doll by Jizhi is so pretty! She looks exactly like her pictures. She is bigger than I expected her to be and her limbs and head are posable.

She is packaged very nicely and comes with 2 blue bows for her hair, a magnetic pacifier, bottle, birth certificate, instructions, and a bag of accessories.

Her head and limbs are soft vinyl and her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. Her hair is brown and curly and is nicely rooted. Her hair is very full.

Her vinyl is nicely painted with blushing all over to give that realistic look. She has the bluest eyes and the most adorable smile with her 2 teeth showing!

Her dress is very pretty and reminds me of Dorothy from The Wizard of Oz.

This toddler girl doll looks very realistic and I think both adult collectors and children would adore her. She is nicely detailed and well worth the price.

title: He's a special little guy!
text:
This little baby boy by Jizhi is sooo cute! He is extra special as his one eye is different than the other. I am not sure if all of the dolls come like this, or if this is just a one off - But we still love him just as he is! It makes him more unique.

His features are very realistic and he almost has an angry look on his face which is so adorable. His hair is brown, curly, and rooted beautifully.

He has a cloth body, and a vinyl head and limbs. His body is not weighted, however his legs are posable to move into a sitting position.

He comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, matching hat, and a birth certificate. This guy could be loved by both children and adults!

title: She is stunning and perfect!
text:
This little baby girl by Aori is stunning! For the price, she is such an amazing doll. Her body is even weighted!

She has the most adorable expression on her face and does have blushing all over to give that realistic look. Her hair is rooted beautifully and is nice and full. Her hair is also very soft.

Her body is cloth and her head and limbs are soft vinyl. Her limbs are 3/4, so she is very easy to pose. She arrives in a beautiful outfit with a matching hat, a magnetic pacifier, blanket, stuffed teddy bear plush, a sippy cup, and a birth certificate that you can fill out.

She is perfect for both doll collectors and children. Found no flaws in this doll whatsoever… She was perfect.

title: Sooo cute and such a great deal for a beautiful baby!
text:
This baby girl by Aori is sooo cute! She is also a great deal as she is at an excellent price point.

Her details are realistic and her body is cloth and is weighted. Her head and limbs are made from soft vinyl (limbs are 3/4 and easy to pose). She is wearing the cutest little lady bug outfit and comes with a plush lady bug, birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, sippy cup, and a blanket. She is also wearing a matching headband and flip flops which coordinate perfectly with her lady bug outfit!

Her face is the cutest and her hair is rooted beautifully. Definitely recommend this little lady as she is so beautiful! You won't be disappointed!

title: He looks and feels just like a real baby!
text:
This full body silicone baby boy by Vollence is absolutely gorgeous! He looks and feels just like a real baby! He is painted very nicely and his silicone is very soft, floppy, and squishy.

He is very heavy and feels the weight of a real baby. You must pick him up and handle him carefully by always supporting his head just like a real baby or the silicone may tear.

This doll is perfect for a doll collector, but wouldn't recommend for a child as he needs to be handled with extra care.

He arrives packaged very nicely and wrapped in a plastic gift bag covered in hearts. He comes with a hat and an adorable little outfit and is wrapped in a swaddle blanket. He is not wearing a diaper, so he will need one. He is also anatomically correct.

He comes with magic juice and milk bottles as well as a pacifier. His mouth is closed, so he cannot take any of these in his mouth, but they are still very cool accessories to have.

Would recommend bathing him with gentle soap after receiving and adding some powder to him after to keep him from getting sticky.

All in all, this is one amazing looking realistic baby and you can't beat the price for a full body silicone baby.

title: She is absolutely gorgeous!
text:
This little baby girl doll by Milidool is absolutely gorgeous and looks exactly like her photos. Her facial features are so realistic and she arrives in the cutest little puppy dog outfit. She comes with a plush puppy, a blanket, a magnetic pacifier, a sippy cup, and a birth certificate.

Her hair is so full and is beautifully rooted. Her body is cloth and weighted. Her limbs are 3/4 vinyl. She is super easy to pose. The vinyl on the head and limbs is very soft. She is perfect for snuggling!

She is perfectly painted from head to toe. She is an amazing quality doll for the price. Perfect for both doll collectors and children.

title: She's even prettier in person!
text:
This little baby girl doll by Milidool is even prettier in person! For the price, this doll is a bargain and definitely worth it. She arrives packaged so nicely in a box, secured with ribbons. She is wearing the sweetest “Whoo's the cutest” outfit and even comes with an owl plushie, a sippy cup, a magnetic pacifier, birth certificate, and a blanket.

Her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. Her arms and legs are 3/4 vinyl and are posable. Her head is also vinyl. The vinyl is very soft to the touch. Her eyes are blue and so beautiful. She has the sweetest facial expression that will just make you melt. Her hair is beautiful, but is a wig. It is also soft to the touch.

This doll is just so beautiful all around, even more beautiful that I expected her to be. She is perfect for both doll collectors and children.

title: Such a beautiful and realistic baby girl!
text: This baby girl doll by Caranovo is very realistic looking and is so beautiful. Her hair is painted on and she has blushing and veining all over to add that realistic look. She has glossing over her eyes, nose, and mouth. Her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. Her arms are 3/4 and are posable. Her legs are full limbs and are not posable. She comes with a birth certificate, bottle, and a magnetic pacifier. She truly looks just like a real baby! She is so pretty and any doll collector or child would love her!

title: Perfect toy for a collector!
text: Monsters Inc. has always been a favorite movie in my family and I saw this Mike Wazowski and Celia Mae set, and had to get it! It comes in a nice box. I plan to keep it in the box as it is too nice to open and keeping it as a collector's item. The figures are quite large and look exactly like as pictured. Definitely worth the price! It is the perfect toy for a collector of Disney figurines!

title: A super fun activity with the kids!
text:
Surprisingly, both of my kids had fun with this Barbie Color reveal tie dye set! It comes with 3 colors to mix and match to add to the water and make the tie dye. This was the most fun part about it, and the tie dye outfits came out pretty neat. *Warning* It is messy, but it is fun!

You get 2 dolls with the set and each of them have a color reveal bathing suit. The dolls also have surprise designs when you place them in cold water. It was a lot of fun to watch the magic happen!

You get tons of blind bags full of so many surprises! It's a super cool Barbie set!

title: She is quite big and so pretty!
text:
This toddler doll by Jizhi is so pretty! She is quite big, bigger than I expected her to be and her limbs are posable.

Her facial features are very realistic and she is beautifully painted with blushing all over. Her hair is long and is rooted very nicely.

She comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, accessories, and a birth certificate. Her summery outfit is so pretty and is nice quality.

Her limbs are soft vinyl and her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. I think both doll collectors and children would love this sweet little lady.

title: Adorable realistic baby girl.
text:
This baby girl by Jizhi is so adorable! Her features are very realistic and her hair is beautifully rooted. She is perfectly painted from head to toe with blushing all over. Her facial expression is the cutest.

She comes with her cute outfit, a magnetic pacifier, bottle, accessories, and a birth certificate. She has a cloth body that is slightly weighted and her limbs are vinyl. She is posable so you can place her in a sitting position.

Such a sweet baby doll - Perfect for both collectors and children.

title: One BIG beautiful baby!
text:
This is one big and beautiful baby! It could be a boy or a girl and is even cuter in person. The head and limbs are vinyl and hollow inside and the body is cloth and slightly weighted.

This doll is nicely painted with blushing all over to add that realistic look. It comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, birth certificate, socks, pacifier clip, and a diaper.

The legs are posable so that you can easily put in a sitting position. The hair is rooted beautifully and is nice and full. This doll has such a sweet little face and would be perfect for both doll collectors and children. So cute!

title: She's sooo cute!
text:
This little sleeping smiling baby girl by Jizhi is soooo cute! She is wearing the cutest little outfit that comes with both a matching headband and hat. She also comes with a bag of accessories, a birth certificate, a bottle, and a magnetic pacifier.

She is perfectly painted from head to toe with just the right amount of blushing. Her head and limbs are vinyl and her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. She is not posable.

Her hair is beautifully rooted, but just a bit of an odd hair cut. You can't notice that much when she is wearing her hat or headband though.

She would be loved by both doll collectors and children.

title: A beautiful baby girl!
text:
This toddler doll by Jizhi is absolutely adorable. She is a such a beautiful baby girl! She looks exactly as pictured and actually looks and feels a bit bigger than 20”.

Her hair is beautifully rooted and her eyes are gorgeous. She is perfectly painted from head to toe with lots of blushing to add that realistic look.

She is wearing an adorable dress that would be perfect for Christmas. She comes with a bag of accessories, a magnetic pacifier, a bottle, and a birth certificate.

Her body is cloth and slightly weighted. Her limbs are a softer vinyl. She is posable.

Both collectors and children would love this sweet little girl!

title: Adorable, but hair is thin and eyelashes are too long.
text:
This Maddie doll by DCOLCO is an adorable looking realistic doll. She is not a real reborn, however is a more affordable option if you can't afford a true reborn doll.

She comes packaged in a box and arrives with her birth certificate, bottle, and magnetic pacifier. Her onesie is so pretty and also comes with matching bows for her hair.

One thing that my wife noticed is that her hair is very thin, almost to the point where it looks like she is balding (see photos). My wife will try to style her hair to where the balding is not so noticeable and hopefully this will help.

She is nicely painted from head to toe and has a lot of blushing to add that realistic look. Her eyelashes are extremely long though, too long for a baby. These may need to be trimmed.

Her body is cloth and not weighted. Her limbs and head are a softer vinyl. Her limbs are posable.

This doll would be perfect if her hair was rooted better and her eyelashes were shorter.

title: What a little beauty! More beautiful in person!
text:
My wife loves this little beauty by Jizhi! She is even more beautiful in person! She has blushing all over that gives a realistic look and the cutest little smile and eyes. Her outfit is so silky soft and so cute too!

She is slightly weighted and has a cloth body while her head and limbs are a softer vinyl. The vinyl is perfectly painted from head to toe. She looks so much like a real baby! FYI: Her limbs are not very posable.

Her hair is curly brown and is beautifully rooted. She comes with accessories, a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. She also has a beautiful laced bonnet that matches her outfit.

This little girl is such a sweetheart and perfect for both doll collectors and children.

title: She's adorable, but her hair is so thin!
text:
This realistic looking doll by Zique is adorable! She is so nicely painted and even has mottling and veining to make her look more realistic. She is not a true reborn, however is a more affordable option if you can't afford a true reborn.

She has pretty blue eyes and is wearing the cutest pink onesie and comes with a matching headband. She also comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle.

Her head and limbs are vinyl (a softer vinyl), and her body is cloth, however is not weighted. Her hair is rooted, however is very thin. If her hair was a bit thicker, this doll would have gotten 5 stars.

Her arms are full limbs and are not very posable. Her legs are 3/4 and are posable. You can eventually pose her arms, however it is difficult to work with them.

My wife loves this little lady and she is great for a collector or a child.

title: Perfect for science and learning!
text: My kids love this microscope. It is very well made, just like a high end microscope. You can look and learn about the included specimen slides, or even use your own specimen! My kids found bugs from the backyard and it was amazing to see them up close under the microscope! This is the perfect gift for science and learning!

title: It's awesome!
text: [[VIDEOID:1b8bf3bb265c006098bdccd1763161ba]] This Die-Cast model RV is awesome! The details on it are just like a real camper, and it comes with a bag of furniture to decorate the inside. The top and the side just pop right off so you can decorate easily. There are well detailed instructions which tell you exactly where each piece of furniture goes. Once done, you pull the strip on the bottom of the vehicle to enable the batteries and open the RV driver door and it lights up and plays music. Also, it is a pull back car too! My kids love it! It's perfect for kids or adults!

title: Tiny, but so nicely detailed. My daughter loves them!
text: These little sea animals are so tiny, but are nicely detailed and perfect for imaginative play. My daughter loves them!

title: Whoa! I love it! Amazing bang for your buck!
text:
I love Chucky and have been a fan since the 80's. This BendyFig Chucky doll looks just like the real Chucky!

The details on this little guy are just amazing. He comes with a base and you can bend and pose him into different positions.

He is an amazing collectible at a low price! I hope to get more of these BendyFigs in the future as they are too cool!

title: My daughter's absolute favorite plush!
text: If your kids love Poppy Playtime and PJ Pug a pillar, then you need to get them this toy! My daughter was ecstatic opening the package and PJ hasn't left her side since. He is soft enough to sleep with as well. He is soooo cute!

title: A very beautiful Barbie doll!
text: This Barbie Extra Fancy doll is very beautiful. The box she comes in is nice and she is wearing a fancy pink gown. She has beautiful gold jewelry and a pet that matches her dress. So cute! I think she would be great for both kids and Barbie collectors!

title: Colorful and fun, however wouldn't stand up like they did in the picture.
text: These magnetic butterflies are very colorful and fun. The only thing is that I can't get them to stand up as they did in the picture. It seems the base it too strong and it pulls the butterflies flat.

title: These are so much fun!
text: My kids love these magnetic fidget rings. You can play so many games with them and they are so much fun! Very nice quality all around.

title: She is a beautiful doll with nice details!
text:
This Maddie doll by DCOLCO is not a true reborn Maddie, but she is a great option if you can't afford a true reborn.

The details on this doll's vinyl are amazing. She has blushing, veining, and mottling. Incredible price for such a detailed baby.

There was one little flaw- Her eyelashes were all messed up on her one eye. My wife is hoping that this is something that she can fix. Her eyelashes are a bit long too, if they were shorter it would make the doll appear more realistic. Other than that she is perfect.

Her head and limbs are a soft vinyl and she does not feel hollow inside whatsoever. Her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. Her limbs are posable too. The legs are easy to pose, but the arms you have to work with them a little bit.

She comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate. Her outfit with the matching headband is so cute!

Her hair is blonde, curly and rooted beautifully.

This little doll would make a great gift for a child or an adult doll collector.

title: A beautiful baby girl at a great price.
text:
This baby girl by RSG is absolutely beautiful! She is a bargain at such a wonderful price too. She has the sweetest sleepy smile and she has blushing all over which makes her appear realistic. Her hair is painted on and is done very nicely.

She has vinyl head and limbs, and her body is cloth and slightly weighted. The outfit she comes in is adorable and she also comes with a matching headband, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate.

She would be perfect for a child or an adult collector.

title: OMG, this thing is hilarious!
text: This Mrs. Poop puppet is hilarious! It can fit both kids and adult sized hands in it and it is easy to use. It looks exactly like the picture and is nice quality. My kids love playing with this thing!

title: It's so funny! We love it!
text: [[VIDEOID:18ae320025928f0f80777b45ce07d5cd]] This dancing cactus is so funny and cool, we love it! It requires 3 x AA batteries (not included), and will dance to whatever sound it hears and repeat. It also lights up and looks pretty. See my video to see in action!

title: So soft and fun to squeeze!
text: These stress balls are so much fun! The texture is very soft and they are fun to squeeze. You get a rainbow, blue, and pink ball in the 3 pack. My kids love these things!

title: She looks very realistic and is so cute!
text:
This little girl by Jizhi is very realistic looking and is so cute! Her hair is beautifully rooted and very full. She has some light blushing on her body to give a more realistic look. She has the sweetest little face and smile.

Her body is cloth, but she is not weighted. Her head and limbs are vinyl and are hollow inside. This can be easily modified though.

Her outfit is super cute, and she comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, birth certificate, and a bunch of accessories. You can pose her into a sitting position as well.

Her eye lashes are a bit long for a baby, however these can also be trimmed. My wife loves this sweet little girl as she is just so beautiful!

title: He's so adorable!
text: My 6 year old daughter loves Clifford and she loves this plush toy of him! He is incredibly soft and so adorable! He has a collar that says  his name on it. Any Clifford fan would love this soft and sweet little guy.

title: It's like magic! The liquid really disappears!
text: These magic baby bottles are so neat! You get a bottle of milk and juice, when you tip them upside down the milk and juice disappears and when you turn them upright, the milk and juice comes back. You also get a pacifier for baby dolls with this set. This is perfect for imaginative play with baby dolls. So cute!

title: Perfect for a collector.
text: My teenager collects these cars and loves this Maserati! The details on this little car are amazing. It also makes cool sounds and has lights. The doors and trunk open just like a real car.

title: These tiny little sea animals are very detailed!
text: My daughter loves marine life and she so loves these sea animals! They are tiny, however they look so realistic and have a lot of detail put into them.

title: Awesome toy for a collector! Love it!
text: I have loved E.T. since it came out in the early 80's and I fell in love with this figure immediately! He is so cool as he comes with a base and he is posable. He is highly detailed and looks just like the real deal. It's perfect, and the price is great too! Hope to collect more of these BendyFigs in the future! They are so neat!!

title: So much fun!
text: This Stranger Things slingshot set is so much fun! It is nicely made and it is fun to play with! The instructions to say to crumble the papers into a ball, however if you fold the paper like I have in the picture, it is easier to shoot. My kids love this!

title: A beautiful Maddie doll on a budget.
text:
This doll is not a true reborn. She is a knockoff version of the Maddie doll and is a cheaper alternative to those who cannot afford a true reborn. She is quite beautiful though. Her details are realistic and her hair is full and beautifully rooted.

She has a cloth body and vinyl head and limbs. Her body is not weighted, however that could easily be modified.

She comes with a magnetic pacifier, accessories, bottle, and a birth certificate.

She is a smaller version of the Maddie doll, but still so adorable. She has the sweetest facial expression and her outfit is beautiful. I think both doll collectors and kids would love this doll.

title: My 6 year old loves this car!
text:
My 6 year old daughter absolutely loves this car! It can be used manually or you can use the electric mode. The electric mode doesn't go fast at all. It is a slower speed which I am sure was done for safety reasons. It doesn't have much power going up hill, but works perfect on flat surfaces or a downhill slope. The car is perfect for her size as well. For reference she is 48” tall.

It comes with a charger and the power button is located on the bottom. The assembly was pretty easy and the video on how to assemble included with the product description was very helpful as well. If you are struggling with the included instructions, then watch the video as it was much clearer in my opinion.

title: Sooo cute! But had a tiny hole at the tip of the fin.
text:
My daughter is a huge Orca fan and she loves this giant Orca plush! For the size, it is an incredible price. The Orca even has silver sparkles all throughout his body.

The only reason why I removed 1 star is that he arrived with a tiny hole at the tip of the fin. The area was missed when stitching. I had to repair it and now he is perfect.

title: The perfect Barbie gift.
text:
This Barbie camping set is so nice, and the added bonus with it is that you get 2 dolls with it! The dolls are beautiful and are wearing pretty outfits.

It also comes with a tent that is large enough to fit both dolls and more in there. It comes with a bunch of accessories, and animal friends too! The animals move when you push down on them, so that makes them even more fun!

The box it comes in is beautiful, and it would make a perfect gift for a Barbie fan.

title: Great set of figures!
text: My 6 year old daughter loves Turning Red and she was so excited over these little figures! They look exact to the characters in the movie!

title: Perfect Hawaiian party set!
text: This Hawaiian party set is perfect for a summer Hawaiian themed party! There is enough in this pack to cover 24 kids. You get a bunch of decorations and accessories in this set and they are nice quality - not cheap. Definitely recommend this set.

title: Wow, her details are absolutely amazing!
text:
My wife had previously ordered Ivy from Amazon using a different link, and noticed this was new so she wanted to compare the difference between the 2. In her opinion, this one is better.

The details on this doll are just amazing and make her look so realistic. She comes with her clothing in a separate bag, which is a great thing as the red outfit that my wife's other Ivy came in had stained her skin a pinkish/red color. My wife doesn't plan to put her in the outfit that she came in as she already has a stained Ivy and doesn't want this one stained as well. She plans to put her in a light colored outfit so that it won't stain her skin.

Her body is cloth and is slightly weighted. She is a big girl at 22” and comes in a big box. Her head and limbs are vinyl, and the details on the vinyl are just incredible. She has veining and mottling which make her look super realistic. If you can't afford a real reborn, this doll is a great option as she is affordable and really looks like a real reborn!

She comes with a birth certificate, bottle, and a magnetic pacifier. She fits in 0-3 month size clothing perfectly.

My wife loves this Ivy doll by Adolly, and the Adolly brand in general. The details on their dolls are just amazing for the price.

This little girl would be perfect for a child or a doll collector. She can be loved by all ages!

title: Beautiful and realistic looking baby girl.
text:
This baby girl is very realistic looking and beautiful. She has the most adorable smile on her face and her hair is rooted very nicely. Her outfit is so cute too!

Her body is full vinyl and she is anatomically correct. She is painted nicely and has veining details on her skin, which makes her look very realistic.

There is one weird thing that I have to call out though. I have seen this not just on this doll, but other full vinyl body dolls. Their backs are concaved!! It is a bit odd to see babies with concaved backs and not sure why, but all full vinyl body dolls appear to be like this. Not taking off any stars as it's not a defect, it's just how the doll is made.

Other than that 1 minor weird thing, she is absolutely perfect and a doll collector or a child would love her. She comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate that you can fill out.

title: Super cute set! So much fun to open!
text: My 6 year old loves this B Pack Reina Reef set! She is small, but such a beautiful doll with pretty hair. She comes with another outfit and a bunch of accessories and keychains! It was so much fun to open this toy as it had lots of blind bags!

title: He's soooo cute!
text:
This baby boy by Wooroy is soooo cute! He truly looks so realistic and his details are amazing.

His outfit is adorable, and he comes with a baby bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate.

His hair is rooted nicely and is soft to touch. His body is cloth, and his head and limbs are vinyl. His limbs are even posable!

He feels slightly weighted to give that realistic feeling of holding a real baby. He has the sweetest face ever too.

My wife is a doll collector and loves this precious little boy. He would make a great gift for both kids and adults.

title: What a gorgeous baby at a bargain price!
text:
This baby girl by Aori is gorgeous! My wife is a doll collector and loves her! This is the first doll she owns by Aori, but is very impressed with this brand.

She comes with a stuffed animal, a birth certificate, bottle, and magnetic pacifier. Her outfit is so cute too!

Her head and limbs are vinyl (lightly blushed), and her body is cloth and actually feels slightly weighted.

Her hair is nicely rooted and this baby has A LOT of hair! What a pleasant surprise! The description says “braids”, however her hair is not braided. It is just tied back in little ponytails with rubber bands, but my wife does love the hairstyle on her!

Her facial expression is so sweet and her details are very realistic. Her limbs are even posable! For the price, she is an amazing doll and I highly recommend.

title: She's so cute! Nice quality doll!
text:
This little baby girl by Milidool is so cute! She looks exactly as pictured, and she is amazing quality for the price. My wife loves the dolls by this brand as they are affordable, yet very nice quality!

She actually feels weighted. Some other dolls from Amazon are not, and this is another reason as to why my wife loves this brand.

She is perfectly painted and comes in her unicorn outfit and includes an adorable unicorn plush. She also comes with a magnetic pacifier, birth certificate, and bottle.

Her limbs are 3/4 vinyl and her body is cloth. Her hair is a wig, but it is soft. You can even pose her to sit or lay down.

She is such a cutie and any child or doll collector would love this sweet girl!

title: Beautiful doll, amazing quality and affordable.
text:
This little girl by Milidool is so adorable! My wife really loves the dolls from this company as they are affordable, yet such nice quality.

She comes with a plush cow and has a cow themed outfit that is so cute! She also comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle/cup.

Her limbs are 3/4 vinyl, and her body is cloth. She is perfectly painted from head to toe and has the sweetest facial expression. She actually feels like she has more weight compared to other realistic dolls sold on Amazon. This is another reason why my wife loves this brand.

She is such a beautiful doll, any child or doll collector would love this girl!

title: Such a cute little set!
text: This camping set is so cute! No dolls are included but you can use any type of doll or action figure with this set. The tent is nicely made and so pretty with it's cat ears! The campfire and lantern light up and batteries are already included. It is the perfect little set for imaginative play. The only part I disliked was removing it from the packaging, that was a bit of a struggle.

title: It was a nightmare to open this! The doll is so pretty though.
text:
Oh my gosh. Where do I start? This doll was securely, i mean SECURELY locked into this packaging that a car jacker could steal a car much faster than opening this doll from the package. It is the truth too! It was such a hassle just to get her out of the packaging. I have never seen a toy this secured to it's packaging before.

Now about the doll, she is so pretty! She has the prettiest face, and her tail changes colors in the cold and hot water. Her hair is long, pink, and beautiful. My daughter loves playing with her at bath time. She is a very nice toy, but the packaging could be improved.

title: Wow, she is absolutely beautiful!
text:
This sweet little baby girl by Jizhi is absolutely beautiful! Her skin is a bit lighter than the photos, however she is still beautiful.

Her hair is rooted beautifully and her head, arms, and legs, are vinyl while her body is cloth. She is not really weighted, but that is fine as this is something that can always be modified later on. The only thing that could have made her better is if her limbs were posable. I think her zip ties are too tight that you cannot pose her.

She comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, a bottle, and a bunch of accessories. Her outfit is so pretty and is silky soft. The headband itself looks a little cheap, but that is something that can be replaced. The doll itself is absolutely beautiful and so realistic. For this, she deserves 5 stars.

title: He's perfect!
text:
This little baby boy by Jizhi is so cute! He looks so realistic and his details are amazing. He even has veining in his head, which makes him look even more real. He is perfectly painted from head to toe. His hair is painted on as well.

He has a cloth body, and a vinyl head and limbs. He is not really weighted, but that is fine and is always something that can be fixed.

My wife thinks he is just perfect, and any doll collector would just love this sweet little guy! He is so precious!

title: Oh my! She has the sweetest little face!
text:
This baby girl is so precious! She has the sweetest little face and you will instantly fall in love with her. She is very nicely detailed and her features are so realistic!

Her body is cloth and her limbs and head are vinyl. Her hair is painted on, and her details are just amazing. She is not really weighted, but you can always modify her to add more weight if you wish.

She comes with a birth certificate, pacifier, bottle, and accessories. Her outfit is so cute too!

My wife is an adult doll collector and adores this little sleeping beauty! She is perfect!

title: Awesome little dinosaur!
text: This little dinosaur is awesome and looks exactly a pictured. He has realistic details and his mouth even opens and closes. My daughter loves this little dude!

title: They are so big and cool!
text: My 6 year old daughter loves these Spider-Man action figures! They are actually a lot bigger than what I was expecting, but that is a good thing. Perfect for a youngster to play with! So cool!

title: She's beautiful and so realistic looking.
text:
This baby by Charex is so realistic looking and is absolutely adorable. It could be either a girl or a boy as the outfit is gender neutral. My wife chose to make ours a girl.

She has a cloth body and vinyl head and limbs. Her hair is rooted nicely, and she is painted nicely. There was one minor thing off with the painting - The tip of this baby's nose has a white spot on it. She is not really weighted either, but you can always modify her later to add weight.

She comes with a birth certificate, a bottle, and a pacifier.

She is a beautiful baby, and looks so realistic. She would be a great gift for a child, or even an adult doll collector.

title: Short battery life and a bit pricey.
text:
[[VIDEOID:e8aae7ed53b167fbe8bd2192a0b5bce]] This bubble machine gun is nice, however there are a few things that could make it much better.

First of all, when you get the bubble machine gun, you need to charge for at least 3-4 hours. When using, it will only last for about 30 minutes before the battery starts dying. Then it will require another 3-4 hour charge. If the battery life was better, I would have gave this a better rating.

Another thing is that it is a bit pricey for a small timeframe of fun. It works well, but if it were about $20 cheaper, I would say that price would better fit this product.

Also, when you charge it, you need to unscrew the compartment. It comes with a mini screw driver, but this is a hassle to do every time, and then you have to put it back together again.

On the plus side, yes it does create a lot of bubbles. No, it doesn't come with bubble solution so you need to use your own.

title: This stuff is so neat! My kids love it!
text: This UV putty is a winner! Both of my kids love playing with this stuff! It comes with a mini UV light that you can use with it. The putty itself is not sticky whatsoever and has a very nice texture to it. You can mold it, and then draw on it. So neat!

title: They really do smell like s'mores!
text: My 6 year old daughter just loves these Whiffies! They are the cutest little creatures with big fluffy tails, and they smell so good! She loves the marshmallow scented one the best, but they also smell so good when you twist their tails together - Just like s'mores!  You may want to stay away if you are sensitive to strong scents.

title: It's purrfect for a young child.
text:
[[VIDEOID:91b61e43959ea12919420bec68827aa1]] This Purse Pet is so adorable! It requires 3 x AAA batteries (not included) and there is a button on the lower right side of the purse which activates the eye movement and sounds.

It is a small sized purse, purrfect for a child around the ages of 6-10 years old. Think it would be too small for a tween. The strap is long and your child can wear it as a cross body. It is seriously so cute!

The only downfall is the battery pack takes up a big portion of the inside of the bag, so the bag can only hold small items. Also, you will need a small flat head screw driver to install the batteries, luckily I had one handy!

title: Awesome set!
text:
[[VIDEOID:e322c3dea027103ceda99f3033d29b29]] This Batmobile is awesome! Just like a miniature version of the real deal. It comes with 3 x AAA batteries already installed, which is an added bonus.

It makes sounds and lights up. My teenager loves this as he collects superhero stuff. It also comes with a mini 4” Batman action figure. It's a very nice set for the price.

title: Tiny, but so cool.
text: This Batman 3 pack of mini action figures are tiny, but so cool. My teenager collects a bunch of superhero stuff, and he loves this set. The figures are posable and come with their own weapon which attaches to their hand.

title: Fun for the whole family.
text:
[[VIDEOID:c96b6a20051e54ca0245fbe7bad05159]] These are great stress balls and fun for the entire family. Once we opened the container, we couldn't stop squeezing them. They are so much fun!

The container that they come in is nice as well. You can keep them in here after you are done using.

I did notice a bit of an unpleasant smell similar to paint/rubber, however I am hoping that this is something that will go away in time. It's not a big deal as long as you don't have them near your face while using them.

title: It's a bit wrinkly, but my kids still love it.
text:
My kids love Among Us as well as Sonic the Hedgehog. This is a great idea mash up!

It arrives in a vacuum sealed bag, but it is a bit wrinkly after you take it out. Hoping that this is something that will go away in time. My kids love it and that is all that matters.

title: Super adorable!
text:
This Baby Alive Foodie Cuties pack is soooo adorable. This is the first I have seen of a Baby Alive mini series, but I hope so see more. My daughter just loves this set!

It comes in a cute little lunchbox type container, and inside you find blind bags filled with surprises!

You get an adorable baby, along with snack items, a bed with a mobile, and a high chair. The baby is posable, and looks just like the bigger Baby Alive dolls, but is a tiny version. Can't wait to get more of these!

title: Amazingly detailed, but she is not silicone -  She is vinyl.
text:
This baby girl by Jizhi is so adorable. She is probably the most detailed doll I have seen from the Jizhi brand. Her face is so pretty, and her eyes do look so realistic. Her hair is nicely rooted. There is great detail on her veining, and her painting is perfect from head to toe. No flaws whatsoever.

The only thing that could be changed is her description - It says she is silicone, however she is not, she has a vinyl head and limbs, and her body is cloth. She is not weighted, however her limbs are posable. Her little outfit is so adorable, and she comes with a birth certificate, bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a bunch of accessories.

Highly recommend this little girl as any doll collector would love her!

title: So much fun to hatch, and they are so cute!
text:
My daughter loves this Hatchimal CollEGGtibles Unicorn set. The container it comes in is so pretty, and a great case to store your Hatchimals in.

The bigger unicorns are not in eggs, but are so pretty. The babies are in the eggs and are so tiny and cute. These are a lot of fun to hatch.

title: Super cool, but a bit pricey for just 1.
text:
This Bakugan is neat. They are a bit pricey for 1, but they are so cool. My teenager has loved Bakugans for years.

This set includes 1 Bakugan, 2 BakuCores, a character card, and a gate card.

title: It's a lot of fun to hatch.
text: The most fun thing about this Hatchimal toy is hatching the giant egg! My daughter loved it. The toys inside are super tiny, but so cute. You get 4 tiny Hatchimals and 2 accessories with this set. The egg even transforms into a little playset. So cute.

title: A bit creepy, but so cute.
text: This little Zombaes Forever doll is super cute. She is tiny, but so adorable! She comes in a little coffin, and she comes with a stand, a dress, and a crown. Her hair also comes off, where you can see her brain. It's creepy, but I love the idea.

title: The most adorable change purse ever.
text: My daughter loves this tiny purse! It is more like a little change purse due to it being so tiny. It looks like a bat, and when you zip and unzip it, the eyes roll back and forth. So cute!

title: Very nicely detailed.
text: This concrete truck is very nicely detailed. My kids love these diecast cars! There are no sounds to it, however the cement barrel easily spins by hand, as well as the wheels. The doors don't open either, that is the only thing that could make it better!

title: She's so perfect! Even more beautiful in person!
text:
My wife has been begging me for this doll by Ashton Drake, and she absolutely loves her! She is even more beautiful in person!

Her eyes are extremely realistic - They are a blue with brown inside. Her smile is priceless! Her hair is SO soft and silky! It is blonde, but there are pieces of red in it. So pretty!

She is wearing a little Dutch dress, which is so cute. She is also wearing bloomers, an undershirt, frilly socks, pink shoes with flowers, and adorable hair ties that match her dress. She comes with a certificate of authenticity and a tag.

She is even taller than we expected her to be. She wears 18-24 size months clothes, and size 7 toddler shoes. My wife has already redressed her and she looks so adorable in other outfits.

Her knees are jointed and posable. Her head is posable, as well as her arms go up and down. She can sit and stand. Her body is full vinyl from head to toe.

She is a fine quality art doll recommended for ages 14+, but any doll collector would truly adore this sweet beauty! My wife loves her to pieces! Get her! You won't regret it!

title: She's very cute, but has a few small flaws.
text:
This baby girl by Jizhi is adorable, however there were just a few small flaws with her.

1.) Her eyelashes are way too long! It looks like this baby girl is wearing false eyelashes with tons of mascara. Eek!

2.) She has a white dot on the tip of her nose. I am sure this was just a mishap with the painting, and hopefully the others won't be like this.

Overall, I still think she is very cute. Her limbs were actually posable so that she could sit. Her body is cloth, and her limbs and head are vinyl. She is hollow inside and not weighted. Her hair is very pretty too.

She comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and accessories. The magnetic pacifier stays on well with no issues. Her outfit is very pretty too. I think anyone would love this little girl.

title: It's a money trap
text:
My kids love Bakugan, and this arena is neat… However, it only comes with 1 Bakugan, and you can't do anything with just one. The arena is useless without more than 1. That is why it is a money trap.

Luckily, I found some of my son's Bakugans from a few years ago, and we were able to use these in the arena. It is a lot of fun. The set also came with cards.

title: So neat and fun to unbox!
text:
I haven't seen a toy like this before, but it is for sure cool! The Zombaes are like little horror dolls, which is right up my alley!

They come in a coffin box, and you can even see their glittery brains. They even had a little surprise pet come in it's own coffin. Super cool!

title: Adorable little set!
text: My daughter loves Cry Babies, and this set is absolutely adorable! Rose actually smells like roses, and she comes with her bike cart and a bunch of other accessories. It even comes with powders and glitter to where you can create your own perfumes, however this can be a tad bit messy. The main flower also lights up, which is neat. It's a super cute toy!

title: He's very detailed and totally cool!
text:
[[VIDEOID:2ba551aeb1248e11e61093ff562a4e44]] Wow! This Batman action figure is even cooler than I imagined. He is very detailed and stands pretty tall at 12”. He looks just like Batman in the movie.

He also says different phrases and makes different sounds when you push the button on his chest. Batteries are already included too, so that is an added bonus.

The box that he comes in is very nice, my son insisted on keeping it as it was too nice to throw in the trash.

title: Pretty awesome action figure for the price.
text: This Selina Kyle action figure is very nice for the price. I was expecting a lower budget action figure, but she is pretty awesome! My teenager collects different action figures and loves it.

title: Smells sweet and soooo cute!
text:
We love the Happy Flowers by Cry Babies! This has to be the best out of all of the mini Cry Babies yet!

I love the capsule that it comes in, it is filled with fake cotton candy and looks so pretty. You get to unravel the cotton candy which will lead you to your mystery baby.

The first thing I noticed, is that the cotton candy actually smells sweet! So does the baby! It so unique to add scents to these.

The next thing is the flower pot that it comes in is so cool! You can actually grow and re-grow your flowers over and over, by spinning the flower on the front of the pot. The baby fits perfectly in the pot to display afterwards.

The baby comes with a bunch of different accessories, and you can fill up her water bottle which will lead to her magic tears coming out.

My 6 year old loves it! We hope to get the entire collection!

title: A perfect sleeping angel. Love her!
text:
Sleeping Kitten by Paradise Galleries is so sweet! She is the size of a real newborn and is slightly weighted to give that feeling of holding a real baby.

Her rooted mohair is incredibly soft, and she is perfectly painted from head to toe. Her little outfit is so cute and she comes in a little sleep sack. Also, in the box is her Certificate of Authenticity.

Her vinyl is unscented gentle touch vinyl, so she is not as soft as some of the other Paradise Galleries' dolls.

She looks very realistic and is a perfect sleeping angel!

Any doll collector would adore her. My wife loves this little one!

title: Almost just like the original back in the day!
text: My teenager grew up loving Toy Story as a youngster, and Woody and Buzz were his favorites. I got this as a keepsake gift for him and he loves it! It is almost just like the original Woody doll he had when he was 5 years old, except it is slightly smaller, and he says some different phrases. Some of the phrases sound like Tom Hanks, however some are close but no cigar. Still cool though!

title: She's beautiful - Minor flaw in the wig.
text:
My Little Marisol is absolutely adorable. She has the sweetest little smirk! Her eyes are beautiful and are a greyish/brown color. She comes all dressed in her winter ensemble, that includes a hat and a scarf. Her outfit is perfect for the cold weather. The fabric is very soft and cozy!

Her body is cloth, and her face and limbs are gentle touch (unscented) vinyl. Her cloth body is slightly weighted to give that feel of holding a real baby. Her vinyl is harder than some of the other Paradise Galleries' dolls.

The only thing that I could care less about is the wig. There is a sharp point on the wig on the back of her head. I don't think this is something that can be fixed either as it would mess with the integrity of the wig/doll. If I hold her like a real baby, it pokes right into my arm… So most likely she will keep the hat on her head at all times to prevent me from being poked! I am hoping that the wig issue on the doll that I received was just a 1 time fluke.

My wife is a doll collector and really appreciates this sweet baby's beauty! I think any doll collector would adore and cherish her.

title: Kid approved!
text: [[VIDEOID:5f7eada790316484914215e01243b267]] My teenager loves this Nerf gun! He has loved these things all his life, but this is the coolest one yet. It shoots so fast and has a good range. It is very easy to operate too. It comes with 40 squishy balls, but we tried with them all inside the gun, and it wouldn't fire as it was overfilled. We took about 10 out and it worked perfectly! It's so much fun!

title: No action figures included
text:
The main description of this toy is “Masters of the Universe He-Man and The Chaos Snake Attack Playset, Skeletor Fortress with 2 Action Figures (He-Man & Skeletor)”, so it leads you to believe that you get 2 action figures included. If you look at the fine print on the box, you can see that no action figures are included. The detailed product description down below also tells you this, however the main description should be changed as it is misleading.

Now to the toy, it is easy to assemble. There are 2 modes for the snake, “hero” or “villain”. The hero mode lets you attack the snake and it will fall down and the action figure in the throne will also fall down. In the villain mode, you need to open the snake's mouth so it stays open, and when the figure touches the mouth, the snakes mouth will close on it.

It would be cooler if you could control the mouth of the snake to open and close as you wish. It's a neat toy, but still nothing compared to the original He-Man toys back in the day.

title: Awesome little car!
text:
My teenage son loves these metal Die Cast vehicles! Especially this one! It is very detailed and all of the doors, back, and hood open up.

It comes with batteries already included and it makes sounds and lights up. The button is difficult to find (but it is on the front left side of the hood, when looking at the vehicle from the front). It is amazing quality for the price!

title: So many puffy stickers for an excellent price
text: Wow!! These puffy stickers are so adorable, colorful, and easy to stick. You get 10 sheets total, that are loaded with all different stickers. They are really nice for the price.

title: Great quality and so much fun!
text: My kids love these yoyo toys! They are soft, squishy, and have the cutest designs. They are perfect to keep children busy, and even small enough to fit inside plastic Easter eggs. These are even fun for adults to use!

title: Such a neat little car!
text: This alloy collectible Rolls Royce car is so neat! My daughter loves that it is pink too! These cars are great for both kids and adults. The details put into the car are amazing and the doors open and close, as well as the hood and the trunk. It even has lights and sounds!

title: OMG! It's so much fun!
text:
This wireless microphone is so much fun! It is perfect for a child to hold and has the cutest design.

It comes with a USB charger and doesn't take long to get to a full charge. There are different modes, and my daughter loves the echo feature.

You can even use this a a Bluetooth speaker! So neat!

title: So much detail! I love it!
text: This Rolls Royce car is awesome for the price. I cannot believe the amount of detail put into this little car! All of the doors, hood, and trunk open, and it has lights and sounds. It's so neat!

title: Detailed, but are not soft rubber.
text:
These dinosaur puppets are very detailed and they work well on small child hands, however they won't fit adult hands.

When I read the description, it said they were made of soft rubber material. I was thinking it would be similar to the shark hand puppets that they sell at Wal-Mart, but these are not that super soft rubber/silicone that I thought they would be. They are more of a tough rubber, and don't form to your hands.

title: She's very cute, but not weighted.
text:
This baby girl by Jizhi is so cute! The first thing I noticed about her was her sweet facial expression. It is so precious!

She has long curly hair, and is comes with a bonnet that ties under her chin. Her outfit looks very vintage/old fashioned and is just adorable.

She comes with a bunch of different accessories and a birth certificate.

Her head, hands, arms, legs, and feet are hollow vinyl, and her body is cloth. The only disappointment is that her body is not weighted, so she doesn't have that realistic feel. Her facial features do look realistic though.

I still think any child or doll collector would love this little girl!

title: Cute… But overpriced.
text:
My 5 year old daughter is obsessed with Love Diana on YouTube, so I had to order these for her.

What is fun about them is that you get 4 surprise Dianimals in this set. That is the most fun part of this toy… The surprise element.

Inside each mini backpack is a tiny stuffed animal. There is a collector's guide included that will tell you the name of the animal and if it is a common, rare, or ultra rare. The ones we got are common.

These are fun to open, however the price is too high for 4 tiny stuffed animals. If these were more reasonably priced, we would probably get more.

title: So detailed! Great for a collector!
text: I love this Die-Cast Model Rolls Royce car! It's great for a collector, and I cannot believe the detail put into this car for the price. It is magnificent! Highly recommend if you collect these type of cars!

title: It's a blast from the past!
text:
This costume is a blast from the past! My wife had so much fun wearing this costume. It is totally 80's! It comes with a bunch of accessories, such as earrings, bracelets, necklaces, a headband, wig caps, the wig, and the outfit itself.

The fit is true to size and the quality is amazing. The wig is so funny! My wife can't wait to wear this for next Halloween!

title: So so cute!
text: This Sugar Puff Bee doll is so cute! She is wearing the cutest outfit, has the sweetest facial expression, and her hair so so curly cute! She's a perfect little friend for my daughter to play with.

title: A mix between a train and a rollercoaster! Love it!
text:
[[VIDEOID:42ab468d07e9bdcb52a27c164eb34fc8]] This train set is so much fun! What is neat about it is that it is a mix between a train and a rollercoaster. The track was easy to set up and the train takes 4 x AAA batteries (not included). There is a button on the engine that turns it on and just watch it go!

The only bummer is that at first the train played cute music and sounds when going around the track. Once we turned it off and back on again, the music and sounds were no longer there. No biggie though, it is still super fun!

My kids love watching this go around the track. It is actually quite BIG too! Bigger than what I was expecting. It's an amazing toy for the price. Watch my video to see the train in action!

I hope that you found this review helpful!

title: She's so beautiful! A doll collector's dream!
text:
Birthday Wishes Barbie is just beautiful! My wife loves her as she is a doll collector. She plans to keep her in the box, as the box is too pretty to throw away.

Barbie's dress is so pretty, and her face is gorgeous. My wife likes her better than last year's version of this doll.

Any doll collector or a child who loves dolls would appreciate the beauty of this doll!

title: He's absolutely adorable and smells good!
text:
Peek-A-Boo! By Paradise Galleries is the most adorable little boy doll! My wife loves Paradise Galleries dolls and they never seem to let down. Their dolls are always of amazing quality.

The first thing that you notice about this sweet little guy is how amazing he smells - He has a sweet baby powder scent to his skin. He smells SOOOO GOOD! His head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are soft touch vinyl and his body is cloth and weighted.

He has the most adorable realistic looking eyes, and his hair is rooted mohair and very soft to touch. He comes with 2 outfits. He is wearing a teddy bear outfit, but also comes with a glow in the dark skeleton Halloween outfit. Both outfits are just so cute!

He also comes with a magnetic pacifier and a certificate of authenticity. I think any doll collector would absolutely fall in love with this little boy!

title: The Boglins are BACK! Yay!
text: I was so excited to see that the Boglins are back! I remember these from the 80's and now it's like a nostalgia dream come true. The new version of the Boglins allow you to control both the eyes and the mouth, whereas the vintage version only allowed you to control the mouth. So neat!

title: The Boglins are back! And more improved!
text: I was so excited to see that the Boglins are back! It literally takes me back to the 80's, however these Boglins do much more than the ones did back in the day. You can control the eyes and mouth like a puppet, whereas the 80's version you could only move the mouth (from what I remember).

title: The Boglins are BACK!
text: I was so excited to see that the Boglins are back! My wife and I loved these toys back in the day! They do more than the old ones used to as well. You can move their eyes and mouths like a puppet. So neat!

title: An affordable and adorable Maddie doll!
text:
This little Maddie doll by Charex is such a cutie pie! For the price, the doll is amazing! She is not a true reborn as she is a mass produced doll, however she is a much more affordable option.

Her head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are soft vinyl and her body is cloth. Her body is not really weighted, however It is easy to pop her limbs off and on so that you can make her weighted if you wanted to. She is filled with polyfill stuffing.

My wife is a doll collector and really fell in love with this sweet girl. What is nice about this doll is that her limbs are posable too. Just be careful as they may pop off. My wife was posing her and her leg popped off, however it is easy to pop it right back on.

The doll's outfit and headband are so adorable. Her hair is brown and is actually rooted. She comes with a birth certificate, bottle, and magnetic pacifier that stays on well without falling off. For the price of this doll, the quality is amazing.

title: She's beautiful, but not scented at all.
text:
Rainbow Ballerina by Paradise Galleries is such a beautiful doll. Her features are so realistic looking. She comes with a Certificate of Authenticity and her outfit and headband are so pretty!

The description says that she is scented, but she is not scented. Most of the Paradise Galleries dolls do have a baby powder scent, however this one is Gentle Touch vinyl (not soft touch vinyl) and there is no scent at all. The vinyl is a bit harder than the soft touch vinyl from Paradise Galleries. Her body is cloth and she has a decent weight to her.

She has the sweetest little wrinkles on her face, and her fingers and toes are perfectly painted. I think any doll collector would adore this sweetie!

title: She is cute, but has some flaws.
text:
This doll by Jizhi is not a true reborn as it is not a one of a kind doll by an artist. It is a realistic looking baby doll with lifelike features.

She is super cute in her Christmas outfit and she is great for a doll collector. She has a precious smile and her hands and feet are perfectly painted.

Her body is all vinyl, her abdomen area feels sort of “flat”. One thing that was odd is that they did not put a diaper on this doll. Warning: She is anatomically correct. I am not sure why they would not put a diaper on a doll like this.

Also, her hair is curly and a bit out of control. I put some gel in it to calm it down some, but she also comes with a brush (a regular plastic doll brush). I would not recommend using this brush on this doll's hair as it will pull it right out and she will be bald in no time! Instead I would use a soft bristled baby hairbrush.

She comes with a pink magnetic pacifier (not sure why pink? As it doesn't match her outfit), a birth certificate, and some other feeding accessories for pretend.

While this doll is very cute, there are just a few things that could have been modified to make her perfect.

title: So much fun and they have a lot of detail!
text:
These Boley dinosaur cars are awesome for the price. They are quite nicely detailed, and are a good size. They are friction powered, which is neat as they don't require batteries.

You get 4 in the set: A Tyrannosaurus Rex, a Triceratops, a Rhinoceros, and a Great White Shark. These are so nice, my kids love them!

title: Engaging, educational, and fun!
text: This STEM construction set is very educational, engaging, and fun! Both of my kids loved playing with this. The instructions are easy to follow and you can put together 5 vehicles OR combine all into a robot! The robot makes sounds which is neat, and it already includes batteries which is an added bonus. It's a perfect activity for a rainy day!

title: Fun indoor activity for all ages!
text:
Both of my kids love this dinosaur car painting set. You get a total of 6 pull back cars, 2 brushes, 2 sets of paint, a paint tray, and dinosaur cards. This activity is fun for all ages, as both my 5 year old and 16 year old had a blast with this set.

The paint dries fairly quick and the cars are nice quality as well. The paint is a big of a struggle to open for a child though, so it will require adult assistance.

title: The scent is light - which is GOOD!
text:
I ordered these Hot Tamales markers for my kids as they love drawing and they also love Hot Tamales candy!

The scent is not overpowering at all, it's very light to the point where you are sitting right next to your child, you can't smell it. This is great for people who are sensitive to strong scents. They write very nice and you get 8 different colors in the pack.

title: Educational and so much fun!
text: We love Channie's Sentence Builder Puzzles! This idea is very educational and so much fun! It comes with a bunch of different puzzle pieces that have words and pictures on them. Your little one can trace the letters to learn how to spell and write. You can attach the puzzle pieces to each other to make sentences. It comes with a black dry erase marker with an attached eraser, so you can write on the puzzle pieces and then make a whole new puzzle over and over!

title: He's so realistic looking and smells so good!
text:
Dino Darling by Paradise Galleries is the sweetest little baby boy doll. He is truly so realistic looking and is painted perfectly.

His head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are soft touch vinyl which has the scent of baby powder (He smells so good)! His body is cloth, and weighted.

He comes with a pacifier (not magnetic, it actually fits right into his mouth). He also comes with a hat, dinosaur blanket, booties, and a Certificate of Authenticity.

His hair is long and blonde. It is rooted. His eyes are big and blue. He has the cutest little facial expression.

He is so handsome and a doll collector would absolutely adore this sweet little boy!

title: She looks like a baby Snow White! So cute!
text:
Kayo Hana is such an adorable little girl. My wife adores her as she is a doll collector. She actually said that she reminds her of Snow White with the way her hair is styled.

Her outfit is so super cute. She is wearing a polka dot dress romper with a floral cardigan over it. Her hair is a wig (not rooted), but is soft to touch. Her body is cloth and weighted. Her hands, arms, feet, legs, and head are soft touch vinyl, which actually smells like baby powder - so good!

She is wearing an adorable little headband as well. She is the first of all Paradise Galleries dolls that my wife has that doesn't come with a magnetic pacifier, but that is fine as she is just beautiful the way she is.

She does come packaged nicely in her box with a Certificate of Authenticity.

title: Nicely detailed
text: This alien madball is a great collector's item. It is painted nicely and detailed. It is foam, and a hard texture. It's not the same as the 80's madballs, but it's close.

title: Amazingly detailed!
text: This Pennywise madball is amazing. It's a great collectors item and the detail on it is out of this world. Perfect for any horror fan!

title: It's so funny! Love it!
text:
[[VIDEOID:b17082c48fa781eb33700938bae85d4b]] This twerking Santa is the funniest thing! I didn't even know what to expect with this, but honestly I couldn't stop laughing watching it twerk!

It requires 3 AA batteries (not included), and he has an on/off switch on his back. He will stay on until you actually turn him off.

This little guy will surely brighten up your holidays!

title: Perfect for birthday traditions!
text:
My kids love the elf on the shelf. Happy the bird is like the elf on the shelf but on your birthday instead of Christmas! 🥳

Happy is so cute and comes in a nice box with a book that features him. The book is a lot of fun to read. This will definitely be a new birthday tradition for my daughter!! 🥰

title: It's a hit! Fantastic toy!
text:
This Peppa Pig RV set is adorable! My daughter loves Peppa Pig and campers, so this is a match made in heaven. 🥰

You can use as a camper or fold out as a play set. If you touch the horn it plays music 🎵, and it comes with batteries already. It comes with all 4 characters and a bunch of accessories. Fantastic toy!

title: Super funny and engaging!
text:
This is a great indoor game for kids! My 5 year old daughter kept seeing commercials of this game and has been asking for it. It is so funny and keeps her highly engaged.

You can play with 2-4 players and the Gobble Monster is easy to assemble. He requires 3 x AAA batteries (not included). When you are ready to start playing, you set the toys on his tongue and lightly push his tail. The key is to be sneaky so that he doesn't gobble up the toys. The player with the most toys collected at the end of the game wins.

This game is fun for both kids and adults! It also comes with a 24 piece puzzle!

title: So adorable and so interactive!
text:
[[VIDEOID:ffc529855eeaed037261524e9ac07724]] Peek-A-Roo is so so adorable! My 5 year old daughter just loves her! Mama comes with a mystery baby in her pouch that you can see wiggle and then the baby will reveal itself! I haven't seen a toy like this before, but it is so cute!

Once the baby is born, Mama and baby can sing together and play games. It's so interactive and would make the perfect Christmas or birthday gift for your child.

Added bonus: Batteries are already included!

title: Super nice art set!
text:
This art set is so nice for the price! You get a lot in the package. It includes 16 crayons, 16 washable chubby markers, scissors, 8 watercolors with a tray and a brush, a glue stick, and 50 sheets of white construction paper.

Everything in it is great quality. It's perfect for school, or even at home! My kids love drawing and painting, so I am keeping this set home for them.

title: Nice quality game, but the holes are cut small.
text: I have loved playing Mancala for many years. I was so excited to see this game on here to play with my kids. It is nice quality and lots of fun. The only thing that could have been improved on is the size of the holes, they are too small and that makes it a bit difficult for an adult to play.

title: The cutest musical book!
text: [[VIDEOID:203f74e6b6219188169a8536857ddf22]] This Ditty Bird musical book is so cute! It is all about different careers and has songs for each. Just turn it on and push the button on each page and it plays an adorable little song. This book is so great for children learning about all the different careers out there. The animation is so cute too!

title: So adorable, but not really weighted.
text:
This little boy by Charex is so adorable! He looks so realistic and is perfectly painted. His little outfit is so cute and he comes with socks and a hat. He also comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle.

His hair is a wig, and his body is not posable. The description says he is weighted, but he is not really weighted at all. He is light as a feather.

My wife is a doll collector and loves how well he is painted and how lifelike he is. I think anyone would love to receive this guy for a gift. He is nice for the price, but there are better dolls out there.

title: Works great with adult assistance!
text:
I was so excited to see that Creepy Crawlers are back! These take me down memory lane and they are just like I remember!

The instructions are easy to follow, however the molds are super tight, so it will require some adult assistance as it was a bit tough to snap and unsnap.

You get 2 different molds: a spider and a centipede, and you can make in orange or green. Once they are done, they are a bunch of jiggly fun! Just be careful with them though as they may rip if not treated correctly.

title: The camper is huge, however feels a bit flimsy.
text:
This Simba Steffi Love Hawaii Camper is huge. It arrives in a giant box and is definitely bigger than I expected it to be. It is packaged nicely and super childproofed as well!

It includes a bunch of accessories, even the doll herself, furniture, and stickers to decorate. You get a lot in this set.

The only downfall is that I don't know how long it will last with my 5 year old. She likes to play rough and the camper itself feels a little flimsy, but only time will tell!

Due to the flimsiness of it, I would say it is a bit overpriced for the quality of the product. But overall, still a lot of fun.

title: So adorable!
text:
Emerson the Wellie Wisher doll by American Girl is adorable. She is a spotlight girl and loves unicorns! My daughter absolutely loves this doll.

Wellie Wisher dolls are much smaller than the standard American Girl dolls, however are much more affordable as well.

She is a beautiful doll in her pink and purple outfit with boots, and she also comes with a unicorn headband.

She has beautiful dark brown eyes and black hair in bun pigtails.

She is well articulated and you can move her head, arms, and legs. She can sit and stand well.

Emerson would make a perfect gift for a child who loves unicorns.

title: Super cute!
text:
Willa the Wellie Wisher doll by American girl is super cute! She is a nature girl and loves her outdoors.

She is wearing a fairy dress and has ladybug boots. She comes with a leaf headband. Of all of the Wellie Wishers, Willa is my daughter's favorite.

She has adorable strawberry blonde hair and a face full of freckles. She is well articulated and you can move her head, arms, and legs. She can sit and stand well.

She is a beautiful doll and would make a great gift for a nature loving child!

title: A perfect princess
text:
Ashlyn the Wellie Wisher doll by American girl is a perfect princess! My 5 year old daughter absolutely adores her.

The Wellie Wisher dolls are much smaller than the standard American Girl dolls, however are a more affordable option.

Ashlyn comes packaged in a nice box and is wearing an adorable pink princess dress and pink boots. She also comes with a pink crown headband.

She is well articulated and you can move her head, arms, and legs. She can sit or stand well.

She would make the perfect gift for a perfect princess.

title: She's adorable and love the clothes!
text:
Camille the Wellie Wisher by American Girl is so cute! The Wellie Wishers are much smaller than the standard American Girl dolls, however are much more affordable.

My daughter absolutely loves Camille. She has an adorable mermaid outfit and fish boots. She also comes with a sea shell headband.

She is well articulated and you can move her head, arms, and legs. She can sit or stand.

She has beautiful blue eyes and gorgeous blond hair that is very soft. She has a birth mark right below her eye.

If your little girl loves American Girl and you are looking for a cheaper option, these Wellie Wishers would make a great gift.

title: She is not posable and doesn't look as realistic in person.
text:
This baby girl doll by GOAROY is cute, however she is not a real reborn doll. A reborn is one of a kind and this doll is mass produced.

She also doesn't look as realistic as her stock photos. Her body also is not posable. The stock photos show that she is posed in different positions, but her body and joints are stiff. This is a bit misleading.

She has the sweetest little face and her hair is nice. The hair is a wig, but is nice and full. Her body is cloth, and her head and limbs are soft vinyl. She has some light blushing on her, which is not overbearing at all.

The outfit is adorable and she comes packaged in a nice box which includes her birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle.

This doll is more suitable for a child, rather than a collector. She is cute, however just reminds me more of a regular baby doll than a reborn.

title: Magic water art with no mess!
text:
[[VIDEOID:c04a509c10777ad0e0be3f2d45998a12]] My favorite type of art is one with no mess, and that is why these are awesome! You get 2 spiral books in the pack - 1 is the ABC's and the other is transportation. Each comes with a refillable water pen. Just fill up and give to your little and let them doodle away.

The water makes magic and the letters and designs change color. There are even hidden surprises behind the letters, which was so exciting for my 5 year old. It's educational and fun at the same time. The best part is, once it dries, you can do it all over again!

title: So realistic and absolutely adorable.
text:
This Maddie doll by DCOLCO is absolutely adorable. She is not a true reborn as she is not a 1 of a kind by a reborn artist, but she is much more affordable alternative.

She looks so realistic and has the sweetest little face. Her limbs are posable too! Her body is cloth and her head and limbs are soft vinyl.

She is dressed in an adorable pink onesie and includes a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and bottle. The magnetic pacifier stays on well without falling off.

She is perfect for photo shoots due to her being posable. Any doll collector would adore this sweet little girl.

title: Wavy is so stinkin cute!!
text:
[[VIDEOID:23a5cf761815ff752dc959c0c379702c]] Wavy the Narwhal is so stinkin cute! 😍 My 5 year old daughter just adores her. She comes packaged in an adorable box and includes 3 accessories: a ball, donut, and a brush.

Batteries are already included too, which is an added bonus. What is cool and about this FurReal toy is that she has a daytime mode, and a nighttime mode. In the daytime mode, she plays with you, makes adorable sounds, blinks, plays music, laughs, and gives kisses. In the nighttime mode she will play relaxing ocean sounds. You can also touch her fin to change the sounds to relaxing music which is so neat! The horn lights up in both day and night mode. She is so interactive and does so much, you would think she is a real pet versus a toy! 😂

I expect Wavy to be a huge hit at Christmas time this year. She is really one of the coolest toys out right now!

title: She's beautiful, but not posable.
text:
This sweet little baby girl by Jizhi is absolutely beautiful. Her facial expression is so sweet and she is perfectly painted. Her hair is beautifully rooted. She comes with accessories that include a hairbrush, however the hairbrush is hard and due to her soft rooted hair, I would not recommend using this brush and using a soft bristled baby brush instead.
