Her outfit is so cute and she comes with a rattle, plate, utensils, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate.

Her body is cloth, however her limbs are a softer vinyl. She is a beautiful doll perfect for a collector, I just wish her limbs were posable.

title: She is much more beautiful in person!
text:
All I have to say is that the stock photos do not do this sweet little girl justice! She looks SO much more beautiful in person. Usually the dolls look better in the stock photos, but that is not the case for this one.

My wife was pleasantly surprised by this sweet little girl as she is just perfect! Her features are so realistic and she is posable. Her head, arms, legs, hands, and feet are soft vinyl and her body is cloth.

She is a decent weight for her size. Her hair is rooted and very full. If you do comb it, I would use a soft bristled baby brush so it doesn't shed too much. The little expression on her face is so cute too! She is definitely a little boss and full of sass! The outfit is perfect for her!

They also sent an additional onesie, diaper, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate. For the price, this little girl is perfect. Any doll collector would absolutely love her to pieces.

title: She is amazingly realistic looking!
text:
Wow! This little girl by Adolly is so amazingly realistic looking! Her features are so lifelike! My wife is an adult doll collector and absolutely loves this little girl. She is also a huge fan of the Adolly brand as every doll from them has been of amazing quality.

She comes packaged in a box and is wrapped in a plastic zipper bag. She comes with a birth certificate, bottle, magnetic pacifier, diaper, and a red headband that she is already wearing. The magnetic pacifier stays on well.

Her romper is so precious with the little Minnie Mouse on the front! It actually looks like a Christmas outfit.

If my wife were to take this doll out in public, people would automatically think it is a real baby. She is perfectly painted from head to toe. Her hand painted hair actually looks like real hair. The little veins and creases are so real looking. She has just the right amount of blushing, not too much, and not too little.

Her body is cloth, and her head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are vinyl, but it is a softer vinyl. Her head is floppy just like a real baby, and she has a good weight to her.

All in all, my wife thinks she is perfect and any doll collector would absolutely adore this little girl.

title: She's perfect and posable!
text:
This Maddie doll by GOAROY is absolutely beautiful! She looks even more beautiful in person, the pictures do not do her justice.

My wife has wanted a Maddie doll for awhile, and this little girl is just perfect. She is very affordable too!

She arrives in a nice box, packaged perfectly and includes a magnetic pacifier, hat, bib, birth certificate, and a bottle.

Her hair is beautifully rooted, and the brown curls are just adorable. She is perfectly painted too! Her body is cloth, and weighted. Her head, arms, legs, hands, and feet are soft vinyl. The details on her are just amazing, she truly looks so realistic.

She has beautiful blue eyes and the sweetest smile. Her mouth is slightly opened.

What my wife loves most about this doll compared to similar ones is that her limbs are posable. This was a huge surprise to her, but she loves it. You can easily pose her arms and legs to add more realism to the doll and she would be perfect for a photo shoot.

I think any doll collector would absolutely adore this sweet little girl. My wife just loves her!

title: The perfect water play toy!
text:
My 5 year old daughter loves this Aquaplay set. It is so much fun and is the perfect water play toy! It is not only fun, but educational at the same time.

I loved how easy the instructions were to follow and how easy it was to put together. It's definitely the best water play toy that I have seen. Highly recommend!

title: Awesome set!
text:
My 5 year old loves the game Among Us and was thrilled with this set. The stickers are her favorite! They are nice quality vinyl stickers and waterproof, and there are so many different designs!

You get 100 stickers, 12 buttons, and 12 bracelets. The buttons and bracelets are cute too. The bracelets fit my wife perfectly, but were a little too big on my 5 year old's wrist. This is an awesome set to make birthday party favor bags.

title: It's awesome!!
text:
This toy is awesome!! My kids love it. I also love it as it has soft wheels which will not damage anything. You can use both indoors and outdoors.

It comes with the vehicle itself, a USB charger, and a remote control. It requires 2 x AAA batteries that are not included.

The vehicle can jump up to 22” in the air. My kids get a kick out of it and it keeps them entertained. This is probably one of the coolest remote control vehicles that I have seen and it's definitely worth the price.

title: He's perfect in every way.
text:
My wife is a doll collector and is a huge fan of Adolly brand. They never seem to let down.

This little boy is a doll collector's dream. He looks so realistic, that if you took him out in public, people would automatically think he is a real baby!

He is so chubby, but so precious. He is definitely a big boy and feels weighted. His body is cloth, and his head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are made from a softer vinyl. He is perfectly painted from head to toe.

He comes with a birth certificate, a magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. The magnetic pacifier stays on well without falling off.

His little onesie outfit and hat are so adorable. His hair is beautifully rooted.

Everything about this sweet boy is absolutely perfect. Any doll collector would be delighted with him.

title: Doesn't work as expected
text:
[[VIDEOID:dab2d180850360247cb98c308492e193]] This tiny aero dancer is a neat idea, however it doesn't work that well once put together. Don't get me wrong, I love the concept of putting it together, but the end result is a bit disappointing.

It requires a 9 volt battery (not included), and it only took a few minutes to put together. It comes with stickers to add eyes and accessories to it.

The end result is that it worked, but with assistance (see video as he doesn't stay up). The fabric is very thin too, so you need to be extra precautious when handling it or it will rip. Unfortunately I cannot recommend this product.

title: So realistic looking and very adorable.
text:
This little girl doll by Rebornova is so adorable. She has the sweetest little face and her hair is actually rooted. She is not a true reborn, as she is not a 1 of a kind, but a mass produced doll… However she is very realistic looking. She is a more affordable option compared to a true reborn doll.

Her body is cloth and her head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are vinyl. The vinyl is hollow inside, however even with her being hollow inside she is somewhat weighted. Not as weighted as some others, but she does have some weight added to her.

She has some blushing and her hands and feet are painted nicely. She comes with an additional onesie, a diaper, a magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate. Her magnetic pacifier stays on well without falling off.

Finally, her outfit is so pretty, it is a onesie with a tutu like skirt attached to it.

This little girl doll is so sweet and any doll collector or child would absolutely adore her!

title: Wild thing is the sweetest little thing.
text:
Wild Thing by Paradise Galleries is a sweet thing for sure! She has the most sweetest little face and outfit! Any doll collector would absolutely adore this little girl.

She comes packaged nicely in a box and comes with a certificate of authenticity, a magnetic pacifier, and a soft blanket.

Her features are truly realistic. Her eyes look very real. She is perfectly painted from head to toe and smells so good, just like baby powder. Her head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are soft touch vinyl. Her body is cloth and she is weighted and feels similar to holding a real baby. Her hair is rooted mohair as well and is very soft.

Her outfit is pink leopard print and is too cute for words. She even has the most adorable little booties - Sparkly pink cuteness!

title: He's beautiful and so realistic! Amazing quality doll!
text:
This sweet little boy by Milidool is an amazing quality doll at an awesome price! He's so realistic looking and painted so perfectly. I have other dolls from this brand and all of them are outstanding quality.

He is weighted, to give that feeling of holding a real baby. He is perfectly packaged and comes with a bunch of accessories: a plush giraffe 🦒, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate. His outfit is so so cute and the quality is amazing. The magnetic pacifier stays on perfectly without falling off.

His eyes are beautiful and he truly looks so real. His hair is soft and rooted perfectly. He also comes with an adorable little hat.

He's such a beautiful doll and my wife is a huge fan of this brand. This little guy is waiting to be adored by doll collectors everywhere!! 💙💙💙

title: The eyes 👀 are haunting and she has a monkey face
text:
This doll by Acestar is a bit creepy. The eyes 👀 are haunting, and also are not symmetrical. Her face also looks like a monkey 🐵!

The doll arrives in a plastic bag with no clothes on. This could be a bit alarming as the girl doll is anatomically correct. She does come with a diaper and a hooded blanket , but no outfit. The hooded blanket is very soft and is a panda 🐼 design.

She also comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. The magnetic pacifier does not stay on too well.

The doll is not silicone, she is vinyl from head to toe. She is hollow inside and feels a bit cheap.

For the quality of this doll, the price is too high. I would pay $20 or less for this doll… but no more than that. Unfortunately I cannot recommend this doll.

title: He's very realistic looking and cute!
text:
This little boy doll by Acestar is adorable. He is not a true reborn as he is a mass produced doll, not a one of a kind. He is a more affordable option compared to a true reborn doll.

He is not silicone, he is vinyl on the head, hands, arms, legs, and feet and has a cloth body. He is painted nicely and does look very realistic. His hair is long and rooted.

His outfit is adorable and comes with a hat. He also comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate.

He is not weighted compared to some other brands that are. He is the size of a newborn and appears he would fit in newborn clothes.

I only took off 1 star as the price is kind of high as I have seen other dolls that are better quality with a lower price tag.

title: Skelegod is awesome!! Love Masters of the Universe!
text: Wow!! This Skelegod action figure from Masters of the Universe is awesome!! I remember He-Man from the 80's and loved watching it as a kid. It's awesome to see them back on Netflix. The action figure is nicely made and has great articulation. He is very nicely detailed and is perfect for kids to play with or can even be kept as a collector's item as the box it comes in is SO nice!

title: It's awesome!!
text: My kids love this all terrain bat mobile! It comes with a controller that takes 2 AAA batteries and it syncs right to the vehicle. It is easy to maneuver using the remote and can ride on all surfaces, even water! It is loads of fun!

title: It's not sticky at all! So much fun for my kids!
text:
This butter slime is so much fun! My kids are huge fans of slime, but I am not a fan of the stickiness.

Let me tell you, this slime is NOT STICKY at all! I am so impressed by the quality of it. It's literally smooth like butter and lots of fun without the mess. It also comes with a bunch of sprinkles, confetti, and toys that you can add to the fun. It's the perfect indoor activity!

title: Ava and Adalyn are cute! But Adalyn has a lazy eye!
text:
This review is for 2 dolls: Ava and Adalyn. These 2 look like sisters as they are the same sculpt, however look slightly different.

Ava is adorable in her yellow dress and her hair is beautiful rooted. Adalyn is adorable in her little white romper and her hair is also beautifully rooted. If you comb their hair though, be careful and I would use a soft bristled baby brush as it does shed some and you don't want them going bald!

They both come with additional onesies, diapers, magnetic pacifiers, bottles, and a birth certificate. The dolls are a good size, they are quite big.

Their arms, hands, legs, feet, and head are vinyl and their bodies are cloth. The head and limbs are hollow inside and Ava doesn't feel weighted, however Adalyn feels slightly weighted.

Their features are so realistic and they are beautiful dolls, but poor Adalyn has a lazy eye!! Poor girl! It seems like her eyes were not properly lined up when they put her together. My wife still loves her though, lazy eye or not. These little girls would be adored by any doll collector.

title: She's very interactive and so cute!
text:
[[VIDEOID:968d8b6d5f3e34f60205da1598769e06]] Baby Alive Lulu Achoo is a very cute doll! She comes with a bunch of accessories including a doctor station with attached play stethoscope, 2 charts, a pretend thermometer, a cloth tissue, a spoon, a comb and a bottle.

Batteries are already included, which is an added bonus. When in the box she is on a demo mode where she does a few things, however once you take her out you can switch her to the “on” mode which is located on her back.

I am impressed as to how interactive she is, she does so many things. She is tiny at only 12”, but is absolutely adorable with her big blue eyes and blonde hair. She will sneeze and her nose turns red. Her nose is SO bright red, she reminds me of Rudolph the red nosed reindeer! lol! When you wipe her nose with the tissue, the redness disappears which is cool.

You can also check her temperature with her pretend thermometer. When you do it will make a sound and her head also turns bright red. The lights in the nose and the forehead are so bright, so the point where it looks fake. The only recommendation I have is if the lights were moved further back in her head to where it would look more real. The red light in the nose goes away with the cloth tissue and it goes away in the forehead with the medicine spoon.

When you check her heartbeat with the stethoscope she makes a cute “boom boom” sound, that is adorable. Her eyes also open and close.

I think any child would love her, she is so cute!

title: It's cute!! Perfect for a Pac-Man fan!
text: This Pac-Man plush is so cute! It's actually quite big, bigger than what I was expecting. It is very soft, except for his mouth area. My kids love playing with it! It would be perfect for any Pac-Man fan!

title: She is so cute! Very realistic looking.
text:
This little girl doll is so cute! She is not a real reborn as reborns are a one of a kind. However, she is so realistic looking!

Her facial expression is so sweet and her eyes do look so real. Her hair is brown and rooted. She comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, onesie, and a birth certificate.

The magnetic pacifier stays on perfectly without falling off. Her little outfit is adorable and excellent quality.

The description states that she is weighted, however she does not feel weighted to me. Her body is cloth and her head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are vinyl.

She would be perfect for a doll collector as she is so beautiful.

title: Tiny, but lots of fun!
text:
[[VIDEOID:3abbcd02cd33df102a07cc64eb61a5bc]] My 5 year old loves playing piano. Since it says in the description that it is for up to 6 year olds I ordered it for her as she loves music.

It was so easy to set up, no tools are needed. The pieces connect with no issues. I had this put together in less than 5 minutes.
It does take 4xAA batteries, that are not included.

The only flaw is that it is SO small. The seat is only a few inches from the floor so maybe this would be best for a 1-2 year old. My daughter had a difficult time sitting on the seat as it was so low. You can also choose not to use the seat and sit on the floor and play instead.

There are so many different instruments to choose from and the microphone works well. It is a tad bit pricey for what you get though as it is so small. If the price was a bit lower I would say this would be the perfect piano for a toddler.

title: Affordable realistic looking doll with a few small flaws.
text:
This little boy by Charex is very adorable. For the price, I would say he is definitely worth it. He does look very realistic and has the cutest little face.

His body is cloth, and his head, arms, legs, hands, and feet are soft vinyl, however he is hollow inside. He is not really weighted compared to some other dolls that I have seen. He is difficult to pose and his body is a bit stiff and not very flexible.

He comes with a birth certificate, a baby bottle, and a magnetic pacifier. The baby bottle that I received had a deformed nipple (in photos), however there is really no point to the bottle as it cannot fit in his mouth. The magnetic pacifier stays on well without falling off.

He is a very cute doll at an affordable price with a few flaws. I think a collector or a child would still love him.

title: She is beautiful. High quality doll at an amazing price.
text:
Little Sandy by Milidool is so cute! She truly looks so realistic and she has the prettiest blue eyes. She has the most adorable facial expression.

Her hair is a wig, however feels realistic, so close to real human hair. Her outfit is so adorable too! It is a pink giraffe theme and she comes with a plush toy… Which appears to be a horse.

She also comes with a birth certificate, bottle, hat, and a magnetic pacifier. The pacifier stays on well without falling off.

She is actually weighted to give that feeling of holding a real baby. She would be great for therapy and even for collectors as she is so perfectly made.

My wife is a doll collector and absolutely adores this little girl as she is so sweet. Anyone would love her as a gift! She is a high quality doll at an amazing price.

title: They are even more beautiful in person!
text:
This review is for 2 dolls as I couldn't do a separate review for each. These baby girls (Lilia and Lisa) by Milidool are even more beautiful in person! The pictures don't do them justice!

For the price, the quality of these dolls is out of this world!! The laughing facial expressions are so cute and they truly looks so realistic. The clothing is adorable and is amazing quality too!

My wife is a doll collector and was amazed at the quality of these dolls. Even the packaging was outstanding. They come with a bunch of accessories too: birth certificate, headband, magnetic pacifier, bottle, plush toys (cat rattle and teddy bear), and a hooded cat towel.

Their bodies are cloth and weighted for a realistic feel. Their arms, hands, legs, feet, and head are soft vinyl. Some dolls made of soft vinyl feel hollow inside. Not this one!! The manufacturer did a great job at this. It almost feels like she is filled with gel.

These little girls are just amazing and highly recommend for doll collectors. You will be so happy with either of these sweet girls!! ❤️

title: The sweetest baby boy doll, absolutely precious.
text:
I love you s'mores by Paradise Galleries is the sweetest baby boy doll. His outfit is just adorable as it says “I love you s'mores” and has camping pictures on his shorts and his hood. His little booties are soft and furry, perfect to keep his little feet warm.

He comes with a certificate of authenticity, a magnetic pacifier, and a s'mores toy that attaches to his wrist with a rubber band.

He smells so good, just like baby powder! He is also weighted to give that feeling of holding a real baby. His hair is rooted mohair and so soft to touch. His eyes and facial expression are so cute, and so realistic looking.

I think any doll collector would absolutely adore this little guy as he is so sweet! Highly recommend him.

title: She is a doll collector's dream doll!
text: This 2021 Signature Holiday Barbie doll is absolutely gorgeous and is a doll collector's dream doll. She is absolutely beautiful. From her face, to her hair, to her beautiful dress. My wife absolutely loves her and is going to keep her in the box as a collector's item. Her dress is amazing with so much detail, and even the box is beautiful that she arrives in. She is a beautiful doll at an amazing price!

title: She's cute, but her paci only sticks to her chin! Lol.
text:
This little girl by Rebornova is adorable. Her little outfit is just too cute for words and she comes with an additional onesie, diaper, bottle, birth certificate, and magnetic pacifier. Her body is cloth, but her head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are soft vinyl.

She has very beautiful earrings, and for this reason I would not recommend for younger children. I would say she would be a great doll for 10+ or collectors.

The only issue I had with this doll is that her magnetic pacifier sticks to her chin, and not her mouth, lol. It seems when they put the magnet in her, it was incorrectly placed… So it only sticks to her chin (as pictured). Other than that, she is very soft and huggable and just adorable.

title: The cutest dozen of eggs you will ever see!
text:
This Hatchimals CollEGGtibles Shimmer Babies set is adorable. They come packaged in an egg carton and you get 12 figures, however 1 of our eggs actually had twins, so we got 2! So all in all, it was 13 figures (however not all may get the twins).

The little shimmer babies are so adorable, and each one is so sparkly - full of glitter. The glitter does not come off either, so no need to worry about a mess.

To hatch the eggs in the past, we rubbed them… However we tried that with these and we weren't getting anywhere. A grown up will need to squeeze them in order to hatch and the process is much easier. My 5 year old was not able to hatch these on her own, but was able to with the help of me!

title: Adorable set with a few tiny flaws.
text:
This Kindi Kids mini amusement park set is so adorable. If you have additional mini Kindi Kids figures, they will work with this set.
🌈
This set only comes with 1 figure, but it will hold up to 7 different figures on the rides. The rainbow swing is awesome. She locks on perfectly and you can spin her around and watch her go.
🌈
The Ferris wheel is a bit flawed. While it is so cute, when you place her on there is no possible way to lock her on it. The bar is designed to hold the doll down, however she is so top heavy that eventually she swings upside down and falls off the Ferris wheel! Poor thing! 😢
🌈
The roller coaster was easy to snap together, and this set requires very little assembly. The roller coaster does require some assistance as she does not glide down freely. You will need to support with your hand to keep on the track.
🌈
Just a few tiny flaws with this set, but overall super cute and would recommend for any Kindi Kids fan!

title: Awesome! Great for sensory play!
text: This 4 pack of Goo Jit Zu heroes is awesome! You get Batman, The Flash, Superman, and Aqua man. What is so cool about this set is each figure has a different texture, which is great for sensory play. They remind me of Stretch Armstrong from the 80's. It is almost like a blast from the past! My kids love it and I totally recommend for any super hero lover!

title: Lots of fun, if you don't mind a little mess!
text:
This Barbie Color reveal foam set was so much fun for my 5 year old daughter, but it does get a little messy!

It comes with a pineapple shaped container and a capsule which contains the doll. The doll is pink with no features when taking out of the capsule at first. There is a bubble solution that you put in the capsule which reveals her true colors and features!

She comes with 25 accessories, and you can dress her up. You can even keep the pineapple container as a tub for her and put the foam in the change some of the accessories too.

The foam is scented too, it didn't really smell like pineapple… To me it smelled more like strawberries and it was pink.

I would say this would be better for older kids as it can be a little messy, and will require some adult supervision. All in all though, awesome concept!

title: He's beautiful and so lifelike!
text:
Little Firecracker by Paradise Galleries is a beautiful baby boy doll. His features are so lifelike!

He comes packaged so nicely in the box and arrives with a certificate of authenticity, a magnetic pacifier, and a patriotic bib that snaps on.

The first thing I noticed when I opened the box is that he smells so good! Just like baby powder.

His body is weighted and cloth. His head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are made from soft touch vinyl, which makes his skin so soft.

He is perfectly painted from head to toe, the details are just amazing.

He also poses very easily, so you can have a lot of fun taking pictures with him!

His hair is rooted mohair. So soft to touch! His little patriotic outfit and navy blue booties are absolutely adorable.

Any doll collector would absolutely adore this little guy as he is so precious.

title: Awesome set! My kids love it!
text:
These Akedo Ultimate Arcade Warriors are awesome. Whoever came up with this idea is truly a genius. It is like playing a video game in real life!

You get a bunch of characters in this set and a joystick, where you can change them out. They can hit each other and then they split apart. It is so easy to put them back together again too. This makes a great indoor activity for your kids!

title: Just like playing a video game in real life!
text:
My kids love this Akedo Ultimate Arcade set. It's just like playing a video game in real life! It comes with the battle arena, and 2 legendary warrior figures. If you have additional figures already, you can swap them out too!

What is so neat, is that the arena actually makes sounds when the warriors are fighting. After fighting, they even make a sound like they are out of breath! It is so funny, and loads of fun! It's even fun for adults too!

The music from the arena reminds of me of old school 80's video games. Batteries are also included too, which is an added bonus!

title: Awesome toy!
text: My kids love Goo Jit Zu toys, and this shark one is a huge hit! When you move his head up and down it changes the texture to be firm. There is a black button behind his head which makes him soft and squishy again. It's neat how you can change the texture. He is also very stretchy and almost like a stress reliever in a way. The shark face makes it even cooler!

title: Such a funny game!
text:
[[VIDEOID:2d6e2ae0ad4aeca872e4a0ca1a2416ca]] Fart and Go Seek is such a funny game! My kids love it. It is basically like hide and seek with some extra humor to it!

You have to hide with your bean, and make it back home without getting caught. The pink and the blue beans are loud and make sounds, so if these are your beans, you will be at a higher risk of getting caught!

The 3 smaller beans are silent but deadly, and these are the easier ones for winning as they don't make sounds! It's a great indoor game that my kids love playing!

Batteries are included too, so that is an extra bonus!

title: She's cute, but not a true reborn. Great for a child.
text:
This little girl doll by ENA is very cute, however she is not a true reborn doll.

For the price, she is good quality. Her body is cloth and huggable, however her arms and legs are vinyl. The description says she is silicone vinyl, however it is true vinyl, not silicone at all.

She is not as detailed as some dolls, however like I said earlier, good for the price. She is not a great doll for a collector, but I think a child would love her.

She also comes with a birth certificate, magnetic pacifier, and a bottle.

title: She is perfect - Even more beautiful in person.
text:
Little Love by Paradise Galleries is absolutely perfect in every way. She is even more beautiful in person. She makes the perfect 30th anniversary doll. She is so beautiful, that I had to order another one for my wife as she is so in love with her and she makes a great collector's item! Love is truly the perfect name for her, because anyone that owns her will love her!
❤️
She is packaged so nicely and as soon as you open the box you can smell her! She smells so good! Just like baby powder/brand new baby scent.
❤️
She has the sweetest little face, and the most adorable eyes, she is truly so realistic looking. Her hair is mohair, and beautifully rooted. Her head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are soft touch vinyl. Her body is cloth and weighted to give that realistic feeling of holding a real baby. She is a perfect cuddle baby.
❤️
She comes with a pink bonnet, but also a pink headband, so you can change if you wish. She is wearing an adorable romper with a cardigan and a bib that says 30th anniversary. She also has matching pink booties for her feet.
❤️
She also comes with a magnetic pacifier that stays on well, and a silver plated keepsake rattle, and a soft flannel doll bag with the anniversary emblem on it.
❤️
She is just too perfect for words- Beautifully painted from head to toe, and any doll collector would absolutely adore her! 😍❤️❤️❤️

title: They are both realistic looking.
text:
This review is for 2 dolls.

For doll #1:
This newborn baby girl doll by Jizhi is absolutely adorable. She is not a true reborn doll, however is a more affordable option.

She is packaged so nicely, and comes with a plush bunny, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and birth certificate.

She is nicely detailed from head to toe and truly looks so realistic! Her little onesie outfit is so cute too!

Her body is cloth, however her head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are vinyl.

She is perfect for any doll collector! ❤️

For doll #2:
This newborn baby boy doll is adorable, but tiny. He is very realistic looking and has nicely painted hair. His body is cloth, and his limbs are a soft vinyl.

He is not posable, his body is actually kind of stiff. He comes in an adorable outfit and hat, and includes a magnetic pacifier, bottle, feeding accessories, a hairbrush, and a birth certificate. I am not sure the reason for the hairbrush, as he doesn't actually have any hair that you can comb. Also, I don't understand the reason for the feeding accessories as newborn babies can't eat solid foods! Lol. 😂 Also, why is a boy's magnetic pacifier pink? I think it should be white or blue to match his outfit.
He is also not weighted.

He is a nice doll, but is not the best realistic looking doll out there.

title: She's absolutely beautiful!
text:
Sweet Dreams April by Charex is absolutely beautiful, and even more beautiful in person!

She is 22” long and weighs 3.3 lbs. She has a cloth body, and her head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are soft vinyl. She is perfect for snuggling!

She has a sweet beautiful smile and her hair is so soft. She comes in an adorable onesie that says “Hello World”, and has a white knitted hat and booties.

The packaging was perfect too. She is not an actual reborn, however is a more affordable option compared to a real reborn. I think any child or collector would absolutely adore her!

She comes with a baby bottle, a magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. The magnetic pacifier stays on well without falling off.

title: It's fun stuff!
text: This Crazy Aaron's thinking putty is fun stuff! My kids love it as it never dries out. They can sculpt with it, which is neat. The clear color looks very cool.

title: Never dries out, my kids love it!
text: This Crazy Aaron's thinking putty is fun stuff! The container is small, however it is a lot of fun! It's cool as it never dries out. My kids dig it!

title: Fun to watch her fly!
text:
The Hatchimals Pixie Crystal Flyer - Starlight Idol, is an awesome toy that my 5 year old daughter loves. We have had these Hatchimal Pixies in the past and they have always been a hit!

She comes packaged in an egg, and the USB charger is attached to the bottom of the egg. Upon arrival, she was already partially charged, so we watched her light up and fly! She didn't last that long as she was only partially charged. We fully charged her and she works perfect, just make sure you fly her in an open area, as she does come crashing down sometimes. It's definitely a cool toy though!

title: She is absolutely beautiful and smells so good!
text:
Buttons and Bows by Paradise Galleries is an absolutely beautiful doll. She comes packaged in a nice box, and the presentation of the packaging was outstanding.

She is a beautiful sleeping baby, and her head, arms, and legs are made from soft touch vinyl. Her little finger nails and toe nails are painted just perfectly.

She measures 21” long from head to toe, and her body is cloth, but weighted for a realistic feeling.

Her hair is rooted, and is so soft to touch. She comes with a ribbon to tie in her hair to give her a cute little baby ponytail, and also a barrette, that you can attach to her hat or put in her hair.

She comes with a magnetic pacifier, a little teddy bear lovey blanket that is so soft, and a certificate of authenticity.

She is wearing an adorable nightgown and a diaper underneath.

Oh, and also she smells SO good! Just like a brand new baby smell!!

My wife is a doll collector and loves this doll to pieces. Any collector would absolutely adore this precious princess.

title: So cute and so realistic looking!
text:
This baby boy by Adolly is so cute! He is not a true reborn, however is very realistic looking and a more affordable option compared to a real reborn.

He comes packaged very nicely, and is dressed in a onesie. He also comes with an adorable sleeper. A magnetic pacifier, a hat, baby bottle, birth certificate, and a stuffed bear that goes around his wrist are also included. The magnetic pacifier stays on without falling off.

His facial features are so realistic looking, from his adorable big brown eyes to his painted on realistic looking hair. You can even see the fine details in his little fingertips to the little veins under his skin.

His head, arms, and legs are soft vinyl and his body is cloth, but weighted…for a realistic feel.

Any collector or child would love him, and he would make a perfect gift.

title: So realistic looking and so adorable!
text:
This sweet little girl by Adolly is truly beautiful. She is not a true reborn, however is very realistic looking and a more affordable option vs. a real reborn.

She comes in an adorable onesie and pants set, a reversible bib, a birth certificate, headband, magnetic pacifier, and a baby bottle. The magnetic pacifier stays on her perfectly without falling off.

Her head, legs, and arms and soft vinyl. Her body is cloth and weighted for a realistic feel.

She is perfectly painted, and you can even see the little veins which make her more realistic. Her hair is painted on, but truly looks so real. Her eyes look so real too, the pictures don't do her justice. She is even more beautiful in person.

Any collector or child would love her!

title: She is precious, but arrives with no clothes on!
text:
This sweet little girl, Princess Toddle by LifeReborn is very adorable… However I wasn't too fond of the packaging. She arrived in a bag, and was completely nude. She is also anatomically correct, so this could be alarming to someone! That is the only reason for taking off 1 star.

She has big beautiful brown eyes and very soft brown hair with precious curls. She comes with a ladybug sleeper outfit, a diaper, magnetic pacifier, birth certificate, lady bug blanket, and a baby bottle.

Her hair is a wig, but still very adorable and soft. She is soft vinyl from head to toe. Her head does bobble just like a real baby, however she is hollow inside.

Her arms and legs are posable, so she can sit or stand against a wall.

She is not a true reborn, but is a more affordable option and is still realistic looking and very sweet. Any child or collector would love her.

title: Adorable and in love with the packaging idea!
text:
This little lady by Adolly is absolutely adorable. She comes in a pink box and when you open it, her head is wrapped in a diaper… Just like opening a real reborn!
She is not a true reborn, however is a more affordable option compared to a true reborn.

She comes in a sweet little cat onesie, pants, socks, and a hat. She also comes with a magnetic pacifier, a birth certificate, headband, diaper, and a baby bottle.

She is very nicely detailed and looks very realistic. The blushing paint is light and looks so real. You can even see her little veins painted in finely. Her hair is also painted on, but truly looks so realistic!

Her head, arms, and legs are soft vinyl. Her body is cotton, and she feels weighted to give that feeling of holding a real baby.

Her eyes are beautiful brown, and they look even more realistic in person. The expression on her face is so cute, but pouty at the same time!

I think any collector or child would love this doll. She is gorgeous!

title: He's even more adorable in person!
text:
This Forever Yours Miracle baby boy by Paradise Galleries is even more adorable in person! The pictures don't do him justice!

He is wrapped up in a little cradle upon opening and the presentation is out of this world. As soon as I removed him from the plastic, I could smell him - - He smells so good! Just like a real baby, with the fresh baby powder scent.

His eyes are so realistic and just draw you into them, and he has the sweetest little face. His hair is rooted and his curls are so soft to touch.

His head is even floppy, just like a real baby. His body is cloth, but is weighted for a realistic feel. He comes dressed in a diaper, an adorable forever yours onesie, a hospital hat, and a hospital bracelet. He also comes with a magnetic pacifier and a swaddle blanket. You can also keep the cradle he comes in (which I did as it is so nice).

My wife is an adult doll collector and she is in love with this precious baby. I think any collector would be super in love with him! ❤️

title: Good quality, creepy and cool!
text: I love horror and everything about it! This eyeball is great for a prank, or just to add to a horror collection. It's nice quality and super creepy, just how I like it!

title: She looks amazingly real!
text:
This baby girl by Adolly is beautiful! She looks even more beautiful in person and amazingly real! She has an adorable smile and painted on hair, which is actually done very nicely. Her nails are nicely detailed. She is even detailed down to the precious little wrinkles in her hands and feet.

She comes packaged in a nice pink box, and includes a magnetic pacifier, birth certificate, and a baby bottle. She also comes with an adorable pink flower hat and matching booties.

Her body is vinyl and her limbs are posable to an extent. She is a perfect doll for a collector! So sweet and precious!

title: An excellent first microscope!
text: This Educational Insights Microscope is a perfect first microscope for your child. It comes with 15 slides and the focus knob is easy to adjust, even for a small child. There is so much to see and learn. This is a great educational toy!

title: A miniature baby doll
text:
I wouldn't call this a reborn doll. I would call it a miniature baby doll with realistic features instead. It's adorable though.

it comes in this cute little romper outfit with a hat and a birth certificate. The body is full vinyl, it is that tough vinyl, and the body is posable.

Tiny at only 12”, but has a sweet little smile that will melt your heart. I think any child or collector would love it.

title: She's amazing!!
text:
[[VIDEOID:aa60076ae61ff960b71689a423ce4c45]] This Big City Big Dreams singing Barbie is absolutely amazing for the price. My 5 year old daughter was blown away by her and loves her so much!!

Move her arm and she starts to sing, then her dress lights up in different color patterns. It's beautiful (see on the video)!

She sings 2 super catchy tunes, that are truly GOOD and that I really don't mind hearing all day! Lol!

She comes with a microphone, a guitar, shoes, and a headset. If you make her dance, her shoes do fall off though, but this is normal with a Barbie, also the guitar doesn't stay on too well while making her dance. Still, she is super amazing for the price!!

title: She's a beautiful doll!
text:
My wife is a doll collector and she is so happy with this doll, she's beautiful!

She comes packaged nicely in a brown box, but inside the brown box, she is inside what appears to be a little crib, but it is cardboard and says Paradise Galleries. You can keep this to lay your baby in after you open her up, or even to display her on.

She comes in an adorable onesie with a little pink hat. She has beautiful blue eyes and short blonde curly hair. She smells so good too, like baby powder! I could smell her as soon as we took her out of the box.

She is precious, and would be great for both collectors and children. Her face, arms, and legs are soft vinyl, however her body is stuffed, so she is huggable and ready for lots of love.

She is even wearing a hospital bracelet. So cute!! Her head is floppy just like a real baby too, which adds character.

title: These make drawing so much more fun!
text: My kids love these Scentos scented markers! They smell SOOOO good and make drawing so much fun! They are easy to hold onto and work just as expected. We can't wait for the next season of these markers to come out!

title: Very realistic, so cute!
text: This doll is a cutie pie! He may not be a true reborn, it is darn close without paying thousands of dollars! His features are so lifelike and he has a cloth body which is soft and huggable. His hair is soft and rooted, which feels real. He comes with a bottle, magnetic pacifier, and a birth certificate. He is soft vinyl, not full silicone. I would say he is excellent quality for the price though.

title: Cute little guy
text: This little alien 👽 dude is cool! He is made of latex, and tiny… but a cute little guy! I named him Humberto and plan to bring him with me on my Halloween adventures! The only thing that could be better is if he was filled, the inside is hollow.

title: Very realistic and nicely detailed doll
text:
This doll is very realistic looking and nicely detailed. I am aware she is not a true reborn. She is much more affordable than a true reborn doll though.

She came packaged very nicely wrapped in plastic with a magnetic pacifier and a baby bottle. She is wearing an adorable purple headband and pretty pearl-like earrings. Just be careful if this doll is for a child as the earrings don't have backs and they are a bit sharp. If this doll is for a child, you may want to remove the earrings before giving to your child. The earrings do look very pretty on her for a doll collector.

Her body is vinyl, and hollow inside. Her body is posable too, so you can sit her down or even make her stand against a wall.

One thing I noticed is that her hair was shedding as I took her out of the box though. This was her only flaw, and only minor. Still a very nice quality doll for the price.

title: It works just like it says!!
text:
[[VIDEOID:fa4e108ac71969a6cabe6cce0aaa7b02]] This Happitry Bubble in Bubble blower is so cute, and it works just like it says! The assembly instructions are right on the box and easy to follow. It requires 2 AA batteries (not included). The box shows the 2 batteries inserted the same direction, but this is not how they go, make sure the negative side is against the spring - just as you would with inserting any other battery.

It comes with a small bottle of bubble solution and a plastic bubble solution holder. It's so easy to use, that my 5 year old does it by herself. She really loves this toy and looks forward to playing with it!

The only downfall is if you use it a lot, the batteries die fast. It would be better if it was rechargeable. We used for a few hours in 1 day and it's already starting to die.

title: She's beautiful! So realistic!
text:
Sweet Dreams April - by Charex is truly a beautiful, realistic looking baby doll. She comes nicely packaged and includes a magnetic pacifier, a bottle, and a birth certificate. Her outfit is beautiful- full of pastel butterflies. Her eyes are closed and she has a precious smile that would warm anyone's heart! ❤️

She is 22” long, the length of a real newborn, and she has a soft plush body. Her face, arms, hands, legs, and feet are made of soft vinyl, that is squishy. She is soft enough for a child to carry around. She's not only great for kids though.., collectors would love her too! The price is great for the amazing quality of this doll.

The only thing I noticed is that her hands are slightly different than pictured in the description. But, it's not a big deal since the hands are still very nicely detailed.

title: You need to pull triggers all the way back to shoot
text:
[[VIDEOID:e200e7ee0c48074887957bbdbf0419c2]] My 5 year old loves this dinosaur shooting game! The assembly is very easy, and no batteries are needed for this game.

Just load the balls through the top of the shooters, aim, and go! It's a great activity for a rainy day.

At first, it took my daughter some time to learn how to do it. You need the put some muscle force into pulling the triggers - - you need to pull it all the way back for it to shoot.

The dinosaurs are colorful and have little stands which make them easy to set back up. There is a clear plastic covering which helps prevent the balls from flying out.

Overall, it's a very fun game for your little dinosaur 🦖 lover!!

title: Super fun game!!
text: This Super Mario Piranha Plant Escape game is soooo much fun!! My kids love it! It was so easy to assemble, that even a child could do it. No batteries are included either. You can play 2-4 players in this game. It comes with a Mario and a Luigi figure. You also get 2 plastic pieces with stickers to make Toadstool and Yoshi characters. You first roll the dice, and move the number of spaces on top of the dice. Whatever number you land on, you gently tap the red button (hoping not to trigger the piranha plant!!), and the last man standing wins. It can be a very quick game, but it is still super fun and my kids enjoy it. So for that, it gets 5 stars!

title: Very detailed and cool looking!
text: [[VIDEOID:50745b3684a2495a8c8162055eeef557]] This Jurassic World Sound Strike Triceratops dinosaur is too cool. It's actually very nicely detailed. It comes with batteries already included and when you move the tail up and down or side to side it makes attack sounds! It's simple, but still a very nice toy. Any dinosaur lover would love this as a gift!

title: A realistic looking baby doll
text: This doll is not a true reborn doll as it's not one of a kind (it's mass produced)... It is however, a very realistic looking baby doll. It came packaged in a box that says Hello on it, and she comes wrapped in plastic with a bottle and a magnetic pacifier. She is also wearing pretty pearl-like earrings and a cute purple headband. She is not silicone... the doll is silicone vinyl, which is squishy, but hollow on the inside. She is also anatomically correct. She's cute, but the price is a bit steep for what you get.

title: A lot of fun!!
text: The Space Jam Super Shoot and Dunk play set is a lot of fun! It's super easy to assemble the hoop and Lebron's hand attaches to the magnetic ball. Push him down to lock into the base and push the basketball 🏀 button behind him, which will make both Lebron and the ball go flying! I actually made a couple of shots in the hoop! My kids love it, and so would any Space Jam fan. 😃

title: It's a huge hit for my kids!
text:
My 5 year old daughter loves this Goo Jit Zu Lebron James! It's so strange, but I have to give it 5 stars as she has been playing with it nonstop! 😂

The head is hard, but the body is soft, squishy, and stretchy. You can stretch his arms and legs and they will always return to the normal form. These remind me of the Stretch Armstrong in the 80's, which was a huge hit too!

title: Nice little set for Space Jam fans!
text: My kids and I love Space Jam! These mini figures are so cool, and there is a mystery figure that is fun to open as it's a surprise. Each figure comes with a basketball stand to display them on. I personally like the full colored figures better than the full pink and purple ones... it was a cool idea, but my kids could care less about them and like the full colored figures better. It's still a great set though!! 👍

title: Good posable mini figure for the price
text: This Space Jam mini Lebron James figure with attachable rocket pack is a good mini figure set for the price. I was hoping to keep as a collector's item, however the package as busted in on the back and ripped on the top. But I understand, stuff happens. Lol 😂 My kids do like playing with it though! Lebron is posable and any Space Jam fan would love it!

title: The kids love this stuff!
text: This slime is a huge hit with my kids! It's soft, fluffy, and buttery feeling. You get 3 different scents in this pack: grape, strawberry shortcake, and sherbet. The grape smells amazing!!! The strawberry shortcake smells okay, but the sherbet stinks 😷. Lol...But my kids still love the stuff!! They could play with it for hours on end! They even come with cute little charms! 😊

title: Fun for all ages!
text: This Space Jam set is so much fun. I love it, and so do both of my kids (5 and 15). So it's fun for all ages! It comes with a mini LeBron James Figure, a mini Bugs Bunny Figure, 2 basketballs 🏀 , 2 base launchers, and a Space Jam Basketball Court with an adjustable basketball hoop. My kids love to challenge each other to see who can score the most hoops! The launchers are easy to use and a lot of fun.

title: Sensory fun!
text:
My kids love these popping fidget toys and the game Among Us - This is truly a match made in heaven!!

It looks just like one of the running characters in Among Us, and it's great for sensory fun.

My kids have a collection of these poppers and we play games with them to see who can pop theirs the fastest - it's the perfect rainy day activity.

Very nicely made, and they're even great for adult stress relief!! 🤪

title: The plush sheep was missing
text:
This Charex reborn baby doll is very realistic looking. The price is good, and he comes in this adorable outfit with a magnetic pacifier, a baby bottle, and a birth certificate.

His body is soft, the arms and legs are soft and squishy, and he is not scented. His weight is even similar to a real baby.

The only thing though - - Is that he was missing the plush sheep mentioned in the product description. He's still worth the price without it, but others may be dissatisfied if they don't receive the described product.

title: Fun set, but pricey.
text: This Ryan's World treasure chest is full of blind bag surprises. It is definitely exciting to open, but I feel it's a bit overpriced for what you get in the end. The set includes the micro chest, a small foam sword, micro putty, keys, an eyepatch, a Micro Dig'n Discover chest, 5 micro figures, and a micro pirate ship. If your child is a fan of pirates, then they will like this set. The figures are cute, but are a bit top heavy. My daughter liked the putty the most of all out of this whole set. 🤣

title: Similar to a Popple, but creepier
text:
This Space Jam transforming Lebron James plush reminds me of the Popples from the 80's. The outside would look like a basketball or soccer ball, and then they would transform into a cuddly cute friend.

Now this is the same concept, however it's a bit creepy. The Lebron that transforms from the ball is not cute whatsoever. Honestly, the face doesn't look like Lebron at all. He has a haunting, hideous smile that reminds me of a circus clown. 🤡

I will still give it 4 stars since I love Space Jam and it's a very cool concept....however that face in your kid's room at night may cause nightmares. 😂

title: Awesome talking action figure!
text: [[VIDEOID:2765490682ccd511e716856ed54b037b]] I have loved Space Jan since the original, so I am thrilled about the new one with Lebron James! This action figure stands very tall at 12”, and actually looks a lot like Lebron himself. Press his chest and he says 8 different phrases/sounds. He comes with accessories that attach to him too. The box he comes in is cool, but the toy is open on the front...with no protective covering, the box may not be ideal for a collector, but it's awesome as a child's toy! Definitely worth the price!

title: The figures are tiny
text:
I have loved Space Jam since the original movie, so I was so thrilled to hear about the new movie! And, these figures!

They are tiny, and each stands on their own basketball shaped base. You get 10 figures in the pack, however 4 of these are exclusive... meaning that they are not the normal color. They are blue and purple colored, and it's difficult to tell who they are. If they would have made all of the figures fully painted like the 6 regular characters, it would have been better. I could care less about the 4 exclusive characters. Still, it's a great toy for Space Jam fans!

title: We love Jack Skellington!
text: If you love The Nightmare Before Christmas, then you must get this Jack Skellington Plush! He's so cute in his Santa Suit and 20” long. He looks just like Jack in the movie, just dressed like Santa! Very nice quality! 💀

title: So realistic looking!
text:
This reborn doll is so realistic looking that it's scary! The doll is made of soft silicone vinyl and her limbs are posable. 💕

She comes with sandals, a magnetic pacifier, and a bottle. She is wearing an adorable onesie, a pretty headband, pearl earrings, and a diaper. Her entire body is wrapped in plastic upon receiving and packaged very nicely. She is anatomically correct. Any doll collector would love this doll, the details are so lifelike. 💕

title: Blind bags are so much fun!
text: This Spirit Untamed mini set is so much fun to open! Everything is in blind bags, so it's full of surprises. You get 5 surprises inside. The little barn is so cute and can fit the horses inside. The price is good for what you get. This would make a great gift for a fan of the movie!

title: Adorable set! Just as pictured.
text: This Spirit Untamed toddler Lucky doll and Spirit plush set is adorable! Lucky has the cutest face and big eyes, she even comes with a brush to comb her hair. The Spirit plush toy is so cute too. This would make a great gift for a fan of the movie!  🐴🐴🐴

title: A great set for motor skills!
text: My daughter loves this magnetic building set! You get 64 pieces total, along with an instructional booklet. The pieces connect so easily, and I even enjoy building these with her. The building opportunities are endless, and it's a great set to develop motor skills!

title: Just as cool as I thought it would be!
text: This magnetic floating earth is just as cool as I thought it would be! It works just like it says, it truly floats by the magnetic force! It rotates slowly just like the earth too! It's so cool and relaxing to watch. It would make an excellent gift for someone special!

title: My hands still hurt the next day!
text:
Ouch! This fossil thing was so difficult that it gave me a blister and sore hands the next day. For a child to do this would be difficult. My 5 year old tried, but quickly gave up.

The fossil pieces inside make 1 dinosaur. It's cheap plastic and the pieces wouldn't stay together. Also, there were no instructions on how to put it together. It does glow, but 1 touch to the dinosaur skeleton and it falls apart. Unfortunately I cannot recommend. Also, be ready for a mess.

title: Great collectors' item!!
text: If you are a Cars fan, then this set is a must! The cars look exactly like that in the movie, and includes: Lightning McQueen, Tow Mater, and the Sheriff. They are nicely detailed and would make a great collectors' item! The box is so nice too, I plan to keep it. 😃

title: Great value for the price
text:
You can't go wrong with Play-Doh! This little brontosaurus 🦕 set is so cute! It's nothing extraordinary, but is a great set for the price!

It comes with an egg that is easy to assemble. Place the brontosaurus inside the egg, and wiggle his tail to help him hatch. It comes with 2 eggs filled with play-doh. You can stuff the play-doh inside the brontosaurus to watch his neck grow, and to make cool shapes. The egg is full of shapes as well as the bottom of the brontosaurus' feet. It also comes with 2 tools for the play-doh. This is a very inexpensive fun toy!

title: Cool idea that failed in the end
text:
This design and drill marble maze set was a disappointment. While it is a really cool idea, it's very difficult to drill while standing up, as it keeps falling over... even for me, as an adult. I had to place on my lap to do the drilling, then once I was done, put the legs back on to stand up.

The maze itself is soooo small. I have had other marble mazes in the past where they are long, and it's fun to watch them roll down the track. This is so tiny, that the excitement is gone in just a few seconds. My daughter lost interest in it really quick.

The drill also requires 3 AA batteries (not included).

While it is a cool idea to build and develop motor skills, it's too difficult for a child and will end up in frustration and boredom on the long run.

title: Great for blanket forts!
text: My kids love building and playing in this set! It's easy to build and the pieces connect with a little bit of effort. It comes with a guide that gives you different building ideas. It works perfect for blanket forts with a light blanket! It also comes with lights to decorate your structure- these require 2AA batteries (not included). Overall, it's a nice quality set!

title: Educational and engaging!
text: My family loves this game! It's great for learning to match colors and also for fine motor skills. The key to the game is to fill up your log with 5 acorns, 1 of each color. By spinning the wheel it determines your fate in the game. The game itself is very nicely made and my children were very engaged while playing this! Would make a great family night game. 😁

title: Good old messy fun!
text:
This fossil set is some good old messy fun! I would definitely recommend doing this outdoors as it does make a mess, however washes off of clothes and skin with some soap and water.

It comes with a rock hammer and chisel to excavate the 8 fossils. There is also an included magnifying glass to see the fossils up close. It's lots of educational fun for your dinosaur lover!!

title: Great for fine motor skills!
text: My daughter loves this set! It comes with an actual working drill, however batteries aren't included. It takes 3 AAA batteries. It's so much fun as it's great for fine motor skills as you actually get to put it together. Also, don't  throw the box away, it's part of the play! Bolt Buddies packages unfold to become fun play sets, one simple step toward being sustainable and eco-friendly. 🌳

title: They are cute and cheaper alternatives to reborns.
text:
This baby dolls are not reborns, however they are more affordable options compared to a true reborn.

This review is for 2 dolls:

Doll #1 in the white onesie: She is very realistic looking and has the sweetest little face. Her body is cloth, and not weighted. Her hair is rooted and she comes with a cute headband, magnetic pacifier, bottle, and a birth certificate.

Doll #2 in the pink bunny outfit:
This little girl is absolutely adorable. Her features are so realistic and she has painted on hair, which actually looks like real hair. I am not sure of the reason for her coming with a hairbrush, as she doesn't have any real hair to comb. Lol. She also comes with a magnetic pacifier, bottle, birth certificate, a plush bunny toy, and feeding accessories. I am not sure of the reason for the feeding accessories though, as newborn babies cannot eat solid food. Lol!

Both dolls are very cute though, and I think any doll collector would adore these little girls.

title: Great set!
text: My son loves Roblox! He has started a collection of the characters and he is very happy with this set. There is a code to unlock a virtual item, for this set it's the Rocky Mountain Cowboy. The characters are nice quality and so much fun!

title: Too cute!!
text: My daughter loves Cocomelon, and she loves JJ. This JJ and tractor set is too cute. The wheels of the tractor roll freely and if you press the front grill of the tractor it plays Old MacDonald with a bunch of different animal sounds, and the Cocomelon theme. Just make sure to switch out of demo mode to get all of the sounds. It's a nice toy for the price!

title: We love Blippi!!
text: My daughter loves Blippi on YouTube, so we were excited to see this talking action figure! There is a switch on his back which enables all of the 8 phrases. Press his bow tie, and he will say a phrase. Batteries are already included too. Nice quality toy!

title: Son loves it!
text: My son loves Roblox and was thrilled about this set! He collects the different Roblox figures and loves playing the game. This toy doesn't really do much, but it makes a nice collection piece. You also get a code to unlock a virtual item which is cool.

title: Super adorable chalk set!
text: My 5 year old daughter loves drawing on the sidewalks with chalk, and she loves this set! The sweet treat designs make them so much fun to draw with! The set includes 12 pieces: 4 cupcakes, 4 ice cream cones, 2 macaroons, 1 chocolate chip cookie ice cream sandwich, and 1 candle. It's super adorable and lots of fun!

title: A fun little art set!
text: This Melissa and Doug stamp set is so much fun! The stamps are wooden with a rubber end. It comes with 2 stamp pads, which have 2 colors and the variety of stamps is huge! You also get 6 markers in the set. It's a super fun little art set!

title: Dino fun!
text: My 5 year old loves scratch art! We have tried the blank ones before, but these are different as they already have dinosaur designs on them. If you scratch off the black layer, underneath will reveal the full dinosaur design. They are lots of fun, however the black stuff can make a bit of a mess on your table! 😂

title: My daughter loves it!
text:
My daughter loves this costume! It's so creepy looking too! It's very comfortable for her to wear, and the medium fits her like a glove. For reference, she is 46” tall and 50 lbs.

The head part has Velcro in the back and the face piece is breathable and easy to see out of.

title: So much fun!
text:
This PJ Masks Dino Trouble off-roading set is so much fun. The vehicle is surprisingly big! You also get a 3” Catboy figure, one 6” dinosaur figure, one pile of bones, and one rolling cage.

You can capture the dinosaur in the cage and launch the pile of bones with the launcher. The vehicle rolls smoothly on hard and carpeted flooring. It's very nice overall!

title: Such a cool and funny idea!
text:
Oh my goodness! This doll is hilarious! My daughter loves dancing around with her, and it looks soooo funny! 😂

The arms and legs are stretchy, and there are bands that connect to your wrists and feet or around the ankles, then just move and the doll with move with you! It comes packaged in a cute little box too!

title: Great for all ages!
text: This Mattel Pixar alien remix set is great for both little kids and big kids! The box it comes in looks like a pizza box (Pizza Planet), and the 3 aliens are inside. They are mixed with Sully from Monster's Inc., Woody, and Duke Kaboom from Toy Story. These are great for play, or to keep as a collector's item. Very nice!

title: Full of surprises!
text: [[VIDEOID:603ed815bf4b05fb6f79cb946e0f388c]] My daughter loves VIP Pets! We have tried these in the past, and they are full of surprises! The pet comes in a hairspray bottle and in the bottom is a blind bag of accessories. Then after removing the lid, you hold the bottle under the water and the cap dissolves to reveal the hair color, also the pet's face changes color in the water! The hair is long and beautiful and full of glitter. It's easy to comb with the included brush. Any child would love this toy!

title: Too cute!
text:
This Baby Alive Sunshine snacks doll is too cute! She comes dressed in an adorable swimsuit and sandals, all ready for fun in the sun! She comes with 2 containers of clay to make an ice pop with the included mold and stick, a fork/spoon, a pair of sunglasses, and a comb.

You can actually feed her the ice pop made of clay. After you are finished feeding her, open up the flap on the rear to change her diaper. If the clay gets stuck, she also has a flap on her back that opens up as well. You can also take this doll in the water as well, just make sure you remove all clay before doing this!

My daughter loves her!! 🥰

title: Cute, but strongly scented.
text:
We are big fans of Cry Babies, and we love this Tutti Frutti Version. You get 2 capsules in this pack, each containing 1 baby and mystery blind bags full of accessories.

The babies really do smell like fruit! But if you are sensitive to strong scents, these may bother you, as they are a tad bit strong.

The babies are so cute, however their tears are colored... so be careful! We just took them in the bathtub to fill the heads and squirt out the colored tears to avoid a mess, and it worked! 😃

title: What an awesome idea! Love it!
text:
My daughter loves My Little Pony, and I must say... this set is awesome! It comes with 2 ponies, and a bunch of fashion accessories.

There are 4 blind mystery smashing bags- That when you smash with your hand, they expand and open to reveal the surprises (fashion accessories for the ponies). Each also has a mini balloon that magically inflates after smashing. This is the first I have seen this, but we love it, and hope to see more!

title: Defective- Pieces were cut incorrectly
text:
My teenage son who has loved legos and building things all his life was so excited to build this Pokémon Charizard.

He got as far as the belly, but there are 2 pieces that are supposed to lock into the back, and 1 will lock, but the other side will not stay on. We attempted multiple times, but finally discovered that there is a defect as the pieces were not cut properly. Needless to say, we are disappointed.

title: Loads of fun!
text: My 5 year old daughter loves this garden sensory bin! It comes in a nice container and you get sensory sand, a shovel, tongs, critters, rocks, and flowers! It's great for learning and just fun all around! Perfect indoor activity on a rainy day!!

title: So cute!
text: These little Bloopies are so cute! You get 4 little Bloopies in the pack. The floaties squirt water out of the front and each has a pull string which makes them move in the water. They even come with an organizer that attaches to your tub with a suction cup. The only downfall is that the Bloopies sometimes tip over after you pull the string. Still, it's a very cute bath time toy!

title: So funny! My kids love it!
text: This Play-Doh Dino Crew Crunchin' T-Rex Toy is absolutely hilarious! The T-Rex is interactive and makes sounds as he is chewing and also burps. He has a see through tummy as you can see the play-doh enter... and then poops 💩 it out! The little Pterodactyl friend is so cute too. It includes 3 eggs which each contain a different color of play-doh. Any child would love this set!!

title: Great for both collectors and kids!
text: This Barbie Birthday wishes doll is just beautiful. She's perfect for both collectors and kids. The box she comes in is beautiful too, with a special birthday message on the back. Her dress is gorgeous. Great value for the price!

title: Squishy fun!
text:
Who would have ever thought of a stress ball shaped like virus? 😂

But seriously, these are top quality stress balls and tons of squishy fun! Both of my kids love them! They even come inside a cool box.

title: Realistic looking baby dolls
text:
This review is for 2 dolls: The 20” Saskia Vinyl Body and 12” April Vinyl Body. They are both very realistic looking baby dolls. I would not call them reborns though, however they are easier on the wallet than a true reborn doll as a true reborn could cost thousands of dollars. The quality of these dolls are excellent for the price.

They are both very cute, and nicely detailed. The packaging is excellent too.

The 20” Saskia comes with a bottle and a magnetic pacifier.

12” April comes with a birth certificate and a magnetic pacifier.

Both of them have very nice clothing.

The 20” Saskia vinyl body is anatomically correct, however the 12” April vinyl body is not.

Both are super cute girls, great for children or collectors, ready to be adored and loved!

title: Great stress relievers!
text:
These bubble fidget toys are a genius idea. They are made of soft, but durable silicone. These actually work better than stress balls! Whenever you feel anxious or stressed, just grab one of these! They are so much fun to pop!

My 5 year old daughter has a biting nail habit. These have actually helped with that as they keep her mind busy on something else. The colors and designs are nice too!

title: She's so lifelike, it's unbelievable!
text: This doll is absolutely adorable and so lifelike that it's unbelievable! It comes packaged in this nice box and comes with a birth certificate. There is an option for a full body vinyl, and a cloth body. I ordered both, and both are amazing quality. The cloth body does come with a cute little stuffed bunny rabbit though (pictured). The quality is out of this world for the price. For a real reborn you would pay thousands of dollars for this same doll. She looks just like a real baby. So precious!

title: A great set!
text: This Roblox set is perfect for any Roblox fan! It's great to even keep as a collector's set. The figures are very nice quality!

title: Super adorable set!
text: If your child loves Go! Go! Cory Carson, then they will for sure love this set! It comes with Eileen the ice cream 🍦 truck, and a mini Cory and Chrissy. The ice cream truck lights up and plays songs, it's super adorable!

title: So soft and cute!
text:
This Memory Mates pillow is even nicer than I expected. I got this monster one for my almost 5 year old. The pillow is real memory foam, and is soft and squishy. The fur on the outside is soooo soft! I almost want one of these for myself!

The pillow has 2 pockets: 1 in the belly, and the other in the rear. It comes with a journal for your child to write in. It's super cute all around and I recommend! For both kids and adults!

title: Very detailed and nice quality!
text: This 5 piece dinosaur 🦕 set is very detailed and excellent quality! They come nicely packaged in a cool box and each is individually wrapped. It even comes with a neat guide booklet about the different types of dinosaurs 🦖! I would definitely recommend if your child loves dinosaurs! 👍

title: Fun and engaging!
text: My daughter loves these bristle blocks! The blocks come in a nice carrying case and the building opportunities are endless. They are easy to connect and pull apart. Very colorful and fun! These are a great engaging indoor activity.

title: Nice soft grip and easy for little hands!
text: These scissors are great quality as they have a nice soft grip on the handle and they are easy for little hands. My daughter is almost 5, and they work perfect for her. Also, it's a great price for 10 pairs!

title: Not your ordinary bus! Super cute!
text:
[[VIDEOID:3cb107333afbf71d30da2c0111fbcf07]] This review is for the Kindi Kids Minis School Bus set. It includes the adorable bunny bus and you get a mini Marsha Mello doll as well. As the wheels on the bus move, so does the bunny's face (see video). Also if you press the Bunny's Nose on the front of the bus, it will pop open the door and the stop sign. It's definitely not your ordinary bus! The back of the bus converts to a colorful slide too.

The included doll, Marsha Mello is very cute and she bobbles her head. There are holes underneath so she can sit or stand on the bus. The only flaw is that the doll is so too heavy, so doesn't stay up if the bus is moving. She does stand still on her own though. It's still a super cute set, and any Kindi Kid's fan would adore it! 💕

title: Cute bobble heads!
text: Kindi Kids are so cute and my daughter loves them. This review is for the Rainbow Besties set. With the set you get Marsha Mello, Summer Peaches, and Rainbow Kate. They are the perfect handheld size and each bobbles their head. They have holes underneath their feet to place on other Kindi Kids toys, although since they are a bit too heavy (large heads), they don't stay in place too long (if toy vehicle is moving it will knock them down eventually). They do stand on their own though. They each have a unique style of their own and they are very colorful and cute!

title: So cute!
text: My daughter just loves the Kindi Kids! This review is for the Show N Tell Pets, Marlo the Bunny! The figure itself is tiny, but so cute! She has big blue sparkly eyes and comes with a cup. Insert the straw in her mouth and her eyes open and close and her ears move from side to side!

title: So big compared to the original!
text: [[VIDEOID:23b373c6e5350a9900f304d2c861cb96]] I remember this Fisher Price puppy from when my son was a baby! This is the new and improved giant version. He's really so big compared to the original version. Push his tummy and he says a bunch of different sayings and songs! His tummy also lights up when you touch it. There are 2 different learning levels to choose from. It's a very cute, fun, and educational toy!

title: They really communicate with each other!
text: [[VIDEOID:4d4b7082d4c8ad6311ebd4ae25b3bf47]] These Interactables are so much fun! This review is for Jessie. She has a button that you push to make her talk. She says her regular phrases, but if you bring Buzz Lightyear close to her, they really talk to each other! She is a giant compared to Buzz, but is a nice quality action figure and the batteries are already included.

title: Very detailed!
text: These Godzilla action figures are too cool! They are tiny, but very well detailed. They even come in a handy drawstring bag to keep separate from other toys.

title: Soft and snuggable
text: My daughter loves Siren Head and this plush is too funny! It's very soft and snuggable and looks just like Siren Head. Quality is good too!

title: Love it!
text: [[VIDEOID:f826d7f3080d40e5c09da902eebd436a]] My daughter loves trains and Toy Story, and this train set is a match made in heaven! It's so easy to assemble the track and it's battery operated, so no need to worry about an electric hazard. The train requires 6 C cell batteries and the remote requires 3 AAA batteries (not included). The remote is easy for a child to use and you can make the train go forwards and backwards and control the speed. The remote also controls the train sounds, the bell, whistle, and music! There is even a light on the front. It's awesome!

title: A bit disappointed.
text: My daughter loves Ryan's World and is a huge fan of his toys and characters. This giant surprise egg seemed so cool, but for the price you don't get too much. You get 4 spy figures, cards that you can decode with the spinner, and a hovercraft vehicle. The hovercraft vehicle doesn't do anything special. It's sad that my daughter hasn't played with it again after the initial surprise. I wouldn't purchase this again.

title: Kids love it!
text: My kids love this scratch paper art kit! It includes so many things: 1 scratch paper notebook, 35 separate smaller sheets, 1 plastic stylus, 6 wooden styluses, lots of puffy stickers, stencils, and 1 brush. My 4 year old can never sit still for very long, but this kept her in 1 place for over an hour!! She loves it! It's a nice indoor activity and is very engaging and fun!

title: Amazing abs for a puppet!
text: [[VIDEOID:12a292a01e818719c11b5c56c18490af]] This 25” superhero ventriloquist puppet is hilarious. I have never seen a puppet with more amazing abs than this one has!! The quality is nice, the mouth opens and close easily and an adult hand fits perfectly inside. It comes with a detachable metal rod that is used to control the movement of 1 arm. Works great for puppet shows or just having a silly fun time with your kids!

title: Seriously, so much fun!
text: [[VIDEOID:84f2f4c254aa4184aecd0e2fcc391211]] This 25” ventriloquist style superhero puppet is so much fun! It's great for puppet shows or just to bring a smile to your child's face! The puppet looks exactly as pictured and is very lightweight. Fits my adult hand perfectly, and it's easy to control to movement of the mouth by opening and closing your hand. It also has a metal rod used to control the arm movement of 1 arm. The clothing is nice quality and very sparkly.

title: Just as cute as I thought it would be!
text: [[VIDEOID:c2a811f708989180da1fa9659cf0a351]] Aww! This unicorn 🦄 toy is so cute!! Any child would love this! It requires 3 AAA batteries (not included), and then you press the button on it's leg to make the wings flap and play a pretty melody. The horn even lights up! It looks exactly as pictured and is very nice quality. It even came packaged in an adorable little box! 🦄🦄🦄🦄

title: Easy to open and close mouth, but eyes look a little funny
text:
This Elmo puppet is great for puppet shows with your little one. My hand fits perfectly inside and it's easy to open and close his mouth. The fur on the puppet is very soft.

Side note: His eyes look a little funny, keep in mind that this is not the real Elmo, just a puppet that looks like him!

title: Cute!!
text: [[VIDEOID:c77998a141f5189305890aeb9de601f1]] This Paw Patrol Jet to the Rescue Skye set is too cute! It comes with batteries already included, 1 jet, and 1 Skye figure. Skye is all dressed in her flight suit and ready to fly! The jet is cool as there is a seat which fits Skye perfectly inside, and she locks in without falling out. The button on the jet activates the wings to pop out and it makes realistic jet sounds and lights up! It's a great toy at a great price!

title: Cool concept, but be cautious of surface it's used on.
text:
This antibacterial slime is a cool idea for sure, sanitize your hands as you play! In this set you get 3 colors, however the containers are very tiny.

The slime doesn't stick to hands and is very stretchy. Unfortunately, I cannot recommend this product as I used it on my wood table and it removed the varnish. It's fun, just be cautious of the surface you use it on. There is a warning on the back that does say it may stain certain surfaces, but not sure which surfaces it pertains to as it isn't specific.

title: The spider is huge!
text: This blue tarantula toy is awesome, but could be creepy for some who don't like spiders 🕷! It would be great for a prank! 😱 It comes with a remote control and the spider has LED eyes that light up. Use the remote control to move the spider left, right, forward, and even spin 360°! The spider itself is huge!! It's totally cool and the kids love it!!

title: Just as expected! Adorable little set!
text:
Oh my goodness! This Belle kitchen set is adorable! If your child loves Beauty and the Beast, this is a must have!

The Belle doll is nice quality and very beautiful. The kitchen is lots of fun as it comes with many accessories so your child can pretend Belle is cooking or baking.

I love the fact that it comes with the adored characters, Mrs. Potts and her son Chip! So so cute! For the price it's totally worth it!!

title: Cute and great for learning to tell time!
