text: My daughter is fascinated with clocks and she loves this one. The quality is excellent and it's definitely worth the price. It's full of color and great for learning to tell time! It requires to AA batteries, which are not included.

title: Sooo adorable!! Very interactive and fun!
text:
Awww!! FurReal has done it again! They always seem to come up with the cutest and coolest ideas! Josie the Mama kangaroo 🦘 is just adorable!
💕💕💕
She is very interactive and comes with 3 surprise babies! She can move her head and arms, hold her babies in her paw (one at a time), and kiss them! 💕💕💕
Touch her paw and she dances! She even makes funny sounds when eating! She really does so many different things, it's awesome! My daughter loves her!! 🦘💕🦘💕🦘💕

title: Doesn't look as pretty in person
text:
My wife wanted this bling face mask. It looks so pretty in the picture. When she opened the bag, the mask smelled foul... so she immediately tossed in the washer. It did survive the washer and dryer, which is good, and the stench vanished.

The inside of the mask is so soft and breathable. My wife has a tiny face, so there was some extra room around the chin area in this mask. She likes this mask as it's comfortable and breathable, however it's not as pretty as pictured.

title: The catapult is a hit!
text: This Peppa Pig set is small, but so cute. I would say it's well worth the price of 19.99. My daughter loves the characters and the catapult is her favorite! It actually works quite well and makes the figures fly into the air!  There were no instructions inside the box, however assembly was just attaching the stairs and snapping the rose bush together. The castle opens up, and folds back up easily for storage. There is a handle on top, so it's a great toy to take on the go.

title: They look real!!!
text: These fake cockroaches actually look so realistic that they would fool anyone! They are great for Halloween and pranks! Great quality, especially for the price! 👍

title: Very interactive and lots of fun!
text:
My 4 year old daughter loves fishing sets, and this one has got to be the most interactive and fun yet!
🎣🎣🎣🎣
It comes with an interactive fishing pole, 7 sea creatures, and a fishing mat. There are 3 different play modes, and it teaches about animals, numbers, and colors. The songs that it plays are so so cute! Batteries are already included, which is an added bonus.
🎣🎣🎣🎣
The fishing pole 🎣 is truly so smart that it identifies the sea creature as soon as you catch it. The sea creatures are pretty easy to catch as it's magnetic. This set is truly amazing for the development of fine motor skills.

title: Bringing this baby home!
text: Oh my goodness!! This Pip and Freddy plush is soooo adorable! If your child loves T.O.T.S., then this plush is a must! 😍 When you press Freddy's tummy, they say different sayings and Freddy actually flaps his wings! It also comes with batteries included, which is an added bonus!

title: A prehistoric blast!
text: This Cave Club set is a prehistoric blast! My daughter loves it! It comes with a doll (Rockelle), and a T-Rex 🦖 dinosaur! The doll and dinosaur 🦖 both have beautiful hair! The doll actually attaches her legs to the saddle on the dinosaur's back. The dinosaur is so much fun as you can push the lever on the back of the head, which makes it's mouth open and close. It comes with accessories for the hair and for the dinosaur to chomp on!! We dig it!

title: So soft, huggable, and cute!!
text: My 4 year old daughter is fascinated with elephants and she carries this one around with her everywhere! It's very well made, and soooo soft! It's perfect for hugging and she has been sleeping with it every night! 😍 It's the perfect size for toddlers.

title: Cuteness overload!!
text: My daughter loves this T.O.T.S surprise babies nursery set! The set includes 10 fuzzy baby animal figures in all, one double highchair, one double rocking cradle and 6 baby care accessories. 7 of the babies are displayed and 3 are in blind bags which make them a surprise. The babies are soooo cute and if you dip them in ice water their diapers change color!

title: Perfect for a 4 year old!
text: This Pedal Go Kart is so much fun for my 4 year old daughter! The assembly was easy, it comes with a handy tool and all you need is that and a Phillips screwdriver. It took me about 10-15 minutes to put together. The seat adjusts and is ergonomic. It's easy to steer and I love the peddling concept as it's similar to riding a bike! It's a great form of exercise for your child and they don't even realize it! 😉

title: She's gorgeous, and ideal for collectors!!
text: This 75th anniversary Mattel Barbie Doll is gorgeous! She comes packaged nicely in the 75th anniversary box. She is wearing an elegant red dress and her hair is voluminous and curly. I love the fact she has that classic Barbie Doll look to her face, not the new age look. I plan to keep her in the box as she is a great collection piece.

title: Make your GIFs come to life!
text:
This set by Oh! My GIF is super cute! You get 6 different dancing GIF toys in the set, along with cards. You then download the app and scan each card and the dancing GIFs appear on your phone! Too cool! The app seems easy to use.

The toys are nice, but some of them fall down easily. It would be cool if they moved on their own too.. The dog is a windup and he does dance on his own, however the others you have to do manually.

title: Adorable little set!
text:
This T.O.T.S. Chugga Chugga Choo-Choo train set is super adorable! The train comes with batteries included and plays music and moves! It even lights up when moving!

Pip and Freddy are permanently inside their train seats, however the baby animals come out. The babies are so so cute and look exactly like the show!

title: A must have for Led Zeppelin fans!!
text:
These Hot Wheels Led Zeppelin collection cars are totally awesome! If you are a Led Zeppelin fan, then you really need these in your life! They look exactly as pictured. The cars contain Zeppelin art from their first 4 albums! So cool!!

I plan to keep these in their packaging as a collector's item. The packaging of the cars is awesome too! 👍

title: Wiggle it just a little bit!
text: [[VIDEOID:964d22abae101cc5ebb669602ab2fb89]] This Barbie dance and prance piggy is too cute! It plays the 90's jam, Wiggle it just a little bit and she wiggles and walks! The batteries were included, but they didn't work, so we had to replace them. It only does the 1 song and dance and reminds me of a novelty animatronic.

title: Too cute for words!
text: [[VIDEOID:8b80df5cc9343df20607dffa45935c6d]] Peek-a-Blue is too cute for words! My daughter loves Blue's Clues and loves playing peekaboo with Blue! Push Blue's tummy and she plays peekaboo with you and makes the cutest sounds. ❤️

title: From a hot mess to glamorous!
text:
Oh my gosh this Failfix makeover doll is hilarious!! 😂 It's a transformation from a hot mess to glamorous!

When you take her out of the box, you realize she has definitely seen better days! She is literally a train wreck! 😂 Her hair is a mess, with earrings and shoes stuck in her hair, her face is hideous, and she's wearing a robe. This poor girl definitely needs some work and that is your job to help her!

First, you put to magic mask on her face and remove the shoes and earrings from her hair. Her hair is literally as hard as a rock (feels like a ton of hairspray in it); so you need to put a lot of effort in combing it.

Take off the magic mask, and her face looks beautiful! Her hair is so thick, long, and pretty one combed. It comes with paint to put in her hair (pink and blue), and wait 30 minutes and comb it. She comes with a day and nighttime outfit, 2 pairs of shoes, and earrings. She comes with a braiding stand that attaches to her chair if you want to braid her hair.

Once her makeover is complete, she looks gorgeous! The fun part is, you can use the mask to turn her back ugly or pretty. I have never seen a doll like this, but my daughter loves it and it's totally fun to give her that much needed makeover!

title: Full of surprises!
text: My daughter loves Ryan's World and this mystery spy vault is full of surprises! Use the key to open the vault and there is another key in a blind bag to open a secret spot in the vault. The digital watch is nice and came with batteries already included. The toys are nice, but nothing too spectacular. The surprise aspect is great, but the toys are just so so. It's a bit overpriced for what you get.

title: Interactive and adorable!
text: This Blue's Clues dance along Blue is too cute! It comes with Blue herself and a guitar that you use to control her. The music note button on the guitar plays the Blue's Clues theme song and makes Blue dance! Blue moves her head and lifts her ears and paw up and down. She even wiggles her bottom from side to side! When you press the guitar strings it will speed her up or slow her down. Push the blue spot on her back and his will make her bark and move. It's super adorable, just a bit pricey. But my daughter loves her! ❤️

title: Sooo adorable and nicely detailed!
text: My daughter loves T.O.T.S., and this figure set is so adorable! The set includes Pip the Penguin 🐧 , Freddy the Flamingo 🦩 , Mia the Kitten 🐱 , KC the Koala 🐨 , and Captain Beakman. It also comes with a vessel that you can put Mia inside and it fits perfectly on Freddy's back. The figures are very nicely detailed and excellent quality for the price!

title: Very detailed and cute!
text: If your child is a fan of Muppet Babies, they will adore these little figures! You get 6 characters in the set: Kermit, Piggy, Fozzie, Animal, Summer Penguin, and Gonzo. They are very nicely detailed and colorful! My daughter loves them!

title: Soooo cute! Just as expected!
text: [[VIDEOID:a585264496aee0e3e713c891a142ccd9]] This E I Oh Mickey Mouse is adorable in his little farmer's outfit! Push his foot and watch him sing Old MacDonald had a farm! It does change to different animals every time you push his foot. If you push the other foot he plays guess the animal sound game. My daughter loves to watch him dance and flap his arms like a chicken. It was nice as batteries are included too!

title: Adorable surprise toy!
text: Disney Doorables are absolutely adorable! 😍 They come inside a cute colorful box that opens like 2 doors on the front. Once you do that you see 5, 6, or 7 hidden doors on the box. This indicates the number of surprises you get. For us, we had 5. Each character is hidden inside a mystery door and inside a blind bag. I love the mystery theme, as it's a surprise who you will get. The characters are very nice quality and durable. They all have big sparkly eyes. These would be great for kids and collectors who love Disney! ❤️

title: Super fun and engaging for all ages!
text:
Treasure X just keeps coming up with more brilliant toys! My kids love this set as it's very engaging. Follow the steps on the instructions to find the hidden stuff inside the ship; Rescue the captain, find the black magic foam, and defeat the beast octopus to find the gold coins!

The box shows additional characters, but if you read the small print, they are not included with the set. The black magic foam actually looks like dirt, but the texture is awesome and quite therapeutic! Inside the chest is 1 real gold coin, and the others are plastic. My daughter cherishes that 1 gold coin and won't let it out of her sight!

title: The closest thing to a real fish!
text: This Lil' Dippers fish 🐠 by Little Live Pets is awesome! It's the closest thing to a live fish without the maintenance of a live fish, because it's a toy! It's water activated and starts swimming as soon as you place it in the water! It comes with a magnetic feeding bottle, so it automatically swims towards it as soon as you put near the fishes mouth! It's great to play with in the bathtub!

title: Treasure X has done it again!! 👏
text:
My daughter loves Treasure X toys as they are always full of fun and lots of surprises. This Sunken Gold Shark's 🦈 Treasure set is awesome and exceeded my expectations!

There are so many hidden surprises inside and it's very engaging as you get to dissect the shark to find the surprises! If your child loves slime, sharks, and surprises, then this is the right set for them! Totally awesome 👏!!

title: Cute miniature figures!
text: My daughter loves Ryan's World toys! These little micro figures are too cute! They are the perfect size for tiny hands and are very nicely detailed. You get 10 figures total in the set, 9 of them being a mystery! So much fun to open and reveal!

title: They glow and look awesome in black light!
text: These little mystery spy figures by Ryan's World are awesome. They actually glow and look awesome in black light! You get 6 figures total, 3 are known, and the other 3 are a mystery! The figures are nicely detailed and so much fun to play with! My daughter loves them! 👍

title: Ruthy the reindeer is too cute!
text:
My daughter is a big fan of Cry Babies, and she just adores Ruthy the red nosed reindeer baby! She is too cute for words!
🎄
She comes with batteries included and when you take the pacifier out of her mouth, she starts crying. When you put the pacifier back in, she stops crying. You can also lay her down to get her to stop crying. The other option is just to turn her off, using the switch on her back.
🎄
You can fill her head with water which will make it look like she is really crying. But just be aware: your floor may get wet. 😂
🎄
She has big green eyes and an adorable red nose. Her little reindeer outfit is too cute! We may just use her as a Christmas decoration if my daughter lets me! 🎄🎄🎄

title: Coney is so cute!
text:
[[VIDEOID:fe5800ec7df6e5c080896b067997145c]] My daughter loves the Cry Babies and we have so many of them. But, I have to say that this Goodnight Coney is one of the cutest I have seen!

She comes in her adorable bunny 🐰 pajamas that are very soft. Her body is soft and huggable. Her head and hands are hard plastic.

She comes with an attached plastic pacifier that you can place in her mouth to stop her from crying. Squeeze her tummy and she plays adorable lullabies and her face lights up, like a nightlight.

Other Cry Babies dolls require water for their head, but not Goodnight Coney! So no water messes to clean up! Instead of water, her tears light up in her face with blue LED lights. It looks so cool! I am a big fan of no messes! 😃

title: Full of surprises!
text:
My daughter loves the Cry Babies, and she loves this set too! You get 2 Paci House capsules in this pack, and each is filled with a mystery. The description says to open the house with water in the little tear drop dropper, but we didn't do that as we were afraid of a mess! You can still open these capsules regularly (thank goodness)!

The babies are wrapped up inside and there are surprises hidden inside the capsules. In blind bags, and there is a little knob on the front of the capsule that you turn, this allows the other surprises to fall out on the left inner side of the capsule. The surprises are the babies' accessories.

Now, for the babies themselves, they can be quite messy. When you fill them up with water and squeeze them, you soon find out that the tears are blue. I recommend playing with the babies in the sink, or a bathtub, of you don't want your entire house blue!! 🤣

This set is still so cute and my daughter loves it. So for that, it deserves 5 stars ⭐️ ⭐️ ⭐️ ⭐️ ⭐️!!

title: Last for about 3 days, nice quality!
text: These Halloween tattoos are too cute! They are not too small or too big, and they actually last for about 3 days before they start wearing off. They are very easy to apply, just put a damp cloth over the tattoo and hold for about 10-20 seconds and wa-la! It's a tattoo! The designs are very cute and colorful.

title: Great for both kids and collectors!
text:
This Disney Princess Comic's set is just darling. I love how they are packaged. They actually come in what appear to be “surprise” boxes, however it's really not a surprise at all, (As the description tells you what you are getting)! I would love to see them make more characters and mix it up, so it then will be an actual surprise.

The characters are miniature, but so nicely detailed! These would be great for both children and collectors. You get 9 characters total, along with bases for them to stand on, a blue transparent castle, a pink display box with a clip to hang if you wish, and the base of a pink staircase (which also works as a stand for 2 characters).

title: Brings back memories!!
text:
This Ryan's World popcorn parachute is really all that! It brings back memories of using parachutes at school in gym class! This is not as big as the ones that I remember, however my kids loooovvvvee this! It's currently their favorite toy!!

We like to put a ball or toy in the middle and watch it fly into the air! It's colorful, lightweight, and very easy for a little one to use. My kids are 15 and 4, they both love this parachute. It's really fun for all ages!

You can use this toy so many different ways. We have a 10 ft trampoline and actually used it as an umbrella cover on it!

title: OMG, it's Buddy!!
text:
Elf is one of our favorite Christmas movies that we watch every year as a tradition. I was so excited to see this talking Buddy doll! 😃

It really looks exactly like him! The quality is nice and he has a pull string on his back. He says soooo many different phrases that I was actually mind blown! They really did a good job of making sure he says all of the important lines from the movie! He's totally awesome!! 👍

title: Better than what I imagined! Daughter loves it!
text:
When I ordered this Peppa Pig Shopping Mall set, I thought it would be a standard play set used for imaginative play... It turns out that it's so much more than that! This set is quite interactive and my daughter really enjoys it!

It's very easy to set up, just snap the pieces together. My daughter's favorite part is the working elevator, and yes! It actually works! The characters has small holes in their feet to lock them on the play set. Each place in the mall has a knob to lock the character on.

Peppa and George slide down the slide perfectly. Momma and Daddy pig are a little big for the slide, as well as the horse swing, but they do work on the elevator.

The top is a food court which comes with a table and 2 chairs. You also get a pizza pie that you can spin which makes it look to be partially eaten.

This set is awesome and I definitely recommend! 👍

title: Posable and cute! We love Cocomelon!
text:
My daughter loves watching Cocomelon on YouTube. The nursery rhymes and characters are so cute, and this set brings the characters to life!

This set includes 6 Cocomelon kids. All of the figures are very nice quality and look exactly like the cartoon on YouTube!

They are posable and even have little holes in their feet so they work with other play sets that have this feature.

So so so cute! Daughter loves these! 😍

title: So cute!
text:
My daughter loves Cocomelon and we are so excited to finally see toys from them! 😍

This musical baby JJ is so cute! Push his tummy and he plays lullabies and says cute phrases! His body is soft, but his head is hard plastic. He came with batteries included, so that was a bonus. He looks exactly like the cartoon on YouTube!

title: Yay for Cocomelon!!
text:
My daughter loves Cocomelon nursery rhymes on YouTube and we are thrilled about this set!

My daughter carries this with her everywhere! She loves that the doctor case plays music and says different phrases. Included inside the case is a small stethoscope, otoscope, thermometer, and a syringe.

The set is nicely made and just as expected! Thank you Cocomelon!

title: Her hair really changes color in the sun!
text:
This doll by Adora is very nice quality. She has big blue eyes and gorgeous long hair. She is very pretty and my daughter loves her!

We own other Adora dolls and the quality is always top notch. This one in particular is really cool as her blonde hair turns pink in the sun. When out of the sun, it quickly turns back to blonde!

Her clothes are very cute, and her hair is so long and thick; perfect for a child to comb or style!

She would make a great gift!

title: Fun for all ages!
text:
These punching balloons are so much fun...For all ages! They are even fun for adults!

The quality of the balloons is very nice. They seem quite durable, like they will last awhile. The Halloween art on them makes them even more fun! The elastic band is already attached to the balloons and they are easy to inflate.

title: Adorable set!
text:
This Itty Bitty Pretty's tea party set is so adorable! It comes packaged in a little teacup ☕️ and inside you find a surprise doll and hidden accessories!

The doll is tiny, but so cute! The accessories and outfits are hidden in blind bags, a bath bomb cube, and a teabag. This set is full of surprises! You even get some scented cotton candy slime!

Once you dissolve the bath bomb cube and teabag you can dress up the doll. The outfit and shoes are a little difficult for a child to put on the doll, so it will require a parent's assistance.

title: Colorful and cute!
text: My daughter is fascinated with insects 🐞, and these finger puppets are great! She loves playing with them and they fit on her small fingers perfectly. My wife has thin fingers and can wear them too! Great quality, cute, and very colorful!

title: Full of ooze and surprises!
text:
These Dino smashers are so much fun and full of so many surprises!

First, you smash the egg, it opens and you find a mini egg and blind bags. The mini egg contains a little mystery figure.

The blind bags are full of stretchy snow, crystal slime, and frozen slime. Each has their own unique texture, and my daughter loves playing with it.

Inside the slime and snow, there are pieces of the dinosaur so that your child can build it. The dinosaur very easy to put together.

title: The cutest doll ever!
text:
Rainbow Kate is seriously the cutest doll ever! My daughter adores her! 😍
🌈
She comes with all the accessories you need to make her better. She also comes with batteries, which is an added bonus.
🌈
She will tell you what she needs to make her feel better. She will shiver (vibrate), which indicates she needs her blanky and a hug.
🌈
She will ask you to check her heartbeat with the stethoscope, and you can actually hear and feel her heartbeat vibrate!
🌈
She will also ask you to check her tummy with the stethoscope, and she will fart 💨!! Then you need to give her vitamin stars to make her tummy better.
🌈
She also has a booboo on her leg. Use the dish to add a bit of water and wipe it with the small cloth and it vanishes right before your eyes! She also has sticker bandaids that you can place on her booboo.
🌈
Her hair is colorful and beautiful. Her eyes are bright, sparkly, and so pretty. She is also a bobble head! Seriously, so so cute!!

title: He does much more than just talking! Lots of fun!
text:
My 4 year old loves Rock and Rhyme Elmo! He does much more than just talking, which makes him more interactive and fun!

When you push the button on his guitar, he talks and sings. While he is singing, your child can strum his guitar which makes music too! He speaks in both English and Spanish.

My daughter's favorite part is his nose... When you squeeze it, it makes a honk sound! Super adorable! ❤️

title: So sweet!
text:
This little golden retriever pup is so sweet! When you take him out of the box he has a tear drop that your child can wipe away with a damp cloth.

The box he comes in folds out to a huge coloring display, which is a lot of fun!

The pup comes with an adoption certificate that your child can fill out. The pup has 2 settings, happy and sad, so you can change his mode. When you hug him he goes off. In addition to sounds, he also moves his head and wags his tail.

The only downfall is that he doesn't sit up too well, he kind of falls on his face as he is top heavy. He's still so precious though, and my daughter loves him!!

title: Creepy cool!!
text: These Halloween decorations are creepy cool! In the pack you get 2 long hem strings, 11 pieces of the bloody hands and feet, and 12 pieces of bloody weapons. You also get a plastic needle to thread the pieces onto the string. The pieces are constructed of flat pvc and already have precut holes to thread onto the string. I hung them inside my house for now, but plan to move outside closer to Halloween! Love them!!

title: Warm and full of love!
text:
This little beagle pup is the cutest ever! He comes in a box with an adoption certificate that your child can fill out to give the pup a name.

Use a damp cloth to wipe away the pup's tear. He's incredibly soft and perfect for hugging with the sweetest face ever!

There is a Velcro opening on his back with a microwaveable pouch inside to keep him warm up to 20 minutes. I usually warm him up right before my daughter's bedtime as she likes sleeping with this precious pup. 🥰🐶

title: The toucan is tou-cute!!
text:
This Toucan Rainbocorn set is full of surprises inside! 🌈 It comes inside a giant egg with a colorful horn! 🌈 Inside you find the most adorable blue Toucan. The sequin decoration snaps onto the front of the toucan. When you move the sequins, they reveal a hidden picture! It's like magic!
🌈
You will also find blind bags with other surprises I side. Some include slime or “rainbow poop”, and you also get a mini figure, and a set of wild colorful nails!
🌈
My daughter loves the nails! That is her favorite thing about this set. They already have glue on them, so you just press on and wa-la! You have beautiful diva nails! The nails fit her tiny 4 year old hands perfectly.
🌈
This set is absolutely adorable and would make a perfect gift!

title: Sooo many surprises!!! Daughter loves it!!
text:
This Itty Bitty Pretty's Tea Party set is full of soooo many surprises! This is so engaging and tons of fun to reveal the surprises hidden inside this HUGE teacup!

The huge teacup opens up and inside is filled with so many blind bags! You get 2 adorable little dolls, a teapot, a teacup, 2 pets, and clothes and accessories for each doll. You also get 3 different colors of cotton candy slime. The huge teacup is great for storage so you don't lose any pieces.

The magic bath bomb like cubes dissolve in warm water. There are hidden surprises inside these too!

You place the 2 tea bags in warm water and they actually disintegrate to reveal the outfits for your doll! It's like magic!

This set is adorable and colorful. This would make the perfect Christmas gift 🎁!!

title: Full of surprises and so so cute!!
text:
This 2 pack VIP Pets is a fun and engaging set full of surprises!

You get 1 pet in each mousse bottle along with 9 surprises.

You twist the cap of each mousse bottle and fill with warm water. Place the pet inside and their hair towels dissolve to reveal their beautiful hair! The towel leaves a bit of residue, so you will want to wash your pet's hair with soap and warm water. The hair does dry quickly, which is a plus.

When you wipe your pet's face with a warm rag, it reveals their unique beauty mark!

Each pet comes with a chair and suction cup which attaches to the chair to keep in place while you style your pet's hair.

The pets are sooo adorable! Even cuter than expected! The hair is so colorful and long. The styling opportunities are endless!

My daughter really loves this toy and is begging me for more already! I guess I will add these to the Christmas list! 👍

title: Spitzy is so cute and funny! A must have!
text:
My daughter loves Spitzy the funny Llama 🦙! He's quite hilarious! You fill his leg with water and squeeze it, which makes him spit. He actually spits a far distance too!

He comes with batteries and when you push his chest, he makes a chewing sound and his mouth moves. He also burps! 🤣

He's very soft and huggable. This would make a perfect gift for a child.

title: Such a cute set! Daughter loves this pup!
text:
This Rescue Tales pup and bathtub set is too cute! My daughter loves dogs and immediately fell in love with this set! 😍

The chocolate Labrador puppy is soft and plush. Very huggable!! ❤️ The puppy comes with a birth certificate that your child can fill out to make the pup their own. The pup has a teardrop in his eye that you can wipe away with a damp cloth.

The bathtub is adorable! It's the perfect size to fit the pup inside. It comes with accessories: a scrub brush, a sprayer, a shampoo bottle, and a blow dryer. The blow dryer doesn't do anything, it's more for imaginative play.

The sprayer does work, however only very little water comes out. My daughter wanted more water, so we ended up just taking the whole set in her bath to play, and she ended up giving the pup a real bath!! 😂

He was soaked, however you can ring him out really well and just throw in your dryer on a gentle cycle and he will be like new again! 🐶

title: A walking koosh ball! Love it!
text: This noodle pup by Little Live Pets is adorable. He's like a little walking koosh ball! You push the top of his head and he plays music, walks, and wags his tail to it. Batteries are included. He doesn't do too much, however my daughter loves him as he feels so cool! He walks best on hard floors. He doesn't work too well on carpets.

title: Very nice quality balloons!
text: These balloons are very durable and awesome quality! They work with both air and water! They actually do not pop easily which is a plus! The smiley faces on them are too cute!

title: As realistic as it gets!
text:
[[VIDEOID:ca0009f8e1cc4c681dac74ae94aa89ea]] Mealtime Magic Mia reminds me of Newborn Luvabella. They are very similar, however Mia does a lot more.

Mia is as realistic as it gets. She interacts with you just like a real baby. My 4 year old daughter loves playing with her!

Mia comes with accessories: A bottle that converts to a pacifier, an interactive spoon that requires batteries, and a plate of food. You simply place the spoon on a type of food on her plate and Mia will identify it! Once you are done feeding her, there is a button on her back which allows you to burp her.

She also has a button on her chest which makes her laugh. She can sense when being rocked and will fall asleep in your child's arms.

Mia is absolutely adorable and would make a perfect gift!

title: Cute and colorful!
text:
Riley the unicorn 🦄 is so cute! She reminds me of My Little Pony. My daughter really enjoys playing with her!

First, you touch Riley's magical necklace to choose a color. Then, touch her horn, eyes, and wings to change them to that same color. She looks so pretty when she lights up.

You can also touch her mouth and she will say different things and even sing a song.

If you squeeze in her back legs she will flap her wings. Unfortunately, our Riley keeps losing 1 wing and we have to keep putting it back on.

All in all, it's a cute colorful toy that any unicorn 🦄 lover will adore!

title: Fun and engaging!
text:
My daughter is a huge fan of this set! She wants to play with it every day!

The track is very easy to assemble and it comes with a battery powered car (battery not included), dinosaurs, bridges, and trees.

I love that you can change how the track is set up. It's always fun to change things up!! The car drives on the regular floor and on the track. So much fun!! 👍

title: Like hot potato, but with popcorn!
text:
This is a fun and suspenseful game for kids! Actually, it's great for all ages!

It's like hot potato 🥔, but with popcorn 🍿 instead! First you pull the string on the popcorn box, which sets the timer. Then you roll the die and follow the instructions on the die. You keep passing the die and popcorn to the next player, and if it pops on your turn, the popcorn shoots out of the box and you're out.

The popcorn is colorful and made of plastic. My entire family loves this game as it's full of surprises!

title: Rollo is the cutest little sloth ever!!
text:
My daughter just loves Rollo the Sloth! He's very interactive and lots of fun!

He has 2 modes:
1. Action mode, where he reacts to loud sounds, such as clapping. Once he hears you, he will start rolling around all crazy!!
2. Repeat mode, where he will repeat what you say.

He's very soft and his arms are bendable and attach at the hands, so you can hang Rollo anywhere!!

Totally cute and lots of fun! 🦥

title: Nostalgic memories in the palm of your hand!
text:
This handheld game console is so cool! It reminds me of my old Gameboy! It contains 400 classic games and comes with a USB charger and battery. The controls on the console are easy to use and there is a volume control on the side. It even comes with an adapter for your TV and a remote for a second player. It's easy to hook up to your TV, however I wish the cords were a bit longer as I have to stand up while playing on the TV as the cords are short. The volume also doesn't work when using on the TV. The volume works perfectly using the actual handheld console.

For the amount of games you get and the price, it's definitely worth it! Brings back nostalgic memories of playing these games as a child!!

title: Super fun surprise toy!!
text:
My little girl loves dinosaurs and this blind bag set is full of surprises and is lots of fun!!

You get 4 blind bags in this set that consist of: a baby dinosaur, a hair piece for your baby dinosaur, an accessory, and moldable sand or slime.

With ours, we got the pink triceratops, a fluffy yellow hair piece, a bottle, and blue moldable sand.

The dinosaur 🦕 is posable and oh so cute! The accessories and sand are nice quality. Any child who loves dinosaurs or Cave Club would love this set!

title: Cute set!
text:
I haven't heard of Cave Club before, so this is all new to me. My daughter likes Barbies, so I decided to try this out.

The set is so cute! It includes Emberly and her pet dinosaur, Flaire. Emberly, (the doll) is very pretty and my daughter loves her long, beautiful, colorful crimped hair. She is very posable.

The little dinosaur, Flaire is sooo cute! Pretty and pink with a movable head.

It also comes with other accessories, a comb for her hair, a clip on hair extension, and a torch.

My daughter loves this set and it would make a great gift!

title: Fun and exciting game!
text:
My kids and I love Inky's Fortune! They key to the game is to gently remove the gems without waking up Inky.

You have to be careful and twist gently when removing the gems. If you are not careful, you will wake up Inky and he will shoot out a rubber ink blob!

The game is simple, but quite hilarious. It's a lot of fun for the entire family!!

title: Defective toy.
text:
We got both the pink and purple Hatchimals Pixies, however the purple works like a champ... The pink one (this one) was defective.

You flip the switch on the bottom to turn on after charging, and unfortunately she didn't do anything. 😢

We even tried the purple charger on the pink one and she still does not work at all.

I guess this will just be a decoration for my daughter's bedroom.

title: Fun flying toy!
text:
My daughter loves toys that fly! This Pixie by Hatchimals does just that. She comes in a plastic crystal egg, and inside you find a Pixie, a stand, and a USB charging cable.

There is a button on the bottom that turns on the Pixie. You hold her in your hand, raise your hand a little, and her wings begin to spin. She then takes off and flies!

She flies well, however she only lasts about 10 minutes before having to charge her again.

title: The most awesome toy of 2020!!! Wow!!!
text:
[[VIDEOID:e783e9a23abede169bf4fed742f3a2e5]] This is by far the coolest toy of 2020!! Maybe even the coolest toy of ALL TIME!

The Monster Jam Official Megalodon Storm All-Terrain Remote Control Monster Truck is totally awesome!! I am beyond impressed by this toy.

It comes with a charger, a remote control and the monster truck itself.

It drives on all terrains, it even drives on water!!! I have never seen this before in a remote control car! So I believe this is the first of it's kind.

My kids and I love this toy and definitely give it 5 stars! This would make the perfect gift for a child who loves Monster Jam!!

title: Perfect for a 4 year old!
text:
My 4 year old daughter loves this Power Wheels racing ATV. It really looks exactly like a real ATV, just mini sized for your little one!

The assembly was very easy and is nicely made. It comes with stickers that you need to put on yourself.

The magenta pink color is very girly and this for sure stands out! 🤩

Rest assured, it has a parent-controlled, high-speed lockout and Power-Lock brakes for extra safety. The max speed is 6 MPH, which is average for a Power Wheels rider.

It comes with it's own charger, and it plugs in very easily. Very nice product all around!! 👍

title: Daughter loves her!!
text:
[[VIDEOID:9bccd96636e10326cea3ee7fdd4fcec6]] If your child is a fan of Disney's Zombies, they need this doll in their life!!

She really looks almost exact to Addison on the show. This is the werewolf version of Addison, and she sings “Call to the wild”.

She only sings the 1 line of the song and there is a button on her neck to activate her singing. As an adult, you kind of get tired of hearing the same song all day, however if it makes your child happy it's worth it! 😜

Her clothes are very soft and nice. She's very flexible and posable too. This doll would make a great gift for a child.

title: Awesome learning toy!
text:
My 4 year old daughter loves Smarty Flutter by Flycatcher! It's a very interactive toy and is great for learning directions, colors, and shapes!

It requires 3 AAA batteries, (not included), and has 2 language settings: English and Spanish.

The toy itself is so cute and very colorful. Smarty Flutter will ask your child to find a specific color or shape, and it has a sensor on the bottom that actually identifies them!

Smarty Flutter also is great at teaching directions, he will say: go left, or go right, and it actually senses if the motion is correct!

The only thing is that he is sometimes hard to hear if there is a lot of noise in your house, and I don't see a volume control. The toy is best to use in a quiet setting where your child has full attention. It's fun for your child and educational at the same time!!

title: If your child loves My Little Pony, this is a must have!!
text:
The My Little Pony friendship castle is so much fun for my 4 year old daughter! If your child loves My Little Pony, this is a must have!! It's a very well constructed set and is easy for an adult to assemble. It took me about 20 minutes to get it up and running.
🌈
The castle includes a door that opens, a pretty pink staircase, and a swing for the ponies to ride on. This set is great for imaginative play and allows your child's My Little Pony dreams come to life!!
🌈
The set comes with 2 ponies: Twilight Sparkle and Pinkie Pie. It also comes with a bunch of accessories for your ponies!
🌈
All in all, awesome set! This would make a great gift for a child!

title: Super easy and fun!
text: [[VIDEOID:dfbd8f52ab3f81c198f8e4f62d8208c4]] These are by far the best water balloons out there! Just hook to your hose, turn on the water, and within a minute you soooo many water balloons! This does ALL of the work for you! My kids love it and it's the perfect cure for summertime quarantine blues!

title: It's HUGE!!
text: This inflatable swimming pool by Joyin is all that and a bag of chips!! It's HUGE, so huge that my whole family can fit in it! It's easy to inflate with a pump and feels durable. It's 3 layers high which makes it the perfect height for a pillow or resting your arms on. Great quality and we love it! ❤️

title: Great strategy game for kids!
text: My kids love Yeti in my Spaghetti 🍝!! It's very easy to play and to follow the rules. First you roll a number: 1, 2, or 3 and this indicates the number of noodles you need to remove from the bowl. Once you touch a specific noodle, you need to stick with that noodle. The key is to be careful about removing the noodles so that the Yeti does not fall in the bowl. It's a great strategy game for kids and is hours of fun!

title: Kids love it, but not sure how long it will last.
text: I have mixed feelings on this 30' waterslide by Backyard Blast. It was easy to set up, and it is HUGE at 30 feet long, and my kids love it... However, the plastic is thin and doesn't feel that strong. The pool area is a nice addition to the slide and it has a section to inflate (you will need an air pump), and a section to drain the water after using. You will need to use your own hose to hook up to the slide and the water sprinkles out from the middle yellow striped section. If you have the slide on an incline, the water will not sprinkle onto the first 5 feet on the slide. The only way to get the top of the slide wet is to stand on the yellow stripe at the top of the slide and this will allow the slide to get wet. The corners and ends have sections in which you insert the stakes. The tape is only on 1 side, not both. If it were on both sides, it would be more durable. I have a feeling that it may rip after using a few more times. Also, I hope you don't mind sticky fingers! The tape was extremely sticky, that even washing my hands repeatedly with soap and water after would not get rid of the stickiness! Finally, the product is overpriced, I would pay $40 for something like this, but not $100.

title: First game of it's kind!! My kids love it!
text: [[VIDEOID:54f69ecb0edfbe4e07975d434b41e632]] I have never seen a game with a flying drone before, so I believe this is the first of it's kind! The game is for 2-4 players and recommended for children over 8 years old. I played this game with my wife and kids (ages 4 and 15 years old), and they both loved it! The objective is to shoot your aliens 👽 into the spaceship 🚀, and once you do, there is a short delay which gives other players the opportunity to knock you out and take your place. Whoever gets their aliens 👽 on the spaceship first and back home wins the game. The game is a lot of fun and very engaging. FYI: The drone only holds it's charge for about 30 minutes, so you will have to recharge at that point. Very easy to assemble too!

title: Very educational, colorful, and fun!
text: Blues Clues has been around since my teenager was a tot and we loved the show then, and we still love it now! This book is very educational and fun! My 4 year old daughter loves learning and playing with this book. It's very colorful and has the most darling animation. There are 3 different modes: ABC's, phonics, and skidoo. All 3 modes are a ton of fun! Batteries are included as well.

title: Beautiful baby boy doll!
text: This baby boy reborn doll by Charex is very beautiful. My daughter loves him! His body is so soft and huggable. His face looks very realistic and his skin smells baby fresh. His head, arms, hands, legs, and feet are made of soft silicone. He comes with a giraffe toy that comes with a suction cup to stick to a window, a birth certificate, bottle, and magnetic pacifier. The only downfall is that it's difficult to get him to sit up. Any child would adore this doll!

title: The best birthday set out there!
text: My 4 year old daughter absolutely loves this birthday party set! It comes with a cake and accessories to decorate. It's very interactive as you push on the candle to the cake 🎂, and it starts singing, “Happy birthday to you”. When you blow on the candle, it senses it and stops singing and begins to cheer and clap! It's about as close to the real thing that you can get. It also comes with plates, utensils, a teapot, teacups, a second smaller cake to decorate, and a bunch of other sweet treats and accessories! Oh, and the batteries are included already in the cake which is a bonus! My daughter has been playing with this toy everyday since we got it and she adores it!

title: Amazing quality magnetic tiles! Lots of fun!
text: My daughter and I love playing with magnetic tiles and the building possibilities are endless. We have tried other brands and these ones by Vatenic are AMAZING quality and you get so much for the price! It came packaged so nicely and even includes a carrying bag and fun stickers! We love them and would definitely recommend!

title: Tweeterina is a pretty bird and lots of fun!
text: [[VIDEOID:968c4dc100ff03241c69465270b8c01a]] My daughter loves Tweeterina by Little Live Pets! She's a very pretty bird and will repeat what you say. When she gets to be too annoying there is a switch on the bottom to turn off. We also ordered the other Little Live Pets bird Rainbow 🌈 Tweets. The difference is that Tweeterina does not come with a plastic cage and batteries are not included, whereas Rainbow 🌈 Tweets included both the cage and batteries. My daughter is a huge fan of these birds and really enjoys playing with them!

title: It's a creepy dude! Run!!!
text: This is a mask of a creepy looking dude. In a way he looks like a creepier version of Sylvester Stallone mixed with some Scott Baio? It's a cool mask, however it's very difficult to breathe in. The nostrils and eye holes are tiny, and I don't see anyone being able to wear this mask for a long period of time. If you want to be a creepy Rocky or Chachi for Halloween 🎃, then this is the right mask for you!

title: Above and beyond customer service!!
text: My family loved this pool at first as you can fit 2 adults in it comfortably, however we were very disappointed that the bottom deflated within 2 weeks. The seller reached out to me and apologized for this happening and offered to send me a replacement, which I gladly accepted! Dressbar has AMAZING customer service and we are very happy with them for taking care of us! We will definitely purchase from this seller again in the future as their service rocks! They really went above and beyond!! ❤️

title: Bunch tubes not included. Cheap quality water balloons.
text: My kids have been asking to play with water balloons so I ordered these hoping they would be a blast. Unfortunately, the bunch tubes which are needed to make this product work are not included and you cannot purchase separately. The only solution is buying a complete water balloon kit that includes the bunch tubes. We tried them without and they do not work. The balloons feel of very cheap quality as well. I was disappointed with this product.

title: The closest thing to a real pet bird!
text: [[VIDEOID:92385742ce12f10a66c037b2d4f3ac64]] Rainbow 🌈 Tweets is absolutely adorable! My daughter loves this little bird so much. It's head turns as it tweets and there is a button you push which will record your voice, music, etc. The bird then plays back what was recorded. It comes with a little pink cage that you can keep the bird in. This is the closest thing to having a real pet bird 🐦!! This would make a great gift for a child.

title: Tiny, but my 4 year old loves it!
text: This little swimming pool is perfect for a 2, 3, or 4 year old. Unfortunately, it's too tiny for big ol' me, however my daughter loves having her own personal little pool! It's only big enough to fit 1 child and is a perfect way to cool off during the hot summer season.

title: Very educational and fun!
text: My little girl loves frogs 🐸, and she loves this set! The figures are small and are the perfect size for your child to carry around. They are very detailed and great for educational purposes. It teaches the stage from the eggs, to tadpoles, to a full grown frog. This set covers the entire life cycle and it's great for learning!

title: Fun for the entire family!
text: [[VIDEOID:4b7ef0f2158561b3b92b87fd2a7011cc]] My family loves the original classic Operation game, but this one is so much better! It comes with foreign objects which you place into the dog's mouth to play the game. The objects consist of: a pair of socks, a broken phone, a teddy bear, homework, a dog bone, shorts, and even poop 💩! Once he swallows the objects, they enter his intestines and they key is to use the magnetic tool to gently remove the items from his intestinal tract. If it buzzes, he whimpers and you lose your turn. My wife did a short video to show how it works and what it does (included with this review). Once you make it to the end, you will hear a congratulatory sound and a fart from the dog! 😂My 4 year old daughter even loves this game! It says 6 and up (probably due to the small parts), however we play with her and she does great! This game is so much fun and I would definitely recommend!

title: Adorable and nice quality!
text: This princess play set is super adorable and easy to set up. You can connect the 3 pieces or keep individual. They connect with ties (as shown in picture). The only thing that could make it better is if they connected with Velcro instead of the ties. With a little bit of rough play, the ties come undone and you have to reconnect. Other than that, it's a very nice quality set and my 4 year old daughter loves it! It's definitely worth the price.

title: Fun and engaging activity!
text: My 4 year old daughter is crazy about dinosaurs and this set is totally awesome! You get 12 individually package dinosaur 🦕 eggs 🥚, and each comes with it's own chisel and brush. Each egg contains a different kind of dinosaur. The eggs are easy to scrape, however you may want to do outdoors as the dust can get messy. It's a very fun and engaging activity to do with your child!

title: So realistic! Very nice quality doll for the price.
text: My wife and I collect creepy dolls and we have become fans of the Vollence brand. These are high quality, finely detailed dolls at an amazing price! The doll is very realistic, her skin is soft silicone, and her weight is of a real baby! Her body is soft plush, so she is huggable. She comes with a swaddle blanket and a comb for her realistic hair. She is so nicely detailed, even her fingers and toes look real! My 4 year old daughter is afraid of this doll, however my wife and I love her as part of our collection.

title: So realistic that it's scary!
text: This reborn doll by Vollence is so realistic that it's scary! My wife and I love to collect creepy dolls as we are horror fans, and this doll fits perfect in our collection. She is very detailed, and about as real as you can get. My 4 year old daughter is absolutely terrified of her and runs every time she sees this doll! 😂 But my wife and I love her as she's wicked creepy! The doll comes packaged so nicely in her box, and a comb is included for her hair. She comes wrapped in a swaddle blanket with teddy bears 🧸 on it. This doll may scare a child, however Horror fans would love her!

title: Surprisingly comfortable to wear!
text: [[VIDEOID:cebef6928309705be0e02c1e632c320]] This is 1 rad plague doctor mask! It's actually surprisingly comfortable and there is a strap behind the head so you can customize the fit. When wearing, it's almost like sunglasses, everything appears of a darker tint. The mask is very nice quality and didn't have a strong rubber scent like most masks do. My entire family loves this mask and I can't wait to use for Halloween 🎃!!!

title: Creepy cool and very detailed!
text: I love Halloween and this 2 headed skeleton is a great decoration for the Halloween season! It's very well detailed and easy to assemble. It looks exactly as pictured!

title: So adorable! Fits true to size.
text: My 4 year old daughter loves playing dress up and she loves this princess 👸🏻 costume! It comes with the dress, gloves, wand, clip on earrings, necklace, and tiara. The costume is very nice quality and fits true to size. My daughter is a large 4 year old and she wears size 6 clothes. The 5-6 year old size fits her just right. The back of the dress has Velcro, so it's easy to get on and off. The only unfortunate thing is that the tiara had broke (most likely in transit). However, I'm not deducting any stars as it's gorgeous without the tiara. This would make a great Halloween costume for your little princess!

title: Fun and engaging game for kids!
text: [[VIDEOID:4ed0120355e4e08847be08464e36402f]] My daughter loves this fishing 🎣 game! It's so much fun and very engaging. It's very easy to assemble too, which is an added bonus. The dolphins 🐬 slide down the twisty slide and once they reach the bottom they climb back up the wall to go down the slide again! It also plays a bunch of different children's songs. Some songs are louder than others, but you can change songs or play with the music 🎵 on or off, which is a nice option. It's a great game and is totally worth the price!

title: Such a great quality watercolor set!
text: My kids love painting with watercolors, and this set exceeded my expectations. It comes in a nice case and the presentation is outstanding! It looks like a professional set! There are 48 different colors, 2 brushes (1 is water refillable), 8 pieces of watercolor paper, and so much more! The paints and brushes are nice quality and easy to use. Any little artist would love this set!

title: Super cute and fun!
text: My daughter just loves Hatchimals! These Colleggtibles are so cute! They come in a plastic egg carton and the fun part is hatching the eggs. Inside the eggs you find surprise Hatchimals, and it comes with a collectors guide as well. The figures are nicely detailed and so cute!

title: Plastic for the price of gold.
text: [[VIDEOID:9d2d176c0a9cc0dfe2a8a17e48165af]] I never knew that 1 long piece of plastic could cost so much. Literally, that's all it is.... 1.long.piece.of.plastic. The plastic must contain diamonds 💍 for this price? Or maybe gold? Ok, to the point now... The plastic is great for sliding and works well, however it tore after 1 use. The ends contain heavy duty tape, but only on one side. This becomes an issue as there is no protection on one side where the stakes are inserted. After sliding for some time it begins to tear. This could have been an easy fix if both sides were reinforced with this heavy duty tape. Also, it doesn't come with a sprinkler, so you need to use your own. It comes with a nice carrying bag, 1 piece of replacement tape, and stakes (be careful as these are sharp)! My kids did have fun on it, however since it tore after 1 use I would not recommend. It's overpriced for what you get.

title: Colorful, fun, and educational!
text: This United States and World Map Puzzle set is a great educational activity for your child. I love that it's filled with so much color and the animation is charming! The puzzles are wooden and feel very durable. My 4 year old daughter loves this set, however I do have to help her as there are a lot of pieces, and sometimes they are difficult for a child to “lock in”. The pieces are sorted by different colors and animals which help you in putting to puzzle together. This is a great learning toy and is a lot of fun!

title: Very fun concept!
text: My 4 year old loves this toy. It's very fun and actually very therapeutic. It comes with a plastic scraper and knife, where you can scrape or cut the gel surrounding the surprise. The gel has a cool feel to it and smells good... like soap! We did it in a bowl so it didn't make a mess on our table. The bowl idea worked well for this toy! The toy inside is too cute and it's a surprise of what you will get. I love the concept of this and overall, it's a great toy for kids!

title: Adorable little baby pool!
text: This little swimming pool is so cute! Would work great for a baby 1-2 years. The manufacturer recommends 2 years and up, however it's so tiny that it would be too small for a 3 year old. It's small and adorable, very easy to set up and the sun shade is a nice feature to have. It comes with 2 little toy ducks and you can add more small toys and watch them go around the lazy river. You need to paddle with your hands to make them go around though. All in all, it's a great starter pool for a baby and very nice quality.

title: Awesome little ride!
text: My kids love this drifter cart. I ordered 1... However they always fought over it, so I ordered 2. They are so much fun to ride! Very easy to assemble and to charge. They hold their charge for up to 30 minutes to 1 hour... Which mostly depends on the weight of the person riding. Overall, these are a great product!

title: My kids love it! Easy set up and lots of fun!
text: This inflatable elephant is so much fun! It's a very easy set up and perfect to cool down on a hot day! My kids love it! The vinyl is thick and good quality. Seems like it will last awhile.

title: Fun toy for your child!
text: This Toy Story Pizza Planet rocket 🚀 shaped toy is a lot of fun for your child. It only comes with 1 alien figure, however any small toy works with it. You open the top, insert toys, and pull the lever which spins them around. Then you push the yellow button and your toys come out. The lever is easy for a child to spin, however the yellow button is a bit difficult for my 4 year old to push... I have to help her with that part. Overall, it's a great toy and perfect for any Toy Story fan!

title: Cute idea, but is a bit frustrating to push.
text: This idea is very cute, however is a bit frustrating for a child. The handle that connects is very flimsy and makes it difficult to push. The doll itself is cute, as well as the dog... however the trike was a fail. The dog is also difficult for a child to connect to the basket. The dolls feet are supposed to move when pushing, however they don't move too well as it's difficult to push.

title: Very realistic and beautiful.
text: My daughter loves this doll by Adora. She's beautiful and is very realistic looking. Her yellow dress is very pretty. She's not too heavy and easy for a child to carry around. Her body is soft and perfect for hugging. She has a fresh baby powder scent. Very nice quality and would recommend.

title: Beautiful doll with realistic features!
text: This doll by Adora is absolutely beautiful. She has realistic features and a soft body which is perfect for hugging. My daughter loves her! Her monster outfit is so cute too. She smells like baby powder. Very nice quality and would recommend.

title: Fun activity to do with your kids!
text: My kids and I had a blast with this set! You get 3 colors of clay: blue, green, and orange. You also get the accessories for the dinosaurs, 3 finger puppet tubes, and glue. The guide is easy for adults to follow, however children still need adult guidance with this. Our end result doesn't look exact to that in the picture, however it still came out very cute! The clay is nice quality and easy to mold.

title: Silly and fun!
text: My kids love slime and this game is approved by them! It comes with 2 cans of play dough slime that you put inside his head. The gooey slime then comes out through his big nose. It also comes with tweezers shaped like fingers which are to be used to pull the slime out. His nose is soft so you can squeeze it to help get the slime out as well. The slime is not sticky at all and great quality. Lots of fun for days that you are stuck inside the house!

title: Nice colors for a child and wash off easily!
text: My daughter is a fan of makeup and always tries to use my wife's, so I got her this set. I was pleasantly surprised as to how nice it is! The makeup is real, and the shades of color are light, which are perfect for a child. It also washes off very easily which is a plus! It comes with a shiny iridescent makeup bag, which is great for storing the makeup. Very nice set!

title: Detailed figures, great for a collector!
text: I was planning on giving these figures to my daughter to play with, but after receiving them I changed my mind. These are great detailed figurines and are a great collector's item to have. They come packaged nicely in a cool Monsters Inc. box, and I'm leaving them inside as they are too nice to take out! Great quality figures with excellent detailing! Would recommend.

title: Cute little set!
text: This little doctor set is so adorable. The doll reminds me of a Kewpie doll. You get so many pieces and accessories and it's great for imaginative play! My daughter loves it!

title: So adorable! Lights up nicely and very soft!
text: [[VIDEOID:b724a0ccad3d7cceb112a00d98762a7f]] This little plush doggie 🐶 is soooo cute! He's extremely soft and cuddly. He comes packaged so nicely and batteries are even included with a little mini screwdriver. I was really impressed by the presentation of this product. There is a button that you push and he lights up. You can change the modes and colors which is neat. He lights up so nicely and is like a cute huggable nightlight!

title: Tiny, but adorable.
text: This little doll is smaller than expected, but she's still very adorable. She's great as a bath time playmate and comes in an adorable unicorn bathrobe. Any child would love her!

title: Lots of fun and is a nice size!
text: This water table is very durable and sturdy. It's a lot of fun and my 4 year old daughter really enjoys it! It's nice as you can use indoors without water or outdoors with water. Very nice quality!

title: Great quality toys inside!
text: These eggs actually have great quality toys inside! It's a mixed variety as well. Perfect for an Easter egg hunt!

title: Great collector's item!
text: This Barbie looks just like the very first original Barbie. It's great for collectors, like myself as it's for the 75th anniversary. She comes in a nice box and I plan to keep her in there, as she is a collector's item. Awesome product!

title: Super stretchy and so much fun!
text: This kinetic sand is not your ordinary! It's super stretchy and lots of fun! You get 3 colors: pink, blue, and green. You also get lots of different molds that you can make and a roller which makes dinosaur footprints! It's a very fun and engaging set for your child. My daughter loves it!

title: Great collector's find!
text: I have been a Toy Story fan for as long as I can remember and this Buzz Lightyear action figure is a 1 of a kind! He talks and says different phrases. This figure is a great collector's item and I plan to keep in the box as it's for the 25th anniversary of Toy Story.

title: Great collector's item! Nice quality!
text: I have been a Toy Story fan since it came out. This Woody figure is totally awesome and ideal for any collector as it's for the 25th anniversary. I plan to keep him in the box as he is a great collector's item to have.

title: Totally awesome and fun!
text: This set is so much fun! My kids love it and any Hot Wheels fan would love it! Very nice quality and easy to use.

title: Nice quality cars, but pricey!
text: For 4 cars I must say the price is a bit steep. My kids love Mario and this set is nice quality, however I feel this is priced as a collectors item, and not a toy to be played with.

title: Great for collectors!
text: I have been a Toy Story fan since it came out. I originally ordered this Bo Peep for my daughter, however after receiving she is too nice to take out of the box. This is a 25th anniversary doll from the original toy story and is a great collector's item. She really looks identical to the Bo Peep in the original Toy Story!

title: Huge and realistic looking!
text: This stork lifelike plush is huge! Very realistic looking and my daughter loves it as she is fascinated with birds! Very nice quality!

title: So adorable!
text: If your child loves dogs, this Corgi plush is perfect! So soft and perfect to love on ❤️!! The plushie looks just like a real Corgi and is too cute for words!

title: Fun, but gets sticky.
text: My daughter loves everything about slime. This one is cool as the texture is different and it's scented. It's a lot of fun, however be careful because it's quite sticky and can make a huge mess!

title: The possibilities are endless!
text: This is the ultimate arts and crafts set! Literally the possibilities are endless with what you can make! My daughter loves making things with this set. Very nice quality!

title: Looks just like the mouse in the movie!
text: [[VIDEOID:65161b36943529bea18b6f76ce82c5a1]] If you give a mouse a cookie is one of the cutest movies! This little dancing mouse looks exact to that in the movie. When you give him the cookie he starts talking and sings and dances. It also works by pushing on his chest. Very nice quality!

title: Very therapeutic and fun!
text: My daughter loves slime and I am not the biggest fan of it as it can be messy. This slime is actually quite nice! It doesn't stick to the hands too much and it's actually very relaxing and therapeutic to play with. The little balls stay in for the most part, you get some strays that fall out here and there.. which is normal. Unfortunately, I have to remove 1 star because the smell is so strong and not good. If you are sensitive to strong scents, this slime is not for you.

title: Awesome toy!
text: My daughter loves this bus! It's cool how you can fold up into a bus or open it up to play with your Puppy Dog Pal friends! It comes with both dogs, Bingo and Rolly. There is literally no assembly required which is nice and it already has batteries included. Very nice quality toy for the price!

title: The cutest unicorn 🦄 ever!!
text: [[VIDEOID:5138ca86ec5727aeb0215d5c53c52b78]] My whole family loves Mia the unicorn! To activate her you hold her by the back of the neck. She starts by making sounds and then sings a cute song and starts walking around. She even walks well on carpet! All around very nice quality toy!

title: Such a cute play set!
text: My daughter just loves the Enchantimals and this play set is super cute! It comes with the barn standup, 1 doll, baby animals, and accessories. It's great for imaginative play and nice quality. Any child would love this set!

title: Nice quality and very engaging!
text: My 4 year old daughter loves these magnets! The possibilities are endless as you can use your imagination to build whatever your heart ❤️ desires! You get a lot of different shapes, sizes, and colors! The quality is outstanding! So engaging and hours of fun!

title: So much fun!
text: [[VIDEOID:3b7d932a8965e8458d84bf1ecdccf73e]] This Mickey is truly a blast! He sings the hot dog song and dances, and even plays red light, green light. He's very engaging and so much fun. Very nice quality toy!

title: Perfect for Easter!
text: Any unicorn 🦄 lover would love these eggs on Easter morning. They are actually very nice quality and the unicorns inside are posable. You can even fold back up and put in the eggs again.

title: Soft and adorable!
text: My daughter loves this plush unicorn 🦄!! It's so cute and soft... Perfect for hugging! Very nice quality!

title: Interactive and fun!
text: This is the coolest Olaf I have ever seen! He's so realistic as his eyes move when he talks and sings songs. He comes with batteries, however you need to purchase your own for the snowflake remote. It's cool that you can control him with the remote and he actually follows around the projected blue snowflake image from the remote. Very cool toy all around!

title: Adorable well made play set!
text: My daughter loves this set as she is crazy for T.O.T.S.!! It's very easy to assemble and well made. The only thing is the flag at the top was a bit tricky to insert... it appears this piece was not cut correctly. Other than that it's great! The little figures that come with the set are bobble heads and just so cute!

title: Amazing quality doll for the price!
text: Journey Girls are the affordable alternative to an American Girl doll. I am just blown away with how nice this doll is for the price. She is well detailed with nice hair and realistic looking. Her clothing is nice quality and stylish. Any little girl would love her as a gift! 💝

title: Adorable product!
text: This little scooter is the perfect accessory for your Kindi Kids dolls! The colors combination is too cute and the ears move as you roll the scooter across the floor. You also get 2 Shopkins with it: a strawberry 🍓 and a smoothie. They are just too cute for words! Overall, this is a very nice product.

title: I love the concept! Very cute!
text: This toy is adorable and very affordable. Any child would love this as a gift. Inside the carrier is a surprise rescue pet. We got the walrus and at first look he's in pretty bad shape. Once you brush out the tangles he is fluffy and cute! It teaches your child how to care for animals which is a great concept! Very nice product!

title: Portable and sturdy!
text: This table top easel is very nice. I love how it's foldable and portable, which is great for on the go. It's very sturdy as well. The one side is a chalkboard and the other is dry erase. Both are very easy to draw on and it comes with markers, chalk, and an eraser. The only thing is that the markers don't come off with the eraser. It finally came off with a baby wipe. This is a great product, but you will need to invest in better markers and more chalk as it only comes with a few chalk sticks.

title: Adorable nicely detailed baby doll
text: This baby doll is very nicely detailed and is very well worth the price. I wouldn't call her a reborn though, she's just a nicely made baby doll. She comes with a birth certificate, baby bottle, and a magnetic pacifier which connects to her mouth. She would be great for both a child or a collector. Very nice quality!

title: Adorable set!
text: My daughter loves the Minnie and Penelope the unicorn 🦄 set! It's so adorable and well made. It's nice as the batteries are already included. Minnie sings and Penelope dances. You connect Minnie's hand to Penelope's back and they walk together. They need to be on a flat surface though. They don't walk too well on carpet. Overall, very nice quality!

title: Engaging and fun
text: This bath toy set is very nice. There are 2 suction cup toys that you can hang and the suction holds well. When you pour water in these toys their eyes spin around which is cool. These toys are very engaging and any child would love for bath time. It also comes with 2 water cups, 3 squirter toys, and a turtle that winds up and swims in the water. It's a nice set, however I feel it's a bit overpriced for what you get.

title: Fun little set!
text: My daughter loves this set. Both the truck and helicopter are detailed very nicely and the sound effects of the truck are cool. When you push the truck it also makes a realistic sound! It feels pretty durable, but it would have been better if the doors opened for the truck and helicopter to put toys inside. The doors do not open.

title: Perfect for little girls learning to style hair!
text: This Elsa head piece is beautiful. My daughter loves learning how to style hair and this is the perfect learning tool! She comes with different accessories to use with her hair, and for the price you can't beat it. The top of her hair is very thin though. If it was a little thicker, it would be perfect.

title: Nice quality vinyl stickers!
text: My little girl loves stickers and dinosaurs. The thing that drives me bonkers about stickers is pulling them off and you find goo residue with paper (which is so hard to remove)! These stickers don't do that! They are made of vinyl and are easy to pull off and re-stick (if need be), and they don't leave any residue behind. They are also waterproof, which is nice! Awesome quality stickers!

title: So many accessories!
text: My 3 year old daughter loves this set! You get 2 Baby Alive Littles dolls that are twins. The one is blonde and the other has reddish brown hair. They each come with a surprise box, you open and get so many accessories! Shoes, headphones, hair clips, cups, blankets, etc. My wife and daughter had a blast dressing the twins up! Then you can take them for a walk in the stroller and watch their little legs kick! The dolls are the perfect size for a small child to carry around. Very nice toy!

title: Cool science experiment!
text: I did this with my 3 year old daughter and she loves it! You can see the tiny dragons swimming after a few days! The tank lights up with a blue LED light, which looks pretty. We can't wait for the dragons to grow! This reminds me of the sea monkeys I had as a child! It's a lot of fun and a cool science experiment to do with your child!

title: So much fun! Very interactive!
text: [[VIDEOID:37ddf68b5b37793ff11bfd5de89d44a8]] My daughter loves this robot! He sings, walks,  dances, plays music, and so much more! He holds his charge for a long time and comes with a remote, which takes 2 AAA batteries (not included). My daughter loves how easily you can control him with the remote. His voice reminds me of Buzz Lightyear too! Great toy, very interactive, and a great price too!

title: Gorgeous collector's item!
text: Wow!! This Princess Leia Barbie doll looks even more beautiful in person! The box she comes in is just as beautiful as her, and it's nice as it has the picture of Carrie Fisher on the box as a tribute to her! I plan on keeping her inside the box as she's a perfect collector's item for a Star Wars fan, like myself! Very nice quality, I am just blown away!

title: Sweet ride for your dolls!
text: This car is too cool! It comfortably seats 2 Glitter Girl dolls and rides smoothly across the floor, even carpet. Very nicely made and pretty colors!

title: Amazing quality doll!
text: This doll is too cute! Amazing quality for the price! She has bun pigtails, red hair, bright blue eyes, and freckles! Her outfit is so cute and her arms and legs are posable. Any child would love her!

title: Fun drawing on so many different textures!
text: My daughter loves this set! She loves drawing, so this set is perfect for her. You get crayons and chalk eggs to draw with on many different textured pieces of paper. The crayons are wider and easy to hold onto. The same goes for the eggs. They are shaped like an egg for easy grasp and doesn't break easily like a regular chalk stick. The different textures of paper are fun to draw on, they are also thick and nice quality. I just wish it came with more paper. It's a bit pricey for what you get.

title: Loads of fun to dissect!
text: My kids love this set! It was a lot of fun cutting the giant bug open and dissecting him! You will find a gut sac, intestine sac, and a brain that you get to open up. I would recommend opening inside of a bowl to avoid a mess as the orbees fly everywhere! 😂 You find an alien inside, some slime, and a few other tiny creepy creatures! It's a very fun and engaging activity to do with your kids!

title: Cute little set!
text: My daughter loves Shopkins and this little set is too cute for words! You get the princess, pony, and carriage with this set. The wheels of the carriage move and it's big enough to fit other Shoppie dolls inside. Really nicely made toy at a great price!

title: Engaging and fun!
text: I tried out this set with my daughter and we both love it! The instructions are easy to follow and it's a very engaging and fun activity. The clay is great quality too!

title: So cute and smells sweet like marshmallows!
text: My daughter loves this! This Pikmi Pop is just too cute for words and smells sweet like marshmallows! Comes in a popcorn container and you can keep your animal in it's sleeping bag or turn it to pajamas. Great quality toy at a great price!

title: Easy to assemble and fun!!
text: My daughter loves this racetrack! It's cool as it's a race between 2 cars to see who crosses the finish line first, and it's a surprise every time! So much fun! The track is nice quality and comes with 1 car (Lightning McQueen). It's very easy to assemble too!

title: Followed instructions and didn't work.
text: Unfortunately we were disappointed with this product as it didn't work. We followed the instructions to the T and no crystals grew on the unicorn. You also need additional supplies that don't come with the set, a jar and distilled water... a lot of people won't have these supplies just lying around your house. Would not recommend.

title: So adorable! Nice quality!
text: This little unicorn is simply the cutest! The flip sequins are fun as you watch the colors change right before your eyes! Perfect size for a child to carry around! Very nice quality!

title: So so cute!!
text: [[VIDEOID:eb674e6f550716ded03b618657c84e42]] This little duck is the cutest! It actually sparkles with glitter and is well made. He dances and sings “You are my sunshine”, and it's just too cute for words!! Excellent quality product!

title: Absolutely adorable!
text: [[VIDEOID:fe98ea7a8b0f37817fa9d0bab845037d]] This little birthday bear is absolutely adorable and any child would love it for their birthday! He sings happy birthday and dances side to side while the song is playing! It takes 3 AA batteries and batteries are not included. My daughter loves him and he's just so cute! Nice quality!

title: So cute and funny!
text: [[VIDEOID:1f4d5894d4589b0bea68f647133e700d]] Oh my goodness! This chicken is so funny and reminds me of Foghorn Leghorn! He plays the tune “Oh the doo dah day” and when you pick him up he clucks all crazy flapping his wings! Very entertaining and hilarious! He also has a restart button on the top of his head! Too cute and very nice quality!

title: Gorgeous doll, packaged lovely!
text: This doll is gorgeous! She's very nice quality and my daughter loves her! She comes packaged nicely in a magnetic box and her ballerina outfit is adorable. She has bright blue eyes, blonde hair, and freckles. She's really so lifelike. Great price for a beautifully crafted doll!

title: Colorful and fun!
text: My daughter loves these magnets! They are great for teaching your child their ABC's and 1,2,3's! So educational and colorful! Easy for little hands to grip and feel durable. Very nice overall!

title: Interactive and fun!
text: My kids love this dragon. He looks awesome and is very well detailed. Batteries are required for him to work, but once they are in he comes alive! He interacts with your touch by flapping his wings and roaring at you! We find him quite hilarious! His chest lights up too, which is cool. Awesome interactive toy!

title: Lots of fun! Very big!
text: This racetrack is a lot of fun and it's huge so it takes up a lot of space. Easy assembly and it's a lot of fun to watch the cars go around the track, however they only go around a few times before falling off the track. That is the only slight disappointment about the product, other than that, it's great!

title: Adorable set of dolls!
text: This Enchantimal doll set is absolutely adorable! You get 3 dolls: Felicity Fox, Patter Peacock, and Bree Bunny! They each come with their own animal bestie too! The dolls and animals are all well detailed and are very colorful. They come with accessories to play birthday party! My daughter loves playing with this set!! The dolls hair is nice to play with too!

title: Beautiful, well crafted doll!
text: This appears to be Adora's version of an American Girl doll, and she's just lovely. She's very beautiful and well crafted! She looks so realistic and has a soft body. Top quality, but much more affordable than an American Girl doll! My daughter loves her!!

title: Easy to assemble and so much fun!
text: This Cars set is awesome! Very easy to assemble and sticker placement was pretty easy to follow. It comes with Lightning McQueen which has flames 🔥 coming out of the exhaust! So cool!! It has a kick-back launcher which propels the car at super speed! He literally is the speed of lightning racing through the loop! Any child would love this toy!! So rad!!

title: Cute multifunction Cars set!
text: This little set is perfect for imaginative play! It was very easy to assemble and comes with a Jackson Storm race car!
