The elevator turns into a bridge, so you can play with it in 2 different ways. There is a car wash and a fuel pump. The instructions for sticker placement were easy to follow too. Nice little toy at an affordable price!

title: Gorgeous doll at a great price!
text: Glitter girl doll Emilia is absolutely adorable! Her eyes are so blue and her face is realistic looking. Her hair is braided down each side and feels thick and realistic too. Her outfit is colorful and too cute! Her arms and legs are posable. Very nice quality doll at a great price!

title: So adorable!
text: This Barbie Club Chelsea dress up set is adorable! Chelsea and her kitty both come with dress up unicorn headpieces! They also come with a cupcake which you can turn into a keychain. Any child who loves Barbie would love this set! Great toy for the price!

title: Nice quality off-road play vehicle!
text: My daughter loves this toy off-road vehicle as she can fit her Barbies inside as well as her other toys around the same size as Barbie! It teaches safety as you actually get to buckle your toys in before taking a cruise! No assembly required other than attaching the side mirrors which was a piece of cake! Drives smoothly on a flat surface, not so much on carpet. Very nice quality and would recommend!

title: Adorable play tool set!
text: My daughter always wants to help me... even when I use tools to fix and repair things. I came across this set and ordered for her... She loves it! Batteries are included with the drill and it spins just like a real drill. The safety goggles fit her perfectly too (she is almost 4 years old). The screws are easy to grasp for little hands and actually screw into the long plastic pieces. The handle of the toolbox is a ruler and detaches. Adorable little set at a great price!

title: Faulty pieces which would not lock together.
text: My wife and daughter started to put this together, however quickly became frustrated as the pieces were cut incorrectly and would not lock together on the right side of the castle (see photo). My wife tried over and over again to try and lock in, however it kept falling apart. Due to this defect, the castle is very flimsy. I'm sorry to say, but I would not recommend.

title: Easy to assemble, very detailed set.
text: This school building was easy to assemble. There are a lot of pieces, so it will take some time to put together. The set is so detailed and it's great for imaginative play. The price is a bit steep for a toy though.

title: Squishy, cute, and smell great!
text: This little set is absolutely adorable! It's a little lunch box filled with squishy plushies that look like food! They smell great and I like these better than regular squishies as they are more durable. They are covered in a plush fabric which makes them so soft and helps so they don't rip.

title: So soft and adorable!
text: Cutetitos really hold up to their name as they are just too cute! Inside you receive an adorable little animal wrapped in a tortilla blanket. The blanket is removable and has Velcro. Both the animal and the blanket are so soft and nice quality.

title: Lightweight, portable, and works great!
text: This Jojo Siwa karaoke machine is great! It's small, lightweight, and portable. The microphone is like a real microphone and not that cheap plastic. Connects easily to Bluetooth and also has a memory card to store hundreds of songs! It's so pretty how it lights up and sounds great too. Any little diva would love this!

title: Very nurturing and sweet!
text: My daughter loves the Little People nursery set! It comes with 2 babies: a boy and a girl, a walker, changing table, and a baby bottle. The play mat has Velcro so it folds up into a diaper bag when done playing. The swing rocks when you push down the button on top. This set is very nurturing and sweet. Very nice quality!

title: Nice quality mini cars!
text: These mini cars are very nice quality. They look identical to those in the movie Cars. My daughter loves them!

title: Just like to 80's version I had as a child!
text: This Speak and a Spell is just like the 80's version I had as a child! It teaches how to spell and letters. Very educational and fun!

title: Taco bout cuteness!!
text: These little plush cuties are so adorable! They come in a taco tray and each animal is a surprise! They are wrapped in a removable tortilla blanket which has Velcro. We got the skunk and chipmunk. They are soft and cuddly and any child would love. They also have colored diapers which reveals their gender!

title: Lots of accessories!
text: My daughter loves this Teresa doll! She comes with a cute puppy dog and lots of gymnastics accessories! The accessories fit perfectly in Teresa's hand. Very nice quality set.

title: So realistic!
text: [[VIDEOID:fb2a0604630d9ef1b1157859889c2453]] This little microwave is so realistic! It actually lights up and spins like a real microwave. My daughter loves it as it's so engaging. It comes with play food and containers of puffy play dough-like stuff in different colors. Very nice quality for the price!

title: Beautiful Barbie doll!
text: This Barbie Doll is just beautiful and my daughter loves her. She's so elegant in her pretty gown and the dress pops out when you push the button below her chest. Very nicely made and would also make a great collector's item. She comes with a hairbrush as well.

title: Smells so good!
text: Oh my gosh! This toy is sooo adorable! The outside of the egg has a sequin reveal which shows a picture. Then you hatch the egg and inside is an adorable soft plush unicorn! The unicorn plush smells so good and comes with 3 colors of unicorn poop which is like a very soft, non sticky slime. It also comes with a surprise accessory. This toy is a lot of fun and my daughter loves it!

title: Have to shake hard to get it to work.
text: This guitar is very colorful and cute, however can be very dangerous. You have to shake very hard to get the music to start and then the buttons work. The toy is made of hard plastic and a young child jumping around or shaking this toy can injure not only them, but someone else. I'm sorry to say, but I don't recommend. My daughter also got bored with this toy very quickly.

title: Great toy! Nicely made and fun!
text: This little bird is sooo cute! It sings and tweets as you pet it and the wings light up! There is a button on the chest that you hold down when you talk and the bird repeats what you say! Any child would love this bird! It's so much fun and nicely made.

title: Beautiful, but wouldn't call her a reborn.
text: This doll is gorgeous and crafted beautifully, however I wouldn't call her a reborn. She's more like a finely detailed baby doll. Her little hands and feet look very realistic. Her body is stuffed and she feels the weight of a real baby, however she's a toddler.. not a newborn...This doll is the weight of a newborn baby. She has a scent of baby powder and her hands and feet were wrapped and she was packaged perfectly. She comes with a magnetic pacifier, baby bottle, and certificate. Her eyes look so realistic and her hair feels real too!

title: Super soft and squishy!
text: These squishies are so adorable! They are quite large and are extremely soft! Great for kids and adults too! They are very slow rising as well. Very pleased with the quality!

title: Adorable little pup!
text: This little pup is so adorable with it's bright blue eyes and sparkly bow! The perfect pet for your doll. I loved that he came in a box that looks like a dog house! Very nice quality toy for the price.

title: Beautiful and lifelike!
text: This doll is beautiful! She comes in a colorful and cute carrying case with an additional outfit. Nice quality! She's so well detailed and very lifelike. Any little girl would love her!

title: Total nostalgia!!
text: My wife loved the Pound Puppies as a child and when she opened up this box she was in total nostalgia as they look just like the originals from the 80's.., so much so that she wanted to keep in the box as a collector's item. They really do look just like the originals from the 80's! Packaged the same way and all. Very nice quality toy and oh so cute!

title: Adorable little dog park for your dolls!
text: This set is so adorable. It's a little dog park to use with your 18” dolls. The set comes with 5 adorable plush dogs and the pieces of the dog park which require full assembly. The instructions are very easy to read and the pieces are all labeled, so assembly was a piece of cake. The set is nice quality and feels durable. The only thing is that the teeter totter tips if you don't hold the center of it while playing with it. The base for the teeter totter should have been made a bit larger to prevent tipping. Other than that, it's an engaging and fun toy!

title: Long and tedious process
text: The instructions that come with the robot are vague. When you build this, make sure you download the 3D instructional app as this will save you time. There is control app that you need to download to program and control the robot through Bluetooth. The process is long and tedious. This took me a few hours to build. Once completed, the robot is quite cool though!

title: Really squishy, relaxing, and adorable!
text: These are nice quality squishies and are absolutely adorable! They are very soft and extremely squishy! They are relaxing, even great for adults. They are scented lightly too!

title: So many memories for my wife! She grew up with Polly Pocket!
text: My wife was ecstatic when Polly Pocket came back! She's in total nostalgia as this brings back memories as a child! This set is adorable, and the cool thing is that you can connect to other Polly Pocket stores! The candy store opens and expands to 4 floors. It comes with 2 adorable dolls: Polly and Lila, stickers, and a bunch of fun furniture and accessories! Very nice toy for the price!

title: Flawed and defective product
text: I was very disappointed with this product. Coming from Step2, which is normally such a high quality brand, this product was defective and flawed, however I was able to make the adjustments to make the product usable. First of all, the 2 front wheels are supposed to be identical and they weren't. Only 1 of them had a hole drilled through it. I had to manually drill the other wheel to make it work. The other flaw was that the handle area had some very sharp, melted plastic. It's not safe at all. I had to melt the sharp plastic to make smooth on my own as I don't want my child's safety at risk. I do not recommend this product due to the defects, as this should have been caught at quality inspection before going out to customers.

title: Experimenting with slime is a blast!
text: This kit is very easy to assemble and is also easy to follow the instructions. It reminds me of creepy crawlers from back in the day! You mix the slime with water in the test tube and fill into the molds. Let it sit for a bit. Then you have a squishy slime creation! This activity is engaging for kids, however it's a bit pricey for what you get.

title: Takes a lot of time and patience to assemble.
text: This hedgehog took me almost a week to fully assemble. It's made for someone with a lot of time and patience. There are so many little pieces that the whole process was very tedious. One flaw is that the battery compartment is one of the very first steps... and in order to change the batteries you need to take the whole hedgehog apart and then reassemble all over again which can be a huge pain! Once completed the hedgehog is very cool as he can walk or curl up in a ball in response to your clap commands. For the time, patience, and effort put into this I would not recommend this product as even though he's cute it's not worth all the effort and time. Not to mention some pieces fall out as he moves around and you have to keep on fixing, which is a pain.

title: Awesome surprise toy!!
text: These surprise capsules are a lot of fun and would make excellent stocking stuffers! You get 2 capsules in a pack and each contains a surprise inside! You get a mystery filling inside: sand, clay, or slime, along with a mystery figure! The cool thing about the figures is that you can detach their heads and match with different bodies. A lot of fun and a great price too!

title: Posable and well detailed!
text: Centaurus is one rad dinosaur!! He's very well detailed and his arms and legs move so you can pose him in different positions. He lights up and growls which is awesome too! Any child who loves dinosaurs would love this toy!! The box he comes in has a prehistoric background as well! Would make a great collector's item too!

title: Engaging and educational!
text: This is an awesome little set that any dinosaur 🦕 lover would love!! It comes with 6 miniature dinosaurs. Disclosure: My picture includes dinosaurs that I purchased in addition to the 6 included with this set. The kinetic sand is bright green and feels squishy/foamy. It doesn't stick to clothes or the carpet, which is wonderful! This is an educational and engaging set as you can teach your child about the different types of dinosaurs and play with the kinetic sand at the same time! The box works perfect for holding the dinosaurs and sand, and you can even add your own dinosaurs for more fun!!

title: When unicorns 🦄 turn evil 😈!!
text: Oh my goodness! This unicorn fingerling is so hilarious with his evil ways! He fits perfectly on your finger and he's very interactive. Batteries are included, so no need to purchase your own. His head turns all the way around which is quite creepy! His eyes also light up red and his sharp teeth retract! My kids got a kick out of him!!

title: Hilarious toy! A huge hit!
text: This toy is basically like a wicked fingerling! The snake is scary as his eyes glow red and he hisses at you showing his sharp teeth. Batteries are included so no need to worry about purchasing on your own. He's very interactive and even farts! 😂 It's quite hilarious too! Fits perfectly around your finger!

title: Adorable large tent! Folds up nicely for storage.
text: Any unicorn lover would adore this tent! It's very large and there's even enough space inside for the parent to join their child in play! The colors are beautiful and it feels pretty durable. Assembly is easy, it literally just pops open and there are a few extra pieces and steps, however the instructions come with it and are easy to follow. It folds up nicely for storage too!

title: Cute fortune cookie collector's case!
text: This collector's case is super cute as it looks like a giant fortune cookie! You open it up and there is a ton of space to store your jewelry. It comes with 5 surprise bracelets and a key to open the secret compartments! Feels pretty sturdy too. Any jewelry loving child would love this!

title: Very educational and engaging activity for kids!
text: This mineral kit is fantastic! You really get so much included with it and the best part is that it is educational for your child as they learn about mineralogy. It educates about the geologic rock cycle and the three main categories of rocks: igneous, sedimentary, and metamorphic. There are also so many different fun experiments to do (18 to be exact) and it comes with a handy instructional guide. You can also create your own crystal rock which is awesome! If you are looking for an educational and fun toy for your child, I would highly recommend this product!

title: Sturdy, lightweight, and lots of fun!
text: My 3 year old daughter loves this rocking dinosaur! It's a lot of fun for her and she will literally sit and rock while watching her favorite movies! It feels very sturdy and the handles have a nice grip. It's very lightweight so it's easy to move around too. The only bummer was that the stickers didn't come with it! So my daughter took the initiative and drew his face all by herself! Was pretty easy to assemble other than the handle, which was a bit tough. Overall, it's nice product!

title: Simple yet fun!
text: This piano mat is simple and fun! Literally just take out of the box and install the batteries and you're ready to play! It requires 3 AA batteries, which are not included. For the price it's decent. Not the greatest I have seen in piano mats. It's quite small compared to others as well. I say it's simple as it only has 4 prerecorded songs on it. Your child can play on their own as there are a few musical instruments on it to choose from as well as animal sounds. It also has volume control which is nice. It's still a nice product and a lot of fun.

title: Watch those little legs go!! So cute!
text: This set is so adorable! My 3 year old loves this doll and stroller set. The stroller requires no assembly, basically just unfold, lock in place, and go! There are adjustable seatbelts on the stroller to hold the doll in place which is nice. The coolest and cutest part of this is when you push the stroller, the dolls little legs kick and it looks so lifelike! The stroller is also very easy to push, even for my 3 year old daughter. The doll is beautiful with her big blue eyes and curly blonde locks. The set comes with a blanket, sippy cup, sunglasses, and a comb for her hair. It's a wonderful price for such a nice set with so many things!

title: Lots of fun and educational!
text: [[VIDEOID:ac7a1c92baf541f125db41d863c055e1]] My daughter just loves Baby Shark and this toy is right up her alley! There are 2 modes, shapes and song. When you insert a shape it will identify the shape to teach your little one or the song mode identifies the different family members: daddy, mommy, baby, grandma, and grandpa through the Baby Shark song! It's very cute, colorful, and engaging! Any little one would love this as a gift!

title: So cute and interactive!
text: Esme the Pixie Belle is seriously so cute and lots of fun! There are 3 different modes and she's very interactive. She spins pretty quickly and her horn lights up! She also sounds adorable! Even cooler, the tail detaches and your child can wear in their hair or as a bracelet! My daughter loves everything about Esme!! Awesome toy!!

title: Adorable little doll!
text: My daughter loves this little doll! She's so precious with her big green eyes and side ponytail! The carrier is easy to snap together and the strap has Velcro so your child can wear like a necklace. The doll is very lightweight. She comes with a set of headphones and a comb for her hair. Her hair is stiff as it has a lot of hairspray in it. When you first brush it, it looks like it's snowing because of all the hairspray! 😂 She's super cute and any child would love her!

title: Engaging and fun for everyone!
text: [[VIDEOID:73dc2bdab74d411737c8097bea26b197]] This game is just like the whack a mole at the arcade, just smaller and portable! My daughter loves playing it! It is very engaging and fun! It's nice as it has suction cups on the bottom so it stays in place while playing. The moles light up and the tactic is to whack the mole before the light goes out. If you have too many misses the game is over, but this makes it very challenging. It requires 3 AAA batteries (not included). You can play in English or Spanish as well. My whole family had a blast playing this game!

title: My daughter loves the baby shark design! So much fun!
text: This tent cube is a blast! It's smaller than your average tent, but works perfectly for my 3 year old! She can sit inside comfortably and even bring in a few stuffed animals for play time! There is an opening on each side which allows your child to enter and exit. Seems to be made well and such a great price too! It even folds up so nicely for storage which is a bonus as it saves space! The baby shark design is so cute and my daughter loves everything about this cube!

title: Awesome educational toy at a great price!
text: My daughter loves this board! It's so engaging, educational, and fun! The one side has the alphabet. It comes with magnets which have pictures of things starting with each letter of the alphabet. Your child can match up the magnets to the letters. It makes it easier for little ones as the color of the magnet actually matches the letter! My daughter really loved this part of it! The other side is a chalkboard. It's nice, however would be better if the chalk was included with it. Still giving it 5 stars as it's good quality at a great price!

title: So adorable and fun!
text: This little Pixie Belle cat is sooo adorable! My daughter loves it! There are 3 different modes that you can use with it. The cat spins around quickly and the horn on top of its head lights up with different colors. The sounds it makes are so cute. The base is removable and magnetic. The tail detached so you can wear as a bracelet too! Very nice quality toy and lots of fun! Would make a great Christmas gift!

title: So much for an excellent price!
text: This is a really nice pool diving toy set! You get so much for the price! Some of the toys even light up. The toys feel very durable like they will last a long time too! They come in a nice portable bag which is great for taking to the pool.

title: The cutest book ever!!
text: This book is really the cutest book ever! The animation is so charming and my 3 year old daughter just loves it! The concept is so cool, you read and then you match up the baby/child with the correct parent. Each page has a slot where you insert the baby or child so they stay in place. In a way, it's like a puzzle. It's really so darling and any child would love. Would make a great bedtime story.

title: So colorful and educational!
text: My toddler loves these books! They are so easy for her to turn the pages. You get 4 in this pack: Counting, Colors, Mommies and Babies, and Shapes. They are very educational and my wife loves reading these to my daughter. The books ask your little one questions like for example: how many puppies? Then this allows your little one to answer with the correct number. They are very engaging, colorful, and fun! The animation inside the books is adorable!

title: Not very sturdy and a bit frustrating to put together
text: My kids were excited about this gum ball machine, however my teenager and I became frustrated with the assembly. It's made of cheap plastic and the base is not very sturdy. It's a cool concept and is great once assembled. It comes with a booklet of the different mazes you can create which is cool. There are a lot of pieces though, so it's a bit overwhelming. We just did the basic track and it works fine. Do not turn the knob to the left to release the gum ball! This will result in a jam which is frustrating as you have to remove all the gum balls and take apart to clear the jam! Only turn it to the right! My teenage son loves having this in his bedroom though.

title: Adorable idea!! My daughter loves it!
text: This book is adorable and we love that you can read and do the puzzles with the foam pieces! My daughter couldn't put it down! My daughter is 3 years old and had no issues setting the puzzles in place. The illustration of the dinosaurs is so cute too!

title: Very detailed set, full assembly required.
text: This set is very nice and so detailed. The horses and the people that come with it are very detailed and nice quality. When you first open the box it's a bit overwhelming as there are so many pieces! Full assembly is required. The stickers are very tedious and there are a lot! Took me about 30-45 minutes to finish the assembly. 1 flaw is the vehicle.. the steering wheel and dashboard piece does not lock in very well. 1 little bump and it falls off. This is disappointing as the doctor is supposed to drive the van... and when you put her inside or take her out the dashboard and steering wheel fall off. The other pieces all lock in like they should. The accessories that come with the set are detailed too. I think this is a bit overpriced for what you get, but it would still make a nice gift for a child who loves horses.

title: Love the sounds! So realistic!
text: This truck with trailer set is all that and a bag of chips! My daughter loves this set. It's awesome that the wheel loader fits on the trailer and actually stays on with no issues. It has 3 buttons on the side which all make different and realistic sounds! It also lights up!! So cool! You can actually fit a lot of toys on the trailer too as it's huge! Moves around easily, even on carpet! Very nice quality truck set!

title: Adorable and fun!
text: This little Frozen quad is just adorable! I see the manufacturer's recommended age is up to 2 years, however my daughter is 3 and she  loves it!! It's easy for her to get on and off and doesn't go very fast which is safe! The only flaw is connecting and unconnecting to the charger. This was a bit difficult. Also, the turning radius is not the greatest.., it makes very wide turns and I am sure this was done for safety.

title: Kids love them!!
text: My kids love the singing monsters! Even my 14 year old as he grew up playing with the app! It's awesome that now they are a reality! They each have a switch on their back and a little button to push which makes them sing. They really sound just like the app!

title: Like the real thing!
text: This dump truck is great for imaginative play! It's just like a miniature version of the real thing! It's big and has a lot of space to fill with toys to dump! Also it moves across the floor easily, even on carpet! The only thing that could make it better is if it had sounds.

title: Wonderful, fun, and educational!
text: My daughter just loves this puzzle set! It's so much fun and educational! I played this with her today and it taught her so much about the human body. We would put together the puzzles over and over again! Super engaging! It's easy enough for a 3 year old too! The great part is that the puzzles are color coordinated, so you know which piece goes with which puzzle.

title: Great quality slime! Not sticky at all!
text: Both of my kids love slime and love this slime set! You get so many colors and they are all so pretty! The texture of the slime is real nice as it's not sticky at all! I see this lasting a long time.

title: Nikki the narwhal is so adorable and fun!
text: Nikki the narwhal is so adorable in every way!  So soft and perfect for hugging! You hug him and he kisses you back! I can't believe how interactive he is! It's amazing! When you play with him he responds in so many different ways! My daughter loves him so much! Any child would love this toy as a gift! The best fingerling yet!

title: The funniest toy on earth!!
text: This toy is by far the funniest I have ever seen! I mean, it's head is a butt!! And he farts when you pull his finger! My kids were cracking up non stop from this as the sounds are just hilarious! Great price too!

title: He's adorable!! So interactive!
text: Oh my goodness! A Dino fingerling! So cute! This toy is so interactive and my daughter loves it! He comes in a cool cage too! The dinosaur makes a lot of cool sounds and interacts with you! This would make a great Christmas gift for a child who loves dinosaurs!

title: Awesome concept!
text: Love love love this idea! My daughter loves it too! You can turn the doll to a boy or girl and there are so many different clothing styles to choose from! Very engaging and this is the first toy I have seen like this! The doll is well made and posable. Would make a great gift for a child who loves dolls!

title: So quiet that you can barely hear it.
text: My daughter loves Pinkfong and we so wanted to love this product, but we don't. It came with batteries included however you could barely hear anything.. so I changed the batteries. With new batteries it is a bit louder but still soooo quiet. It would have been nice if they added a volume control. My child got bored with this fast due to the fact that she could barely hear anything. I do like that it teaches your ABC's and 123's though.

title: Great quality slime and characters!
text: How cool is this? A slime set with Spongebob characters! My daughter is in love with this set! The characters are top quality and look exactly like the ones on the show! They come apart so you can put the slime inside them and watch it ooze out!! Too cool!! The slime is Nickelodeon and reminds my wife of the slime and gak that she played with as a child! This whole set is top quality and my kids are very pleased with it!

title: Affordable and fun for your little artist!
text: My daughter loves this set! Magnets and drawing together = so much fun! The left side is a magnetic dry erase board and the right is a dry erase book about trucks! The magnets are fun as you can build your own truck. The markers all connect which is cool to save space and to avoid losing them! They come with an eraser which is easy to use too! Hours of fun at a great price!

title: A total blast at an excellent price!
text: This set is awesome for the price. The assembly was fairly simple and the track is really 4 feet long! When done playing, it folds up so nicely for storage. You get 2 cars with the set and you get to watch them race down the track. Also, you can use your other Hot Wheels cars on this as well. The only pain is that the stickers were a bit tedious. Overall I am impressed and this would make a great Christmas gift!

title: Adorable and makes realistic sounds!
text: This set is perfect for tea party time! It comes with an adorable little pink teapot, 2 teacups, and some snacks! The teapot has 3 different settings and when you tip the teapot it actually makes the sound like tea is pouring into the cup. It really sounds so realistic!

title: Looks bigger than the picture and so easy to use!
text: My 3 year old daughter is a little artist and loves to draw with every opportunity that she gets! This DoodlePro is the perfect solution to avoid messes and dried up markers around the house! The pen is connected with a string so your child cannot lose it and it's very easy to erase... just slide the bar at the bottom and it clears the board. It also comes with 4 shape magnets that you can use as well. It's actually quite large too, which is a bonus!

title: Like a fluffy balloon animal!
text: This little plush unicorn is so adorable and I love the concept. You can untwist the unicorn to turn into a scarf and then twist the legs and tail back into the original unicorn shape. It reminds me of making balloon animals, except this is a soft and fluffy plush toy!

title: So cute and lots of fun!
text: My daughter loves the Enchantimals and this boat! The little monkey doll and monkey are sooo cute! It also comes with different accessories. The boat actually moves well with it's wheels. This would make a great Christmas gift for a child.

title: Adorable little play set!
text: Full assembly is required with this and when you open the box it's a bit overwhelming as there are so many pieces! It's really not that difficult to assemble though! Got it assembled in about 15 minutes! The little doll and accessories that come with the set are so adorable! Any little one would love this for imaginative play!

title: So interactive and fun! Perfect for Halloween!
text: Any child who loves Buzz Lightyear would adore this set! It was pretty easy to assemble and actually fits my 3 year old. The helmet is cool as you push the button and it goes up and down on it's own! It also talks in Buzz Lightyear's voice and says different phrases. It even has the launchers in the hand pieces like the real Buzz! They really went all out with this set and it would be perfect to accessorize your child's Buzz Lightyear Halloween costume!

title: Full assembly required. Once put together it's adorable!
text: [[VIDEOID:11f48c9c92477ff83892cc83045a8d87]] This has to be the cutest doll stroller ever! My daughter loves the little Mermaid and Flounder is her favorite character! When you push the stroller, the song plays and Flounder spins with the music. The bubble part was a bit messy and leaked at first, I honestly think the product would have been just fine without this piece. Full assembly is required and was a bit difficult. Most doll strollers come somewhat assembled, but not this one. I am not docking any stars because the stroller is superior quality and just adorable after it's assembled!

title: The cutest medical kit that I have seen!
text: My daughter loves playing doctor and this little set is perfect! You can actually squeeze the pump to the blood pressure cuff and it spins while squeezing to make it more realistic. There is also a button on the thermometer, it turns green for healthy, yellow for sick, and red for very sick. The little carry bag is so adorable too. This set is well made and fun at a great price!

title: So cute and fun!
text: My daughter went bananas over this toy as she just loves Spongebob and his pals! The only thing that would make it better is if Gary was included! He is my daughter's favorite! It's still a great set though. The figures are so cute and posable!

title: Tips over easily which was a little disappointing.
text: My 3 year old got frustrated with this toy. It's not very sturdy when the carnival is opened up and tips over easily if not leaning against something. Don't get me wrong, the carnival concept is adorable, but it's just difficult to play with as it's not sturdy at all.

title: So easy to make your own slime!
text: This kit is so easy to use and my kids love it! Just mix the glue with the magic confetti solution, mix, and you got slime in minutes! The quality of this slime is great, not sticky at all and super stretchy! So much fun!

title: So much fun!! My kids love this game and puzzle!
text: Whoever thought that feeding a pig hamburgers till he pops is a genius! My kids absolutely love this game! The concept is hilarious and fun! The puzzle that comes with it is fun too, and the pieces are large and easy for a child to do on their own.

title: This doll looks just like a newborn!
text: Wow! I can't believe how realistic looking this doll is! She looks so real and is just so beautiful. She comes with her own blanky and pillow. Her eyes look so real and are a beautiful shade of purple. She feels the weight of an actual newborn and her arms and legs are soft, not hard plastic. Madame Alexander really did an amazing job on this doll! My daughter just loves her!

title: She's gorgeous and a great collectible!
text: This doll is so beautiful that my wife refuses to remove her from the box. She is a great collector's item and my wife grew up watching The Little Mermaid, so this brings back memories for her! It's so nice of Disney to release this doll for the 30th anniversary of the release of the The Little Mermaid. This doll is just amazingly gorgeous and such a great price!

title: My daughter loves it!
text: This ball pit is great! No inflation required! When done playing, it folds up easily to store. It comes with some balls, but you probably want to purchase more to make it more fun! Great toy for the price!

title: So adorable! Smells so good too!
text: Absolutely love the popcorn box! This idea is super adorable! Inside is the cutest llama ever! She's so soft and perfect for hugging! She actually smells like marshmallows too! My wife says it reminds her of the Popples plush she had back in the 80's!

title: Just adorable and smells so good!
text: This really looks like a bottle of perfume! Upon opening we found a grape scented character. She smells so good! The scent reminds me of the grape scented markers from when I was in school. You also get tattoos and stickers, which is cool! My daughter loves this!

title: Like a plush pillow that smells good!
text: This Pikmi Pop set is adorable! It looks like a giant bottle of perfume! You find a fuzzy friend inside that smells so good! The scent is light and not powerful, which is good for people who are sensitive to strong scents.

title: The doll is cute, but super messy!
text: My daughter and wife tried this toy out yesterday and it's quite messy. The concept is you mix the slime powder and glitter into a bowl, add water, and mix it up with a whisk. Then you suck up the mix with ‘the  regoovenator' and feed it to the doll through it's mouth. This is the part that can be messy. Once done filling up, there is an accessory that covers it's mouth if you want to squish, or you can make the doll regurgitate. If you do, have a trash can nearby! Don't squeeze the doll without the cover on his mouth as the slime like fluid will go everywhere and make a huge mess. The doll itself is cute. The slime is more like a sticky goo. Needless to say, we ended up washing the doll in the bathtub last night to get all the remaining goo out.

title: Look exactly like the surprise eggs on ChuChu Tv!
text: My daughter loves ChuChu Tv and the surprise egg videos! These look exactly like the ones on ChuChu Tv!! They are easy and fun to open and close and the little animals inside are just adorable! They even have letters on the back of the eggs which helps with learning the alphabet.

title: So cute and perfect for storage!
text: My daughter just loves the Shopkins and this is basically a storage case to keep all your Shopkins in! It also turns into a grocery store which is so cool! Then when you are done playing it folds back up so easily! Love that the box it comes in looks like a cereal box!

title: Fun at a great price!
text: Treasure X just keeps on impressing! We have tried their toys before and had so much fun with them! This is a blast too! First, you get to crack open the top layer of the tomb. Inside you find 2 surprise bags with mystery toys along with kinetic rocks which is loads of fun!! My kids really enjoyed this!

title: My little one loves it!
text: My little one loves ChuChu Tv and Mr. Harlow. She was sooo excited about this train. It's adorable as you push the button and it plays the songs from ChuChu Tv and says “surprise” for when you open the surprise egg. You only get 1 egg with it (with Mr. Harlow inside), however you can add other toys to the train and push them around for a ride! This toy is super adorable!

title: So easy! Nice quality slime!
text: This slime was so easy and fun to make! You literally just empty the packets, add water, stir, and let sit for 5 minutes! You get 2 pretty colors (hot pink and teal). The slime is not sticky whatsoever, which is good! It's super stretchy too! The little figurines that come with the set are adorable as well. All around, it's a great product!

title: Fast as lightning!!
text: [[VIDEOID:35ff50a605dca2e20f6e79de1cfacfab]] Both of my kids love playing with this racetrack. Even I love it! It's so easy, just pop in the batteries, place the cars on the track, and watch them go! They zoom so fast and are so much fun to watch! It was very easy to assemble as well.

title: Cool set, however lights and sound did not work.
text: This is a cool set, but my child was disappointed that the lights and sound did not work! First of all, it's odd that this toy take the small circle batteries. I haven't seen this in a child's toy before. After inserting the 3 batteries it still didn't work. I had to shove a piece of metal inside the battery compartment to engage it and it finally worked. The stickers are very tedious and a little bit of a pain. The little airplane is so cute, but you only get 1 that comes with the set. It's definitely cool once you get it working, however this was a long, stressful process.

title: Easy for toddlers!
text: Mega Bloks are seriously the best toy ever for your toddler. They are so easy to build with and the added bonus on this set is the sounds! The jungle theme is so adorable too! Highly recommend!

title: Simply gorgeous!
text: This doll is just beautiful. So realistic that she even feels the weight of a new baby! My daughter just loves her as she is soft and perfect to snuggle. She comes with a onesie and socks so you can change her clothes. She even has her own lovey which is just adorable! So finely detailed that any doll lover would love her to pieces. She's perfect in every way!

title: Adorable little set!!
text: This is the cutest little supermarket set!! The little Shopkins that come with it are adorable too! The scale bobbles when you put an item on it, the cash register opens and closes (coins included), and there is a door that opens below the conveyor belt which allows your Shopkins to fall into the basket. The playmat that comes with it is the cutest!! The only thing that could make this better is if it made sounds and had lights. Still an amazing toy at an awesome price!

title: Simple and fun!
text: This is a perfect little set if you want to play picnic! You just need to have your own basket. The food is soft and comes apart with Velcro. You can pretend to cut the items which is cool, and it comes with a cutting board. Great for sensory and imaginative play!

title: Cute idea!!
text: Love that this idea is all about rescuing animals! You save the pet, bathe him/her, and groom him/her. The dog definitely looks scruffy, but so cute at the same time! Comes with a comb, a hair clip, and a collar to groom after bathing. He didn't dry right away, so we threw him in the dryer for a bit and it worked!

title: The cutest little fridge ever!
text: My daughter absolutely adores this little fridge! The little Shopkins food accessories that come with it are super cute! You can actually dispense the ice cubes and make the eggs jiggle which is cool! This looks exactly like the fridge on the Kindi Kids cartoon, which is totally awesome!

title: Tons of fun!!
text: This set is smaller than the other Melissa & Doug magnetic sets as it only includes the truck. It's simple, yet so much fun! It's easy for a child to put the truck together by themselves. Love how you can change the theme from ice cream, to tacos, to burgers! It comes with a lot of magnets to decorate your truck and the boy and girl that come with it.

title: Oh my goodness! Hilarious!
text: This toy is super silly and my kids love Spongebob! It's simple, you squeeze him and he farts! He says many funny sayings along with the farts! We were all cracking up over this toy! He is very soft and huggable too!

title: Difficult to open and break apart easily
text: These are not very kid friendly at all. They were difficult to open, even for me as an adult. They do look cool, but my kids had a hard time with these. Some even broke apart while trying to open.

title: Cute, but 1 paw is defective.
text: [[VIDEOID:aa96488edb7465cc2ded5fe94a82ec79]] If both paws worked this would be a nice accessory to a Halloween costume. It was unfortunate that 1 didn't work at all. The one that did work was cute with how it talks and lights up.

title: Best slime kit ever!!
text: This set is totally awesome!! My kids have tried so many brands of slime and this by far is their favorite! It's super stretchy and doesn't stick to your hands! Love the light that comes with it and allows your little to draw!! Just amazed by this!! So easy to make too!

title: Oh my goodness!! So cute!
text: My daughter loves playing doctor and loves this set! The little bag that holds the accessories is so adorable! All the accessories are made of wood, except for the bandaids. The bandaids are just stickers. This set is wonderful for imaginative play!

title: Therapeutic and relaxing!
text: The more you play with Pluffle, the more you learn to love it! It's not sticky at all. It works perfectly inside a sand table too! This is very fun to squish and works as a great stress reliever even for me as an adult! When you let it fall out of your hands it's beautiful and mesmerizing!! My kids love this stuff! The only thing you can't do with it is mold shapes as it doesn't hold it's form.

title: Perfect for the price!
text: This little Dino car would be great for a kid's birthday gift! He goes up and down as you push him around. He's fun, but basic, and for the price you can't go wrong.

title: So soft and perfect for hugging!
text: My daughter just loves Elmo and was so excited about this toy! You squeeze his tummy and his arms come up so you can hug him! He says so many different phrases and even sings songs! He asks for hugs and kisses which any kid would love to give him!! So cute!

title: Sooo adorable! We love this shopping cart!
text: Kindi Kids are the cutest toys ever and this shopping cart is so adorable! The dolls fit on the back of the cart perfectly and you can even put them in the cart and take them for a ride! The ears and paws move when you push the cart, which is super cute!! Every Kindi Kid doll needs this accessory!

title: This stuff grows on you!
text: At first I was a little iffy about this stuff, however it's actually very relaxing to play with.. even as an adult. It's so pretty to watch it settle. My daughter loves the glitter in it! Like kinetic sand, but doesn't really form into shape. Doesn't stick to hands at all which is a plus!

title: Adorable little set, perfect for reading to your child in the tub!
text: This little set is absolutely adorable. The whole thing can go in the bath and actually floats. The book comes with 3 penguins. They are made of plastic like material and are oh so adorable. The book itself is very short, but is great for kids learning how to read. The book also teaches to count, and you can use the 3 penguin toys and match them up to the ones inside the book!

title: So much fun putting together!
text: This set is so much fun as you get to build your own firehouse. You can set up any way you wish, and it comes with lots of magnets so you can decorate! Fun and educational for a child. My 3 year old loves this, but finds it easier to stick on the magnets while laying it flat on the floor, opposed to standing it up.

title: Just like my wife remembers Polly Pocket!
text: My wife experienced total 90's kid nostalgia with this toy as it reminded her of Polly Pocket! You get 3 keys to open different areas of the mall, once you open it up the possibilities are endless! The items inside move around and there are so many different places to stand the 2 dolls! It even comes with a little van that is so adorable!

title: She's absolutely beautiful and realistic!
text: From the moment I opened the box I could not believe how realistic this doll looks. She's beautiful and her hair is so soft. Her weight is just like a real baby and her body is soft! Her clothes are super soft too! My 3 year old daughter loves her, but I had to put this doll on a shelf as she looks more like a collector's piece rather than a toy. Will keep her in nice condition and give to my daughter when she's a bit older.

title: So adorable and entertaining!
text: My daughter loves Butterbean's Cafe and was so excited about this set! You get 4 characters, each has their own cart and treats. The carts actually have wheels that move which is a plus! Also the little treats come off the stands so you can use your imagination during playtime! Love that each little doll has hands perfectly cut to fit onto the carts. You can attach them to the handle or even the butterflies on top. My daughter was “making them fly” in the attached pictures (attached hands to butterflies on top of carts). Excellent toy overall!

title: Easy and fun!
text: The little containers for the slime are so cute! Each comes with a slime mix packet and decoration. Just empty contents into container, add cold water to line, shake for 30 seconds, remove lid and let sit for 5 minutes. We tried the hot cocoa one first and the little decorations started falling out. For the strawberry milk and bubblegum we chose not to add the decorations to avoid a mess. The slime is a bit sticky at first but gets better the longer it sits and the more you play with it. The hot cocoa one smells great! The other 2 were a bit overpowering. This is a fun little project for kiddos!

title: So easy to put together!
text: This set was super easy to put together and the instructions were so easy to follow. I have added 2 pictures: The first was yesterday at noon and the other was this morning at 4am. We have used some other So Magic sets and noticed this one in particular doesn't grow as fast as all the others. That's ok though, it's still beautiful and the figurines are adorable!

title: Wow!! It's really magic!
text: This was so much fun and easy to put together. The instructions are so easy to follow. I added 2 pictures: The first was yesterday at noon and the second was this morning at 4am. I honestly couldn't believe my eyes as to how much the coral grew! It's beautiful and looks like a cotton candy tree! The little figurines included are so adorable. This would be a beautiful piece for a child's room as it's sooo pretty!

title: The doll is adorable and fun to squish!
text: The little doll is so cute. My daughter loves it and just loves how squishy it is! The head is hard plastic, however the whole body is squishy. When you squish him you can see all the glitter it's filled with, so pretty! The slime activity was the downfall of this item. You only get a tiny bit and the texture was strange and sticky.

title: We love it!! Lots of fun over and over again!
text: My little one loves opening things and this set is absolutely perfect for her. It keeps her engaged for a long time as you can open over and over again! The gems are so pretty and it's easy to put them back inside the rocks. Then, get your hammer and chisel and open for surprises inside! We actually used some of our own small toys inside the rocks to change it up a bit and it works great! They even come with a carrying bag for storage! Great use of fine motor skills and very entertaining. We enjoy playing with this very much.

title: So easy, fun, and beautiful!
text: [[VIDEOID:293bb8509567da7a4f9dc81d4eb020da]] My wife and daughter did this as an activity tonight and they loved every second of it! It's so easy and fun! Just open the jar, take out the paper and stickers inside, add the toys, fill with water, add your glitter and confetti with the magic mix, turn on the light on lid and put back on tightly, shake, and it's done! Then when it's done you can add the stickers to make it even more prettier. The cool thing is, every time you shake it the light comes on and it changes color!

title: Makes bath time a lot more fun!
text: These are just so adorable! A must have for any child who loves mermaids and sea life! So colorful and fun! They float in the bath water and don't sink. When wet, they stick to the wall of the tub. I love the fact that the container can be used for storage. It has a suction cup so you can just hang right in your tub!

title: Loads of fun!
text: We tried these tonight for the first time and they are wonderful! The artwork Is so colorful and fun, and they are so soft. They float in the bath water and don't sink. When wet, they stick to the wall of the tub. These are great for learning to count and love that the container can be used for storage. It has a suction cup so you can just hang right in your tub!

title: Makes bath time so much fun!
text: We used this tonight during my 3 year old's bath time! She loves it! You can pour from one tube to another and basically pretend you are a scientist! It's even more fun with colored bath tabs and foam (you need to purchase separately). It comes with a little booklet of different activities you can do, and the possibilities are endless!

title: Smells so good!!
text: This is so much fun and it really is so easy! Just empty the packet into the cup, fill with cold water to the line, shake for 30 seconds, and then let sit for 5 minutes! Then wa-la! You have scented slime! The more you play with it the less stickier it gets too. The decorations for the slime kept falling out though. If I could do it again, maybe wouldn't use the decorations as they fall out and seem to get all over the place. Still a wonderful product and lots of fun!

title: So lifelike and adorable!
text: My daughter loves that this doll looks exactly like her! She's so lifelike as her head and mouth move when she talks! She says so many different phrases and lets you know when she's hungry! She comes with 2 diapers, feeding accessories (including 2 food mixes), and a comb for her hair. Any child would love her! She's perfect in every way!

title: Awesome toy! Just wish that his arms extended out when flying him around
text: The design of this toy is awesome and love how he says different phrases and lights up. He's posable, however the arm articulation is a bit flawed as the permanent front piece and back piece don't allow his arms to fully extend. My child was flying him around and it just didn't seem natural with his arms down. The sword does not stay in his hand very well either. The cool thing is the faster you make him fly, the faster the sound goes with him!

title: Feels like shredded rubber pieces, but fun!
text: If you shredded up some rubber, it feels exactly like this. It's not sticky, but like confetti in a way and can get all over the place very easily. Once we put into the sand table it turned out great though. It does look pretty with the colors mixed together. When it sets it reminds me of kinetic sand in appearance, however doesn't feel like kinetic sand at all. You can't really sculpt anything with it either, but it's fun to smush and watch set.

title: Cute, but wish the toy did more things.
text: This owl is cute, and does help with motor skills as you can flap his wings, squeak his beak, and drop in the coins... however my 3 year lost interest in this toy pretty quickly as he doesn't do that much. Just wish he did more!

title: Lots of fun and great for learning colors!
text: My 3 year old loves this set! It's so easy for a child to open and close these little surprise boxes! The little toys inside are adorable too! It's great use of fine motor skills and you can match the colors of the toys to the boxes as well. This is fun and education in 1 bundle!

title: Soooo adorable!!
text: [[VIDEOID:f725f875fc3592684f6c1f1d25ad51d5]] This doll is oh so adorable! My daughter just loves her to pieces! She's so beautiful with her big blue eyes and blonde pig tails! My daughter has light up shoes just like her and loves walking around with her like they are twins! She talks and says a lot of different phrases and comes with the cutest accessories! She's light and the perfect size for your little one to carry around!

title: Fun for sculpting and not sticky!
text: This stuff is great and you get so much foam in this set! You get a case full of it, plus extra in the shape and learn numbers set! My children love this stuff as it's easy to mold and doesn't stick to your hands. Plus, it never dries out which is amazing. You also get a set of flash cards with the set which are great for learning!

title: Cute toy, but thought would be faster than it is.
text: What can be cuter than an elephant in a bathtub car? My daughter loves this. You just pump the elephant up and down a few times, set him in his bathtub car, and watch him go! He goes kind of slow and when it said “zoom” I thought it would have been faster. The toy is adorable though.

title: So much fun and perfect for Mario lovers!
text: This castle was so easy to assemble, the stickers were a bit tedious though. It's so much fun once put together! There is an elevator, a trap door, and cage that opens and closes. It only comes with 1 figure (Bowser) so we used our figures that we already had for more fun! The castle even makes sounds and plays music! So cool!

title: Makes you jump out of your seat every time!
text: [[VIDEOID:22ae3365fe1d5e7618cdf024681d038f]] My wife and kids played this game last night and they all loved it! It's so easy to assemble and the concept of the game is easy. First fill up inside the sink with water and attach the faucet. Then, let the fun begin! You have to take a tool from the plumber's toolbox and attach to his belt without him knowing. If you aren't careful, or his belt gets too heavy, he will pop up and everyone gets sprayed with water! This is a blast, but be sure to keep paper towels on hand or play outside because you will get wet!

title: So lifelike I can't believe it!
text: [[VIDEOID:14f28d9aec319f9dcb5491cfbca11f06]] This doll is absolutely amazing! It's almost just like having a newborn in our house! My daughter loves playing with her, tickling her, feeding her, rocking her, singing to her, and giving her the pacifier. I am just blown away as to how lifelike she looks! Her facial expressions are exactly like a real newborn baby! She's so interactive and fun that any child would love her to pieces! She would even be perfect for an adult with baby fever! She is so soft like a real baby too! Her chest moves up and down after you put her to sleep which makes it appear that she is actually breathing! This doll is quite incredible and is an amazing deal for the price!

title: She's so pretty and perfect!!
text: My daughter adores this doll! She's so pretty with her different color hair and pig tail twists. Her head bobbles, which is adorable! Her dress is so fun and playful too! She is not scented that I could tell, but she is as cute as can be. She comes with 2 snacks, a cake pop and a drink. The cake pop has a lid that you can take off and then feed the cake pop to the doll. Don't worry it's just plastic, but it's so magical as it appears that she is actually taking a bite out of the cake pop! My daughter is fascinated with this! The drink is squeezable, and when you squeeze it it appears that she is sipping through her straw! Love every detail of this doll and haven't seen anything quite like her!

title: Awesome sound effects and lights!
text: This toy is so cool! The sword has a button you push and it lights up and makes sounds. As you swing it around it continues to make sounds, which is super neat! This would be great for Halloween if your child is going as a Power Ranger!

title: Perfect size for a toddler!
text: [[VIDEOID:ec8a61b6293aec1b9e90945e82412d41]] This is the cutest! It has different songs to play to, just push the button, pick a song, and play! The strings actually make music which is so cool! Any little one would love this! It's so easy for my 3 year old daughter to hold and play!

title: She sounds like a real baby!
text: First impression is that this is the most adorable doll ever! Her little bear suit is the cutest! She has a full head of hair too (other Cry Babies don't). My daughter loves playing mini doctor with this doll. She actually gets the chicken pox and needs a shot to make them go away! You can use the stethoscope to hear her heart, and if it's beating fast that means she is sick and you give her medicine to make her feel better. The thermometer determines if she has a fever and if so, apply the cloth on her forehead. When this baby cries, it sounds like a real baby crying... and the cry sounds like she is in pain if you don't help her. You can also fill her head with water to make real tears, however this makes her very top heavy, to the point where she tips over. She's great without the water though! We were so impressed and my little one loves her to pieces.

title: So realistic!
text: My daughter just loves this doll! She's so realistic as her mouth moves when she talks! She says some of the cutest things as well! My daughter loves playing mommy and feeding her! She comes with 2 food mix packets (peas and bananas), a feeding tray, bowl, spoon, 2 diapers, sippy cup, and a comb for her hair. This baby doll actually wets and poops in her diaper! My little one loves changing her too, acting like she is a mommy to her baby. All in all this little doll is so adorable and any little girl would love her!

title: Soft, big, and lovable!!
text: This dinosaur is the cutest plush ever!! Perfect for cuddling as he is so soft! Well made and perfect for any child who loves dinosaurs! He even comes with an adoption tag so you can personalize for your child

title: The perfect gift for a little girl!
text: This set is adorable! It comes with a princess, car, and accessories that are just the cutest ever!! This toy allows your child to use their imagination and take the princess for a royal ride! Any child who loves Shopkins would love this as a gift!

title: So fun and educational!
text: This toy is loads of fun!! It was so easy to put together the hospital and ambulance, that even a child could do it! It comes with so many magnets that the possibilities with this toy are endless! It's educational as well as you can teach your child many new things related to medical. My daughter just loves this!

title: Lightly scented and oh so cute!
text: If your child loves playing with hair, this is the toy for them! These little dolls have so much hair that the possibilities are endless! They come with accessories for their hair so you can do many different styles! The scent is very light, but this is a good thing for people who are sensitive to strong scents. We didn't get the same ones as pictured, however they are a surprise pack so it's random as to who you will get. We happened to get 2 ultra rare dolls and they are simply adorable!

title: The most adorable toy ever!!
text: [[VIDEOID:80b9be94c10b2368cafccd2c1e00d6d4]] If your little one loves unicorns, this is a must have!! The unicorn is so realistic with it's facial movements and makes sounds! Even the horn glows and changes color depending on how she feels. She comes with accessories: stethoscope, bandage, tube of cream, bottle, and thermometer. Each of these accessories is interactive with the toy and it's amazing! Both my wife and daughter love playing with this as they love unicorns!

title: Engaging and lots of fun!
text: My 3 year old daughter just loves Sesame Street and her face lit up when she saw these blocks! These are like normal wooden building blocks, except with Sesame Street designs! It includes the character's faces, trees, clouds, the village, and more! Very easy for a child to stack and create different designs!

title: Cool little cars!!
text: The little cars are so detailed and so much fun! We are Cars fans and absolutely love these! They come in a cardboard box, and inside are placed in clear plastic. If you are giving this as a gift, do not open the cardboard box, as it will appear as it has been opened already.

title: The box is the coolest part!
text: This is a cool concept. It comes in a surprise box. You tear the little door on the front bottom left (as pictured), turn the wheel next to it, and out comes a surprise capsule... This part reminds me of a gum ball machine! In each capsule, there is a piece of a doll. Once you get all capsules, you open and assemble the doll. This was a bit difficult, even for me! The pieces of the doll did not seem to want to lock in place. The doll itself is a bit creepy looking, lol. My child loves the box with the capsules! Do not throw away the box as you can use this and the capsules with other toys!

title: Cute idea!
text: This is a cute toy at a great price! It literally looks like a can of cat food. You twist the lid and it pops open with surprises! Inside the surprise bags you will find tiny little animals (2), some accessories, and some furniture. It also comes with stickers to decorate. Once done playing, just twist back into original can. This is great for taking on the road.

title: Just snap together and go!! Hours of fun!!
text: This is a must have for any child who loves Paw Patrol! When you first open the box you see soooo many pieces to assemble...and it is a bit overwhelming, lol (I was thinking in my head, this is going to take hours to set up!) However it comes with handy instructions and what I thought would take forever, literally only took about 15 minutes!! No screws needed, and all the pieces snap together easily. It turned out to be a breeze!! My kids just love this toy as it keeps them engaged with all the different activities! The command center lights up with sound, the zip line is perfect for the toys to swing down, the elevator goes up and down and also opens the secret doors, and there is a vehicle launcher at the bottom for the car and pup it comes with. This seriously is an amazing toy and would make a perfect gift!

title: The whole family loves Juno!!
text: [[VIDEOID:44aedf13aaca8ea403ffa3aa39e74be5]] Juno is seriously the cutest baby elephant ever!! He comes packaged in the most adorable box and my whole family just loves playing with him! He's so easy to use too! Just insert 4 AA batteries, turn on the switch, and play! The button on his back wakes him up and it's quite hilarious as he wakes up with soooo much energy!! He comes with a little mouse and peanut; these are magnets you can attach to his trunk. He will cuddle and kiss the mouse and sniff and make chewing sounds with the peanut. Watch out though, sometimes he likes to throw them with his trunk!! This had my entire family bursting with laughter! Juno does sooo many different things and will keep your little one entertained for quite some time! My kids absolutely love him!!

title: Extremely entertaining!!
text: This toy is loads of fun!! It's so easy to set up and the horse is soft and adorable!! This set allows children to live their equestrian dream and use their imagination! My daughter just loves this and loves the accessories that come with it to dress up your horse!!

title: So easy and fun!
text: These are so much fun! You get 3 slime containers and in each holds slime mix, glitter confetti, and a small surprise toy! All you have to do is empty the packet contents in the container, fill water to the line, and shake for 30 seconds. Then remove lid, let sit for 5 minutes and it's time to play! The only issue is that the slime came out a bit sticky. The more you play with it though, the less stickier it gets.

title: Easy for kids to use!
text: My 3 year old can operate this on her own, that is literally how easy it is to use! You get the cube + 2 bracelets for your hands. There are so many modes and types of music to choose from that your child will not get bored with this! Hours of fun!

title: Perfect for a little princess!
text: This castle was easy to assemble! It comes with 1 doll, furniture, and accessories. This toy is perfect for imaginative play! My daughter just loves this as she can bring her other Shopkins to the castle for an adventure! It's just so cute!

title: So adorable!
text: [[VIDEOID:158614fa78d8eeb6f02debc44b1912d1]] My daughter absolutely loves this doll! She is all about the Cry Babies and was so excited about Hally the Dragon! She comes packaged so nicely and it looks like she is strapped in her car seat. So easy to use, just open the Velcro on the back of her outfit, turn on, and play! She cries when sitting up, however if you lay her down, she stops. The outfit is so adorable! If you take off her hood, there is an opening where you can fill her head with water which gives the effect that she is actually crying! Be careful though, can get surfaces or floors wet. Best thing is to empty out the water once done playing with her to avoid surprise messes!

title: Takes fine motor skills and time
text: This is a cool toy! Reminds me of the Lite Brite toy I owned as a child! It's so easy to set up and use! Just plug in (or add batteries for wireless), insert card, turn on, and go! There are so many pictures to choose from as well. Setting the pixels in place takes time, patience, and use of fine motor skills. If your child is not patient, then this toy is not right for them.

title: Her hair actually feels and looks like real cotton candy!
text: She looks bigger than the picture in person! So adorable and lightly strawberry scented. Love that she comes with accessories and hair chalk if you want to change up her do'! It's very difficult to get her to stand on her own, but she is very flexible and can sit instead. My daughter just loves her and was like “Wow! She has super long hair!”. If your child loves playing with hair on dolls, this would be a perfect gift!

title: Adorable little surprise toy!
text: First impression is that the ice cream looks so real!! Just like a real DQ blizzard! You open it up and find a cute little doll inside with blind bags! My little 3 year old was able to put the clothes on the doll herself! So easy and fun! The hair and outfits are removable, so you can collect more and swap out their hair pieces and outfits! My daughter loves ice cream and dolls! This is a match made in heaven!

title: So adorable!
text: [[VIDEOID:e024533f9dfbd7806d26dc38af807457]] This doll is the cutest! She's so interactive and says so much! You can make her hop and her shoes even light up. She comes with accessories: diaper, glasses, bottle, and a comb. My 3 year old loves changing her diaper and feeding her! *Note* You can add water to her bottle which will make her wet her diaper. This dolly makes my daughter feel like a real mini mommy!

title: Great for imaginative play!
text: My 3 year old loves this! She spends hours playing with this and it is great for imaginative play. It comes with 1 character, however she has other characters that she plays with and pretends that they are going for a ride! The inside is so roomy that you can fit tons of toys in there! There is a button to push that makes light and sound, which is an added bonus! Comes with disc launchers which is easy for a child to load and shoot on their own. No assembly required, which I love! Very sturdy and well made toy!

title: So educational and fun!
text: This toy is just amazing! Both of my kids just love the Kinderbot! He does much more than what we thought initially. There are 3 black buttons on top which are for different modes. He has other buttons on top for direction: forward, backward, right, and left. Your little one can create codes using the arrows and then push the pink play button and he does exactly what your child coded! He is so realistic and when he falls down says “Whoa” lol. If this happens, you just have to help him up again. He even dances and walks the dog! So educational as it teaches your little one direction, math, shapes, and so much more! This interactive toy deserves 5 stars as it is not only fun, but educates your child at the same time!!

title: Such a pretty little outfit!
text: So sparkly and fun! Came packaged so nicely and is so easy to put on your doll. Velcro on back of dress allows easy on and off. The style of this outfit matches my daughter's style and she absolutely adores it!

title: The coolest truck toy!
text: My daughter absolutely loves Demo Duke! Some of the things he says and does is just hilarious! He crashes, but you can fix him with the touch of a button! He falls asleep and snores if you don't play with him, which I find hilarious. This is such a cool idea! Very interactive toy and engages your child's mind!!

title: Absolutely adorable!
text: My daughter just loves this plush giraffe! He's so soft and big! Perfect to cuddle on! He's bigger than expected, but who would complain about that? Lol. Love that he comes with an adoption certificate that you can write on and personalize for your child! Great value for what you get! Definitely 5 stars!

title: Very interactive and fun!
text: My 3 year old loves this toy! It does everything a real car does from turning on the ignition, to shifting, to controlling the turning signals, to honking the horn (her favorite part)! This is perfect for the car or wagon rides to keep your little one entertained! For the price you can't beat it!

title: She's adorable and perfect for a child to carry around!
text: My daughter loves her! She's so pretty and posable! Her hair is so soft and realistic. Her eyes look very real as well. Adorable outfit and love that there are different outfits you can purchase for different looks! All around, great doll for the price!

title: Cool concept
text: Very cool toy. You need to purchase your own hot wheels track separately in order for it to work. The set comes with 2 very well detailed cars. Easy to operate.

title: Awesome set, loads of fun!
text: My kids love this toy! Easy to set up and is quite hilarious! The grave digger monster truck races down the track to try and take down Grim. Every time you hit Grim in the chest he does something different, which is cool. At the end he throws his head back with his mouth wide open and hands up in the air!! This means you have conquered Grim... From that point do all over again!  Very cool concept and well made toy!

title: Awesome toy!!
text: My 3 year old loves this set!! They are like Hatchimals, but with dragons! The eggs are easy for a child to open and is so exciting to get a surprise dragon inside! They come with cards and you can match your dragons to them! My child has not put down the dragons all day and absolutely loves these!

title: So engaging and challenging!
text: My kids absolutely love this set! It is a quest so you have to follow the instructions. Lots of hidden treasures inside! Once done playing you can easily fold up the case for storage. So many surprises inside and kept my kids engaged for over an hour! Also comes with kinetic rocks. Super amazing toy!!

title: Adorable little set!!
text: My daughter absolutely loves the set. The doll is adorable and posable. The set appears to come with a lot of food items, however in reality you only get 4...which was kind of a bummer! The shopping cart is so cute and you can add other small toys to it for fun. My daughter loves shopping and this toy is perfect for imaginative play!!

title: Easy for kids to use!
text: My daughter loves taking pictures and loves this little camera. It's so easy for her to use and she can play games, make videos, take selfies, and regular pictures. The camera came packaged so nicely and is so adorable. It looks like a makeup compact with a mirror. The only downfall is the quality of the pictures, but my daughter doesn't seem to mind. Comes with it's own charger and there is a slot for headphone access. It's also easy to insert to SD card. Very cute idea and perfect for little girls!

title: So detailed and fun!
text: My kids love these as they look so real but are miniatures! My daughter is fascinated with planes, jets, and helicopters, so this is right up her alley! They are toys, however so detailed that you can keep as collectibles as well. Seem very sturdy like they would last through tons of play time!

title: Coolest Toy Bear ever....A Must get for any occasion!!!
text: [[VIDEOID:8fb3629a78bc0dff8b78192269cd18f1]] No matter whatever the occasion is, Birthday, Christmas, in the Hospital stay......he is just so soft, cuddly & cute. A must get....Highly recommend, price is fair to the market in regards to the item. Make sure to check out product review video. Hope it helps....~~~Happy Shopping~~~

title: Neat concept....But???
text: I have a 14 year old and a 3 year old. They both really didn't get this, game....as well as myself. Can be an educational game nonetheless. Batteries died super fast with all the bugs, they do go super fast! Cards give detailed info about each bugs......but for the price, I feel it's overpriced. The bugs are super fun to play with while they lasted though. Great idea...but missed the mark.

title: The cutest idea!! My daughter loves this!
text: My daughter loves to color and draw and absolutely loves this set!! The 4 little figures are adorable and come with their own bathtub, scrubbing brush, and washable markers! The markers are very washable and come off easily, which is a plus! We colored all 4 of these and then she took the figures and bathtub to bath time with her! They turn white again so easily! The tub is adorable.. when you fill with water, there is a little pink button by the shower that you push to make water come out. After her bath, she colored again!! She just adores this toy!!

title: Totally Awesome Fun...Can't go wrong with this!!!
text: [[VIDEOID:b4cd8fd1b13bafe1499f19a554e899f9]] This bad boy is a blast......even my 14 year old teenager loves this! So much fun.....We can't get enough!!!! Please check out product review video and or photos, Hope they help in possibly purchasing. It will make a great gift for any occasions!!! ~`~Happy Shopping~~~

text:
