Overall super cute and fun little toy, my daughter loved it.....check out product review video and or pictures...hope this helps!!!!

~Happy Shopping~

title: Perfect Gift as always Adorable!!!
text: [[VIDEOID:fd19a49a68b6cdaccebab624d13bd6a2]] We've been collecting these for quite sometime.....Always fun to open and see what's inside. These are really different from previous one, they are like real eggs cracking! Check out pictures and product review video, hope it helps! ~~~ Happy Shopping~~~

title: My 3 year old loves this game!
text: I ordered this game for my 3 year old daughter and she just loves it! She grabbed onto the concept of the game so quickly and it kept her busy for a long time! The little figures are adorable too! For the price you can't beat it! Great for traveling too!

title: Can be annoying to some...But we Love it!!!
text: [[VIDEOID:1ba1ccbf23f4c641c3166efbd0f080fc]] Such a fun interactive toy......can't go wrong with the Sponge! Sponge-bob that is haha! Check out product review video and pictures. Hope it help...I would recommend this for any occasion gift. ~~~Happy Shopping~~~

title: Adorable little set!!
text: My 3 year old just loves Toy Story and this little set! You can turn the handle of the Ferris wheel and Woody and Ducky go around and around! Music plays while the Ferris wheel moves and it is oh so cute! My daughter has a lot of little people, so she tried them on this toy and they fit perfectly! *Note* Only Woody and Ducky come with the set.. the other one is just an example to show that other little people fit just fine!! The toy to the left of the Ferris Wheel is a bit boring as it loses my daughter's attention quickly, however I'm still giving it 5 stars as the Ferris Wheel is awesome!!

title: This Dino is loads of fun!!
text:
This toy is just awesome! Comes packaged so nicely and is easier to remove from packaging compared to other kids toys. The only assembly that needs to be done is attaching his tail.. which was a piece of cake! You can make the Dino move around as if he were real! He has a handle behind his head, when you squeeze it, his mouth opens. This is the part my 3 year old loves as he comes with a little dude that you can put in the dinosaur's mouth! When you do this he swallows him and then open up the compartment on his back to retrieve him. She also enjoys feeding him her other small toys and just gets a kick out of it!!
This toy is well made and deserves 5 stars!!

title: Cute set, however if you move the pieces fall apart easily
text: The pieces were easy to assemble, however if you move to a new location the pieces fall apart easily. The set is very cute and my 3 year old loves the little ladybugs and frog that come with it. She helped pour in the soil and seeds.. this part is very easy and fun for a young child! She is excited to see her flowers grow in her garden cottage.

title: Wish this toy did more
text: My child loves Toy Story and Duke Kaboom! The toy comes packaged nicely, however it really only does 2 things and my child gets bored with it quickly. It launches Duke Kaboom on his motorcycle, however when doing this most of the time he falls off. Launching the motorcycle alone goes a further distance as well. The other part is the 2 red poles pop up. It's difficult for a child to put these back in place, so you may need to assist. One of the poles bent immediately after trying to set back in place. Cool little action figure but wish the set was made better and did more.

title: The perfect addition for your playroom!!
text: My daughter loves unicorns.. Well, I know this is not a unicorn (It is Pegasus), however she just loves him and still thinks he is a unicorn who lost his horn!! Lol. He is beautiful, soft, and very well detailed! Perfect to hug!! Makes a great display for your playroom as he is just so pretty to look at!!

title: So much fun and educational!!
text: My 3 year old daughter loves singing and learning about the alphabet. Turns out she loves this game even more!! This is such a cool concept to put the letters in the whale, have him spit them out, and try to spell the words on the cards! There are so many cards that come with it so the game will keep your littles busy for a long time!! The whale is absolutely adorable and the lever is easy for your child to use to get the letters out. I want to add, sometimes the whale gets clogged, however it's an easy fix by giving him a few shakes! The lid is a little hard to get off and back on (for a young child), so you will need to help your child with this part. All in all, this is a great game and will help your child with spelling.

title: Absolutely adorable!!
text: My daughter loves the Cry Babies but never saw this new character until now! She loves Bruny so much as she is a dragon (dragons are one of her favorite creatures)! But also because she is sparkly and pink! The outfit is so adorable and detailed exactly like a dragon. She has other Cry Babies like this one, however she says this one is special as she has little blue stars on the side of her face!! These definitely give her more character! The product was packaged very nicely and it actually looks like she was strapped in her car seat! The on and off switch is easy to maneuver as it is on her back. Just undo the Velcro on the outfit, flip the switch and she immediately starts crying! There is an opening on the top back of her head where you can fill up with water. By doing this it creates the “magic tears”! Just be careful because it can leak out onto your floor! Also once done playing, make sure you empty out the water so it won't mold. All in all, an adorable little dolly made with great quality!! Batteries are included!

title: He's so big, soft, and adorable!!
text: My daughter loves going to SeaWorld to see the penguins, so I thought I would order this guy for her. She absolutely loves him!! He's actually taller than her! She is 3 years old and in the 90th percentile for height. He's perfect to hug and love on as he is sooo soft! He also stands up without assistance. Very lifelike and he is the next best thing when you can't make a trip to SeaWorld!! The only downfall is he is a bit pricey, however Melissa and Doug always makes quality products so it is expected.

title: So adorable and my daughter loves!!
text: My daughter has loved the Cry Babies for so long and it was so difficult finding these toys in the U.S. We bought for her previously, however it came with a hefty price tag and shipping from the U.K. We were so excited to see the Surprise Bottle House on Amazon!! My daughter's favorite Cry Baby is Lady and we never got her until now!! My daughter was so excited!! Thank you Amazon for carrying this product at an amazing price!! My daughter's face was priceless and she is on Cloud 9!! The product is absolutely adorable with many accessories. *Note* A baby bottle and accessory is hidden on the left side of the capsule. You have to open the cardboard where the house design is to get it out. There are ridges where you can tear. Please be tedious while doing this so you don't mess up with pretty picture on the left side of the house!! The babies are nice too as they have an opening on the top/back of head where you can fill up or drain. Highly recommend  these dollies for your little as they are just so fun and cute!!

text: I bought this after buying one that looked just like it from another seller.  Since their price went up after I purchased the first one,  I looked at other sellers.  This one looks just like it but it does not have a zipper to remove an inner pillow.  The other one did and that pillow seemed more firmly stuffed than this one.  So I'm a little disappointed.  I bought this for my grandson who liked the other one I got for his brother and I'm hoping he won't even notice the differences and will love it.
